URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291408
DESCRIPTION:Fraternity & Sorority is hosting its Annual Leadership Retreat for Chapter Presidents and Governing Council Exec Board Members. The retreat will focus on equipping our FSL leaders with the skills necessary to effectively lead their community and create positive change. \n\nAttendance at the retreat is required for chapter presidents and the entire executive boards of each governing council\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291408
