UID:c9b07637d3b3370a66132115a471685a12192025_2:05:50_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:How to Intern Abroad for Mason Credit - Virtual Info Session
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291984
DESCRIPTION:Join GEO to learn how you can earn Mason credit while interning abroad with an international company or organization.\n\n•	Travel, Virtual, and Hybrid internship opportunities available \n        https://studyabroad.gmu.edu/internships/how/index.html  \n•	Intern during Semester, Summer, or Winter Break\n•	Most career fields available\n•	Options for you to be placed in a guaranteed internship or for you to secure your own\n•	Flexible virtual and hybrid (both remote work and 1-4 week travel) options available\n•	Financial aid can be used towards programs\n•	Scholarships available \n•	Some paid options available\n•	For undergrad, graduate, and recently graduated students\n\n\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/s/93251391228\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291984
END:VEVENT
