UID:9f6dd66773ea44e54bd52296c83dbf4b182026_11:55:29_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Becker CPA Review: New Year, New You Career Webinar
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292248
DESCRIPTION:Join Beta Alpha Psi. Start the new year by investing in your future!\n\nJoin Becker's Mike Brown and Kelly Pope for an engaging virtual session designed to help you take your career to the next level.\n\nIn this webinar, you'll discover:\n- How earning an accounting certification can open doors and boost your professional credibility\n- The benefits of dual certification and how it can set you apart in a competitive job market\n- Unique and unexpected career paths available within each certification\n\nWhether you're looking to advance in your current role or explore new possibilities, this session will provide insights and strategies to help you make 2026 your best year yet.\n\nDate: Wednesday, January 14, 2026\nTime: 1:00 PM ET\nLocation: Virtual (Webinar link provided upon registration)\n\nOpen to all majors. Free to attend.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292248
END:VEVENT
