UID:ff5810493a46466045669cf525af51e01252025_6:34:27_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:George Mason Esports Overwatch 2 Spring 2026 Tryouts
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291782
DESCRIPTION:Overwatch 2 Spring 2026 Tryout Information:\n\nPlatform: PC ONLY\n\nDate and Times:\n- Sign-up Deadline: Friday, January 9th @ MIDNIGHT\n- Main Tryout Dates: Saturday, January 10th and Sunday, January 11th @ 8:00 - 10:00 PM EST\n- If needed, a last chance tryouts will be held a later TBD date for those who can't make it to the original tryout date\n\n- Location: George Mason Esports Discord (https://discord.gg/gmuesports)\n\nRequirements/Recommended Rank Requirements:\n- MUST be a FULL-TIME GMU Student (minimum 12 credits)\n\nRank Requirements:\n- GMU Patriots (Varsity): Masters 5+\n- GMU Academy (JV): Platinum 5+\n\nPlayer Expectations:\n- Must be available 2–4 times/week for practice & matches\n- Clear comms & mic discipline required\n- Must be available for all leagues we participate in\n- Follow player contract guidelines\n- Be ready 15–30 mins before matches\n- Handle schedule conflicts, repeated tardiness = bench/removal\n\nTeam Info:\n- GMU Patriots: Varsity-level, top competitive team aiming for all major events\n- Those who make the Patriots roster will have the opportunity to compete in a George Mason hosted LAN called "The Bloom" in April\n\n- GMU Academy: JV-level, focused on skill growth & competitive development\n\nRegistration Process:\n- Fill out the tryouts sign-up form with rank, role, and experience\n\nTryout Format:\n- Series of inhouse matches where players will scrim against each other\n\nCommitment Notice: \n- Typical matches: Mon @ 7PM\n- Weekends may have tournaments\n\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291782
END:VEVENT
