SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Becker CPA Review: How to Pass the CPA Exam in 2026
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292250
DESCRIPTION:Join Beta Alpha Psi. Ready to conquer the CPA Exam in 2026?\n\nJoin Becker National Instructor and Senior Curriculum Manager, Angelle Cascio, for a practical and motivating session designed to help you pass the CPA Exam with confidence.\n\nIn this webinar, you'll learn:\n- Proven strategies and study tips to prepare efficiently and effectively\n- A walkthrough of Becker's customizable Study Planner\n- How to stay organized, on track, and ready to succeed\n\nThis session will give you the tools and confidence to pass in 2026.\n\nDate: Wednesday, January 21, 2026\nTime: 1:00 PM ET\nLocation: Virtual (Webinar link provided upon registration)\n\nOpen to all majors. Free to attend.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292250
END:VEVENT
