UID:642f7d6f48d7202112ee1dcb1174fc1a162026_10:08:47_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Info Session – Internships in Argentina for Mason Credit
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292089
DESCRIPTION:​Buenos Aires, Argentina holds numerous professional opportunities. To connect students with these, the Global Education Office partners with Road2Argentina to place students in an unpaid semester or summer internship program. Interns gain valuable global work experience and professional skills in various industry fields, Opportunities in the business sector include accounting, advertising and public relations and finance. Additionally, internships are offered in fashion design, allowing students to fully experience the high-fashion culture of the city. Students can choose to live with an Argentinian homestay family or other more independent housing options. The different options provide a fantastic opportunity for cultural and linguistic immersion. \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/91362061753\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292089
END:VEVENT
