URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292095
DESCRIPTION:Start the semester off right at our Welcome Fair! This event is your chance to kick off the new year, make new connections, and set yourself up for an unforgettable semester. Our in-person information fair is designed to introduce you to campus life and connect you with the Mason and Arlington community. Enjoy fun giveaways, learn about student services and resources, and meet representatives from across the Mason community.\n\nAccess, Compliance, and Community\nInternational Programs and Services\nMason Square Library\nMason Student Services Center\nPatriot Pantry\nStudent Support and Advocacy\nThe Graduate Division\nUniversity Life Mason Square\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292095
