DESCRIPTION:Session led by Jana Kosecka, Thema Monroe-White, and Craig Yu\n\nWe're delighted to announce a special year-long, monthly series of workshops on "AI & The Humanities," a partnership between the CHR and CEC. This series seeks to foster cross-disciplinary AI literacy, explore how AI shapes and is shaped by culture, ethics, history, and society, and provide opportunities for research incubation and exchange.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2290928
