DESCRIPTION:Rush is an opportunity at the beginning of each semester to get to know the brothers of our chapter and learn about the goals and objectives of our fraternity. It's a chance for us to demonstrate firsthand the value that this organization can bring to you. Pi Delta Psi Fraternity, Inc. is an Asian-interest, but not exclusively Asian, cultural fraternity that aims to foster academic achievement, cultural awareness, righteousness, and friendship and loyalty. Join us as we present this opportunity to you.\nRequirements for recruitment:\nAttend 2 social events and 1 general interest meeting. Also, please fill out the form in our Instagram bio @gmu.pdpsi\n\nThis event is a general interest meeting for to understand the chapter in more detail.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293662
