DESCRIPTION:The Latter-Day Saints Student Association (LDSSA) presents a weekly institute/bible study. In institute, we will take the time to read & interpret scriptures, such as the Book of Mormon and the Bible, as well as hear & analyze messages from church leaders. We will enjoy Christ-centered fellowship and take time to grow closer to God and Jesus Christ. This event is taught by The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter Day Saints although everyone interested is welcome to attend! We hope to see you there!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293249
