SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:SHPEP Virtual Info Session + Q&A
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293235
DESCRIPTION:Join us virtually as current GMU students and SHPEP ambassadors, Ahmad Tariq Hemat and Kalkidan Negussie, share their experiences with the Summer Health Professions Education Program (SHPEP) at Howard University! SHPEP is a FREE six-week summer enrichment program that prepares college students for a career in the health professions by enhancing their academic proficiency and providing career development opportunities. Summer 2026 will be the final cohort, so don't miss out on applying by February 5th!\n\nFor more details about the Summer Health Professions Education Program (SHPEP), please visit: https://www.shpep.org/\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293235
END:VEVENT
