UID:73906575342a75f0f81b13bf9878290712192025_2:17:24_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Global Internships: Resume & Personal Statement Building
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291985
DESCRIPTION:Have questions about building a strong resume or personal statement for an internship abroad?\nJoin this virtual session hosted by George Mason University Career Services to get tips and guidance on showcasing your skills, knowledge, and experience for your global internship applications.\n\nWhether you’re starting from scratch or refining your materials, this is a great opportunity to ask questions, get feedback, and learn what makes a strong application for opportunities abroad. Feel free to bring your resume and personal statement if you’d like to review them together and receive personalized feedback.\n \nThis is a virtual, drop-in session on Zoom — come by anytime during the scheduled hour!\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/97534387813\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291985
END:VEVENT
