SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Rhode Island vs. Patriots Watch Party 🏀💚💛
LOCATION:Velocity Wings, 10697 Braddock Rd, Fairfax, VA 22032, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293631
DESCRIPTION:Can’t make it to the arena? No problem — we’re bringing the hype to Velocity Wings at University Mall! Come watch the Patriots take on Rhode Island and cheer loudly with your fellow Patriots.\n\nThe watch party kicks off at 1:30 PM, and tip-off is at 2:00 PM. Come early to grab food, claim free spirit gear, and get ready for some serious Patriot Pride.\n\nBring your friends, wear your green and gold, and let’s show everyone how the Patriots do game day! 💚💛\n\n📍 Location: Velocity Wings, University Mall (right across from Fairfax campus)\n🕓 Doors Open: 1:30 PM\n🏀 Tip-Off: 2:00 PM\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293631
END:VEVENT
