SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Handshake Highlight: Summer Internship Search
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292084
DESCRIPTION:It's not too late to find a summer internship. In this 30-minute virtual workshop, we’ll demonstrate the Handshake features most useful in finding paid internships related to your career goals this summer. Handshake can do some of the work for you when you save your searches, “favorite” employers, filter by locations and identify employers that accept international students for CPT.  \n\nZoom to join: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/94084716232 \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/94084716232 \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292084
