SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Summer Study Abroad - Software Engineering in Vienna, Austria (Jan 26 Info session)
LOCATION:Johnson Center Room 241, 4400 University Dr, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293860
DESCRIPTION:This 6-credit study abroad course hosted in Vienna, Austria is designed to provide students with practical experience in software engineering within an international context. Through hands-on projects and real-world scenarios, students will gain a comprehensive understanding of the software development life cycle (SDLC) and develop the necessary skills to work effectively in distributed team environments.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293860
