SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:UndocuMason Game Night
LOCATION:HUB Room 4and5, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292069
DESCRIPTION:The event will focus on spreading awareness of individuals with immigrant backgrounds rights, impact, and history. While also going over the best ways to support this community, and how GMU supports community  individuals. These topics will be discussed in a slide show presentation that will be presented at the start of the event. After which a Jeopardy game show will be played based on the five topics discussed in the presentation. Participants will be divided into groups of 4 with the group with the most points at the end winning. The winning team will be provided a prize for their effort.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292069
END:VEVENT
