SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:An Evening with KPMG: Big Four Careers & Opportunities
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292039
DESCRIPTION:About KPMG: One of the Big Four accounting firms, KPMG operates in 143 countries with over 273,000 professionals worldwide. KPMG's DC Metro practice serves Fortune 500 companies, government agencies, and high-growth organizations, offering opportunities in audit, tax, advisory, and specialized consulting services.\n\nAbout Beta Alpha Psi: The premier international honors organization for financial information students and professionals. BAP provides members with exclusive access to top employers, professional development programming, and a national network of accounting and finance leaders.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292039
