UID:07a4204aca48abe491f677d098b404371222026_1:04:14_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Kicking with Kappas - Pi Delta Psi Fraternity Inc. Rush Event
LOCATION:Hub Meeting Room 2, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293870
DESCRIPTION:This event is a collaborative event with Kappa Phi Lambda Sorority Inc. We will having a game night. \n\nRush is an opportunity at the beginning of each semester to get to know the brothers of our chapter and learn about the goals and objectives of our fraternity. It's a chance for us to demonstrate firsthand the value that this organization can bring to you. Pi Delta Psi Fraternity, Inc. is an Asian-interest, but not exclusively Asian, cultural fraternity that aims to foster academic achievement, cultural awareness, righteousness, and friendship and loyalty. Join us as we present this opportunity to you.\nRequirements for recruitment:\nAttend 2 social events and 1 general interest meeting. Also, please fill out the form in our Instagram bio @gmu.pdpsi\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293870
END:VEVENT
