UID:229eb60ba9cd5be16eacd5e8bafc92f3152026_6:07:43_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:New Year, New Us 
LOCATION:Johnson Center Meeting Room F, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292070
DESCRIPTION:Kick off the semester with a fresh start at our DECA Resolution Crafts social! \n\nJoin us to design custom vision boards tailored to your professional goals while getting the inside scoop on our upcoming competitive season. We'll provide the supplies and a full breakdown of the event calendar, so you can head into competition feeling prepared and inspired. Let's build a stronger DECA presence on campus together, one resolution at a time!\n\nEvent Highlights\n- Vision Board Workshop: Map out your internship, networking, and academic goals for the semester.\n- Competition Deep Dive: Get exclusive information on categories, registration deadlines, and prep sessions.\n- Chapter Growth: Learn how we’re revitalizing DECA on campus and how you can take a leadership role.\n\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292070
END:VEVENT
