UID:671ff3cf4b74dd3f3f2173cd03f5b7721152026_9:09:51_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:2026 CGI Consulting Challenge Information Session
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293117
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever been curious about the consulting industry? \nDo you want an opportunity to expand your critical thinking skills and have a chance to win some cool prizes? \nJoin CGI for an exciting info session to learn more about the CGI Consulting Challenge—a team-based competition where students collaborate to solve a real-world problem affecting their campus. \nWhat’s the Challenge About? \nYou’ll work with up to three peers (teams of up to four students) to develop a creative solution. No prior business or technical experience is required—we’re looking for innovative thinkers from all majors. \nEligibility: \nStudents must be in their: \nFreshman year (Class of 2029) \nSophomore year (Class of 2028) \nJunior year (Class of 2027) \nEach team member must submit an individual application and list their teammates. \nWhy Attend This Info Session? \nLearn how the challenge works and what to expect. \nHear from CGI professionals about consulting careers. \nGet tips on forming a strong team and crafting your solution. \nAsk questions and get guidance before applying. \nReady to apply? \n👉  [Application linked here] \n\nEvent Link: https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_MzE5NzY3NDQtZGNkMi00MDlkLTg3MzMtZDQzMWNjZWMxODY4%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%22b6ed5b7e-5de0-464b-95c0-acbb43267417%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%22466d0bdf-b302-44e9-9844-4c38272eaf91%22%7d\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293117
END:VEVENT
