DESCRIPTION:Come learn about this amazing study abroad program in Granada, Spain. Students engaged in this immersive study abroad experience will take courses at the University of Granada’s Centro de Lenguas Modernas and go on several field trips to other cities in Spain. Students will primarily live in Granada, a small city overflowing with historical and architectural treasures that provides an ideal setting for studying Spanish language and culture.\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/6101383264?pwd=Jsa6aHjaaAfTVKkoereJNqg2x15aCw.1\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293862
