DESCRIPTION:🎉 Student Centers Welcome Back Party at the Corner Pocket 🎉\n\nKick off the semester with an unforgettable night at the Student Centers Welcome Back Party! Join us at the Corner Pocket on Wednesday, January 28, 2026, from 6:00–11:00 PM for a fun-filled evening with friends—new and old.\n\nEnjoy free ice cream, unlimited free gaming, and take the mic at karaoke, plus plenty of other surprises throughout the night. Whether you’re looking to relax, compete, or just vibe, there’s something for everyone.\n\n✨ Free to attend. ✨\n\nStart the semester right—we’ll see you there! 🎮🎤🍦\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292042
