LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291855
DESCRIPTION:Kick off the semester strong with a night dedicated to leveling up your study skills!\nJoin the SYZters of Sigma Psi Zeta Sorority, Inc. as we share our favorite tips, tricks, and academic hacks from majors across the board! From Forensic Science to Theater, and everything in between. Whether you’re looking to get organized, study smarter, or simply start the semester on the right foot, this event is the perfect boost to your study skills!\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/96995476641?pwd=datN9MSPva3OlIcvEr82t4t8z3okgX.1\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291855
