SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:KPL Rush Day 3 - Alluring Encounter
LOCATION:Johnson Center 239A, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292503
DESCRIPTION:The Alpha Alpha Chapter of Kappa Phi Lambda Sorority, Inc. presents Spring 2026 Alpha Iota Class Rush\n\nDay 3 will be our General Interest Meeting (GIM) with a movie after!\n\nIn order to qualify for an interview, you must attend one General Interest Meeting (GIM) AND two other events. All Rush events are non-binding and always free! If you have any questions or concerns, please DM us through Instagram @gmukpl or contact our Spring 2026 Rush Chairs (contact info below). We are so excited to meet you at our events!\n\nSpring 2026 Rush Chairs\nJoy Kim *KORAT* | IG: @joyjkim_\nChristina Mackliet *LOVE DIVE* | IG: @christina_mackliet\nLou Nguyen *VERDYRA* | IG: @juminahans\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292503
