UID:3a5866399f26d1b1eb22e3cfb8bdebe11232026_10:48:30_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Spring Preview #1 - Bachata and Zouk + Social Dancing
LOCATION:HUB Ballroom Middle and Back, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293982
DESCRIPTION:Whether you've taken classes with us before or not, start the Azúcar semester off right with some short classes on the basics of Bachata and Zouk before dancing and chatting with your classmates after class at the social. No partner or experience needed, these previews are meant to give you a taste of what the dances we teach are and help you decide which classes you want to try this semester. \n \nZouk and Bachata will be on Tuesday and Wednesday nights this semester, with classes being 7:00 to 9:00. Classes start the first week of February and have socials afterwards. We offer at least 2 levels for each dance style we teach, with the level 1 classes being designed for people with little or no dance experience.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293982
END:VEVENT
