SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Get Connected Fair [Student Org & Club Fair]
LOCATION:Lower Level of the Johnson Center: Dewberry Hall, Dewberry Lobby, Gold Room, and JC Cinema Lobby, The HUB, Fairfax, 
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2283188
DESCRIPTION:Inclement Weather Date Change!\n\nDiscover the incredible opportunity to get involved at George Mason University! \nStudent Involvement is hosting RSOs as they engage with students at their table in the vibrant lower level of the Johnson Center at Fairfax. Don’t miss your chance to connect, make friends, and be part of something bigger—your campus community is waiting for YOU!\n\nCheck-in at the Info Table to receive a free tote bag!\n\nAre you an RSO, Club Sport, or FSL Group? Sign up for a table! https://cglink.me/2d7/s96276\n\nMore information (list of groups, map, etc): https://si.gmu.edu/get-connected-fair/\n\n\nWeather Forecast Update\n1/26/26: Due to inclement weather, this event has been postponed from Tuesday and is now being held on Thursday, January 29. Updates are being shared VIA the website and Mason360. Groups tabling will also be sent an email with details.\n\n1/28/26: Fair will continue as scheduled!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2283188
END:VEVENT
