DESCRIPTION:Part of Homecoming Team Competition. Each year, registered teams paint a school spirit banner which represents our Patriot pride! It can be a way to showcase your team and who makes it up, it can be a depiction of the basketball teams that will be competing, or anything that is a positive representation of Mason!\n\nBanners due to Student Involvement (HUB 2300) by 12pm (noon) on Friday, January 23, 2026.\n\nRules and more information available on page 6 of the Team Comp. Packet available at https://homecoming.gmu.edu/team-competition-updates/\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291845
