UID:007dba10b762376f1d169a26e7f45481152026_11:42:16_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Homecoming Rally at the Court 
LOCATION:Fairfax Campus: Johnson Center Atrium, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292044
DESCRIPTION:🏀 Homecoming Rally at the Court 🏀\nThursday, January 29, 2026 | 12:00 PM - 2:00 PM\nJohnson Center Atrium\nGet ready to kick off Homecoming Week in style! Join us for an unforgettable lunchtime rally as we celebrate the spirit, pride, and energy that make George Mason University so special! Whether you're a freshman or a senior, this event is the perfect way to get hyped for the week ahead.\n\nHere’s what’s going down at the Homecoming Rally at the Court:\n🎶 Live Music from The Green Machine – Feel the beat and vibe to the sounds of George Mason’s very own marching band!\n🎤 Performances by the Masonette's & GMU Cheer Team – Watch our talented dancers and cheerleaders bring the energy to life!\n🏀 Appearances from the Basketball Team – Get up close and personal with your favorite players before they hit the court!\n🎨 Homecoming Banner Voting – Cast your vote for the official Homecoming banner – your voice matters!\n👗 Bookstore Fashion Show – Check out the latest George Mason gear and school spirit wear in a fashion show you won’t want to miss!\n…and more surprises in store!\nThis is the perfect opportunity to meet new friends, show off your George Mason pride, and start the countdown to an epic Homecoming Week! \nDon’t miss it – see you there! 💚\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292044
END:VEVENT
