SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:KPL Rush Day 4 - Helping Hands
LOCATION:Online, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292505
DESCRIPTION:The Alpha Alpha Chapter of Kappa Phi Lambda Sorority, Inc. presents Spring 2026 Alpha Iota Class Rush\n\nDay 4 will be a community service event where we will be writing cards for the elderly!\n\nIn order to qualify for an interview, you must attend one General Interest Meeting (GIM) AND one other event. All Rush events are non-binding and always free! If you have any questions or concerns, please DM us through Instagram @gmukpl or contact our Spring 2026 Rush Chairs (contact info below). We are so excited to meet you at our events!\n\nSpring 2026 Rush Chairs\nJoy Kim *KORAT* | IG: @joyjkim_\nChristina Mackliet *LOVE DIVE* | IG: @christina_mackliet\nLou Nguyen *VERDYRA* | IG: @juminahans\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292505
