SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Continental Clash - Pi Delta Psi Fraternity Inc. Rush Event
LOCATION:RAC, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293970
DESCRIPTION:This event will feature a sports day at the RAC.\n\nRush is an opportunity at the beginning of each semester to get to know the brothers of our chapter and learn about the goals and objectives of our fraternity. It's a chance for us to demonstrate firsthand the value that this organization can bring to you. Pi Delta Psi Fraternity, Inc. is an Asian-interest, but not exclusively Asian, cultural fraternity that aims to foster academic achievement, cultural awareness, righteousness, and friendship and loyalty. Join us as we present this opportunity to you.\nRequirements for recruitment:\nAttend 2 social events and 1 general interest meeting. Also, please fill out the form in our Instagram bio @gmu.pdpsi\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293970
END:VEVENT
