UID:ff573aded5d654df9c69367391339a6b1232026_11:04:45_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Spring Preview #2 - Cuban Casino and Rueda (Miami Salsa) + Social Dancing
LOCATION:Johnson Center Dewberry South, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293986
DESCRIPTION:Whether you've taken classes with us before or not, start the Azúcar semester off right with some short classes on the basics of Casino and Rueda de Casino (Miami Salsa) before an opportunity to dance and chat with your classmates after class at the social. No partner or experience needed, these previews are meant to give you a taste of what the dances we teach are and help you decide which classes you want to try this semester. \n\nCasino and Rueda will be on Monday and Thursday nights this semester, with class being from 7:30 to 9:30 (Casino) or 7:00 to 9:00 (Rueda). Classes start the first week of February and have socials afterwards. We offer at least 2 levels of class for each genre and the level 1 classes are designed for people with little or no dance experience.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293986
END:VEVENT
