SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Cutlural art night 
LOCATION:HUB ROOM 4 , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292003
DESCRIPTION:Join the World Cultural Student Association (WCSA) for a relaxing and creative Art Night at George Mason University! This event is a space for students to unwind, express themselves, and connect through art. Whether you love painting, drawing, crafting, or just trying something new, all skill levels are welcome. Supplies will be provided, and attendees can enjoy a laid-back atmosphere filled with creativity, culture, and community. Come create, socialize, and take home your own piece of art!\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292003
