DESCRIPTION:Join us Saturday, January 31 at 5 p.m. in the RAC as the Patriots take on Ball State! Students, come out to honor our military with colors presented by ROTC and show your Patriot pride.\n\nNote: The Patriots also will play UMES at 2 p.m. This ticket is good for both matches! The hats will be given out at the 5 p.m. match. \n\nStudents can grab a camo hat giveaway while supplies last—pick up your vouchers when doors open, and hats will be distributed after the third set. Don’t miss your chance to cheer on Mason volleyball and snag some exclusive gear!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2289570
