DESCRIPTION:Get your student tickets right here on Mason360! DO NOT PRINT your ticket, we are a paperless venue, and WILL NOT accept printed tickets. Make sure you have the Mason360 app downloaded with your tickets accessible via mobile device!\n\nHave your QR code ready, present your QR code to the tablet, and you're good to go!\n\nTo find your ticket easier: In the events tab of the Mason360 app, click on the filter button in the top right, filter by group, select "Mason Athletics", apply the filter, and select the game you wish to register for!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2289550
