UID:31d122b5865b1c1f5b819ee676e3b1511222026_1:56:53_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:MIX Innovators Launchpad Spring 2026 Cohort (APPLY ON WEBSITE BY JANUARY 30TH)
LOCATION:Horizon Hall 2100, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293922
DESCRIPTION:First-time founders eager to launch their business ideas now have access to a valuable resource on campus: the MIX Student Innovators Launchpad.\nThis program supports student entrepreneurs aiming to establish and expand their business ventures. Participants will gain a working knowledge of how to evaluate their innovative ideas from both business and customer perspectives, along with essential skills in conducting customer discovery interviews—the crucial first step in any commercialization process.\nThis course equips attendees with entrepreneurial skills and insights applicable across various career paths. \nThe workshop series is integrated with the NSF Regional I-Corps program.\n\nApply for the Spring 2026 Cohort by January 30th!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293922
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
