URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291857
DESCRIPTION:With the semester taking off, it’s the perfect time to get organized and stay ahead! Join the SYZters of Sigma Psi Zeta Sorority, Inc. for a night dedicated to planning your study schedule and learning practical time-management tips and tricks. Hear from SYZters who juggle classes, jobs, leadership roles, and still make time for fun — because we’re all about work hard, play hard. Come build a schedule that works for you and start your semester feeling confident, balanced, and supported!\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291857
