URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293104
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to celebrate and connect at this high-energy kickoff event, which launches our Black History/Heritage Month and Homecoming celebrations with joy, culture, and community at the center. Join us for an unforgettable experience filled with vibrant traditions, powerful moments, and plenty of school spirit. From honoring the past and present to reuniting alumni and welcoming new memories, this event sets the tone for a month of reflection, celebration, and homecoming fun. Come ready to celebrate our history, our heritage, and our home—together!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293104
