SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Grounds for Change: Coffee & DIY Body Scrub Workshop
LOCATION:Southside, 1st Floor, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294213
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a cup of fair-trade coffee while creating your own coffee body scrub using reclaimed grounds from campus coffee vendors. This hands-on workshop shows how simple, everyday actions can reduce waste and support a more sustainable campus.\n\nCome relax, get creative, and learn how turning something small into something useful can make a meaningful environmental impact.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294213
END:VEVENT
