UID:33f7979eca4f554ad7b1f1c993c167a6172026_3:30:03_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Resume: Basics & Formatting Workshop feat. Deloitte
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292203
DESCRIPTION:Join us for this interactive virtual workshop featuring Megan Farina, Specialist Leader, Cyber and Strategic Risk with Deloitte (and GMU alum). \n\nIn this hands-on session, our expert career advisors will guide you through the foundational elements of creating a polished, professional resume. You’ll learn how to structure your resume for maximum impact, choose the right format for your career goals, and ensure your document is visually appealing and easy to read.\n\nKey Takeaways:\n-Understand the essential components of a strong resume layout.\n-Learn formatting best practices to make your resume stand out.\n-Discover how to organize sections for clarity and professionalism.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292203
END:VEVENT
