UID:999dc65030315d6e032cbbab383e68891232026_1:29:42_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Scrap-zining
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294114
DESCRIPTION:Start your new year off right and come to Craft Club's first event of the year: Scrap-zining! We will be creating scrapbook spreads, zines, and journal pages on our goals for 2026, reflecting on 2025, or whatever else you feel inspired to create! \n\nWhether have never crafted before, you're an expert, or anything in between please come join us! If you've never been to a craft club meeting before this is a great opportunity to meet other club members, officers, and get a feel for the club! \n\nSupplies like decorative paper, markers, stickers, tape, glue, and scissors will be provided but if you have them, we encourage you to bring any journals or books you'd like to use, any scrap materials you have at home, and anything you'd like to share with other crafters (like stickers, stamps, and washi tape)! It's a great way to give new life to materials that might otherwise go unused while connecting with fellow crafters in a welcoming, creative environment.\n\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294114
END:VEVENT
