SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:An Evening with PwC: Big Four Careers & Pathways
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292040
DESCRIPTION:About PwC: PricewaterhouseCoopers (PwC) is one of the Big Four accounting firms and the second-largest professional services network in the world. PwC provides assurance, tax, consulting, and advisory services to clients ranging from Fortune 500 companies to government agencies and emerging businesses. PwC's DC Metro practice offers diverse career opportunities across multiple service lines.\n\nAbout Beta Alpha Psi: The premier international honors organization for financial information students and professionals. BAP provides members with exclusive access to top employers, professional development programming, and a national network of accounting and finance leaders.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292040
END:VEVENT
