UID:abb0c16bc617d225debc9290723ad034192026_1:18:34_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Becker CPA Review: AUD Deep Dive — SSARS Engagements Workshop
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292251
DESCRIPTION:Join Beta Alpha Psi. Master one of the most challenging areas of the CPA Exam!\n\nJoin Becker National Instructor Michelle Moshe for a free, live 60-90 minute workshop diving deep into SSARS engagements — one of the most critical topics on the Auditing and Attestation (AUD) Exam.\n\nIn this workshop, you'll get:\n- Comprehensive concept review of SSARS engagements\n- Real-world examples to reinforce understanding\n- Practice questions to test your knowledge\n- Live Q&A to get your questions answered in real-time\n\nThis session is ideal for learners who could use a different perspective or additional practice with challenging AUD topics.\n\nDate: Tuesday, February 3, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM ET\nDuration: 60-90 minutes\nLocation: Virtual (Webinar link provided upon registration)\n\nOpen to all majors. Free to attend.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292251
END:VEVENT
