LOCATION:Spiritual and Interfaith Center (Fenwick A), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291883
DESCRIPTION:Start the new year with intention, warmth, and connection at our Spring into Well-Being kickoff event!\nThis cozy café-style gathering invites you to pause, reflect, and refill your cup—literally and figuratively.\nCo-hosted by the Center for the Advancement of Well-Being (CWB), the Center for Leadership and Intercultural Engagement, and the Office of Access, Compliance & Community, this event offers a welcoming space for the Mason community, including students, faculty, and staff.\n\nREGISTER HERE: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/grounded-in-kindness-tickets-1977402785963?utm-campaign=social&utm-content=attendeeshare&utm-medium=discovery&utm-term=listing&utm-source=cp&aff=ebdsshcopyurl\n\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291883
