DESCRIPTION:The Office of International Programs and Services (OIPS) and INTO Mason welcome you to a night filled with food and fun. Join us at the Johnson Center Cinema on Wednesday, February 04, 2026, at 5:30 PM for pizza and games before heading over to EagleBank Arena at 6:30 PM to watch the George Mason Patriots defeat the Duquesne University Dukes men's basketball team. Attendees will have the opportunity to go to the basketball court and take photos afterward.\n\nA George Mason Basketball T-Shirt will be given out to the first 100 attendees of the game!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293093
