SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Sexual Assault Awareness: Consent, Respect, Connect
LOCATION:JC Room A, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293236
DESCRIPTION:Sexual Assault Awareness: Consent, Respect, Connect is an impactful event centered on fostering a safer, more informed community. The program focused on understanding consent, promoting mutual respect, and strengthening connections among individuals. Through open discussion and guided conversation, participants explored what consent truly means, how to recognize and challenge harmful behaviors, and ways to support survivors and one another. This event emphasized accountability, empathy, and empowerment, encouraging attendees to actively contribute to a culture rooted in respect and care.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293236
END:VEVENT
