UID:2b84579c2866c07f9634c30c326db9c31122026_6:05:21_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Unpacking Conflict: Sports
LOCATION:Johnson Center Meeting Room D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292443
DESCRIPTION:In-Person: JC Meeting Room D | Online: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/92205296648\n\nSports: Where Competition Meets Real-World Conflict\nIn this brown bag session, our panel will break down a range of sport conflicts that keep stadiums loud, college athletes paid, and influence international politics. From controversial calls on the field, NIL deals in collegiate athletics, and sport providing diplomacy - come discuss why people are so emotional for sports—and how conflict plays out on and off the field. Pack a lunch or grab some in the JC main level, and come join us in this energizing and engaging conversation before two of sports biggest events: the Olympics and the Super Bowl. \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/92205296648\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292443
END:VEVENT
