UID:5c669c22772c539452e36844f4474c9d12182025_10:35:52_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Faith/Spiritual Conversations with Cliffe and Stuart Knechtle
LOCATION:HUB Ballroom, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291982
DESCRIPTION:Come see Cliffe and Stuart Knechtle answer questions and have intellectual, open-minded discussions with students about who Jesus is, and what Christianity is really all about! Whether you want to stay for five minutes, or five hours, everyone is welcome to stop by and see them, ask them questions, and listen to their responses to difficult questions about life, meaning, and purpose!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291982
