SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Education Careers Week: Careers in EdTech
LOCATION:SUB 1 3400 Resource Room, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291842
DESCRIPTION:Is a career in educational technology right for you? Join us to learn how new careers in education and research are transforming the way we teach and learn. E-Learning developers, instructional designers, and training specialists are in high demand in the Ed Tech industry. This event will bring together professionals working in this field to share insights into the fast-growing educational technology sector. \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/99553542158\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291842
