UID:4c9ec138b7dc4e1e4e202dd11c9c43fc252026_3:29:17_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Chinese Brush Painting Club
LOCATION:Horizon Hall, Room 5008, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295247
DESCRIPTION:Learn the art of Chinese brush painting from an experienced instructor. Open to all skill levels, and all supplies are provided. \n\nPlease register for the class on Mason 360 in order to secure a seat in the classroom.\nPlease arrive to class on time so that the flow of class is not interrupted while the instructor is teaching.\nIt is recommended that participants wear dark clothing or clothes they do not mind getting ink on as the ink used in class is permanent and can stain clothing.\nIf you cannot make it to the class, please cancel your registration by going to "Events I'm Attending", clicking "Registration", and "Cancel My Registration."\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295247
END:VEVENT
