DESCRIPTION:Meet the Dons is an engaging and interactive event designed to give attendees the opportunity to connect with fraternity brothers in a relaxed and welcoming environment. Throughout the event, participants will interact with the Dons through icebreakers, team-based games, and friendly competitions that encourage conversation, collaboration, and fun.\n\nThe event provides an inside look into the fraternity’s brotherhood, values, and culture while creating a comfortable space for attendees to ask questions and build genuine connections. Whether someone is interested in learning more about fraternity life or simply looking to meet new people, Meet the Dons offers an inclusive and energetic atmosphere.\n\nAttendees can expect an evening filled with laughter, friendly competition, and meaningful interactions, leaving them with a better understanding of the fraternity and the community behind the Dons.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293112
END:VEVENT
