UID:7a64f86a3798fc0696832b6934ee0bfd1212026_3:57:25_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Create Your Own: RSO VISION BOARD at Free Play Friday
LOCATION:The Hub, 2nd Floor Side Pocket, The HUB, Fairfax, 
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293693
DESCRIPTION:Kick off February with creativity and inspiration! Join the RSO Lead Team for a special RSO Leadership Lounge where you’ll craft your very own club's Vision Board—a perfect way to set goals, spark ideas, and dream big for your organization.\n\n📍 Side Pocket @ The HUB\n🕕 Friday, February 6 | 6–7:30 PM\n\nHere’s what’s waiting for you:\n\n✂️ Vision board supplies (magazines, stickers, markers & more!)\n🖼️ Guided prompts to help your org set goals for spring semester\n🍕 Free pizza & sodas to keep the creativity flowing\n🤝 Connect with other RSO leaders & share your organization’s goals\n🎱 Stop in the Corner Pocket for free fun and games\n\nWhether you’re looking to refresh your mission, map out spring plans, or just enjoy a relaxing night of crafting, this is your chance to create something meaningful for your org.\n\nBring your e-board, grab a slice, and envision your next big chapter!\n\nCurious about Free Play Friday? Read more here, hosted by Student Involvement and Student Centers: https://cglink.me/2d7/r2294325 \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293693
END:VEVENT
