UID:3175895d57dc80ff6028f54e4facee381262026_12:12:41_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Free Play Friday 
LOCATION:The Hub: Corner Pocket , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294325
DESCRIPTION:Free Play Friday is back at the Corner Pocket! 🎉 Sponsored by Student Involvement, this is your chance to kick off the weekend with FREE PLAY on every game— no limits. Swing by from 6–11 PM, bring your friends, and challenge them to pool, arcade games, and more. Whether you’re taking a break from studying or just looking for something fun to do on campus, Free Play Friday is the move. Come early, stay late, and play for free!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294325
