UID:69014364645dcc43bb20c4db595d761c1202026_1:37:44_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:The Art of Us: Voices and Creative Expressions of Sudanese People
LOCATION:Johnson Center, Bistro, Fairfax Campus, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293452
DESCRIPTION:Upcoming art gallery titled "The Art of Us: Voices and Creative Expressions of Sudanese People".\n\nThe event will bring together a variety of art forms from visual art and photography to design, fashion, film, writing, and performance, all centered around Sudanese creativity and identity. This event will emphasize how essential art has been in shaping and reflecting recent shifts in Sudanese culture.\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293452
END:VEVENT
