SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AMA Interest Meeting 
LOCATION:JC Room 239 A, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294426
DESCRIPTION:Join the American Marketing Association at GMU for their Spring Interest Meeting, discussing  building marketing skills, expanding your network, and exploring how marketing experience can build credibility in any discipline. AMA is the world’s largest marketing association, giving students space to experiment, learn, and gain career-ready experience. \n\nWhat we’ll cover:\n- Career Benefits: Toolkits, workshops, job board, competitions \n- Creative Pathways: Disciplines optimized for marketing creativity \n- Opportunities: ICC, PCM certification discounts, AMA DC Socials\n- AMA’s national network: 29,000+ members and 320+ collegiate chapters \n\nWe look forward to seeing you. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294426
END:VEVENT
