SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Clearance Ready: Finding Your First Cleared Job
LOCATION:Merten Hall 1202, Fairfax Campus, 4441 George Mason Blvd University Hall, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291742
DESCRIPTION:Finding your first job or internship can be challenging. Entering into the cleared community adds another element to your search process. Hear from recruiters and professionals offering tips and best practices about how you can land your first role that requires a clearance. Come prepared to ask questions and learn what to do, and just as important, what not to do. This workshop is part of the Clearance Ready Program.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291742
