DESCRIPTION:Interested in law school!? Need to study for the LSAT? Want to learn more about the group? Come to BLSA’S FIRST meeting, Pizza & Prep, TUESDAY, FEBRUARY 10th. Here, you’ll meet the executive board, learn about the parts of the lsat, get more information on the mentorship program, and network with other prelaw students of color. Be sure to bring a friend! We can’t wait to see you there!🎊👩🏾‍⚖️🧑🏾‍⚖️\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295537
