LOCATION:HUB Ballroom Front, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291998
DESCRIPTION:Join HLLA for a welcoming and engaging event where upperclassmen leaders share their experiences, tips, and guidance with first-year and transfer students! This event creates a space to build connections, learn about campus life, and feel more prepared as you navigate your first year.  No matter how you’re starting your Mason journey, this is your chance to hear from students who’ve been in your shoes and begin building your community at Mason.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291998
