UID:388f2f5de61de4d9f1caa81a18be25661272026_11:35:12_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:DECA Market Your Mission
LOCATION:JC Room B, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294527
DESCRIPTION:You know where you want to go, but do you know how to articulate your "Why"? Join Collegiate DECA for an immersive workshop dedicated to building a personal brand that resonates.\n\nIn today’s professional landscape, a resume is just a piece of paper—it’s your personal mission statement and unique value proposition that set you apart. This session is designed to help you dig deep and define your professional identity.\n\nWhat we’ll cover:\n\nCrafting Your Mission: Learn how to write a powerful personal mission statement that guides your career decisions and tells your story.\n\nThe Art of Branding: Discover how to align your values with your professional goals to create a consistent, authentic brand.\n\nThe "Me" Pitch: Practice conveying your mission statement through a refined elevator pitch that focuses on your purpose and impact.\n\nNetworking with Intent: Connect with fellow students to share your vision and get immediate feedback in a supportive environment.\n\nDon't just apply for jobs—show up with a purpose. Join us and start building a brand that truly represents who you are.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294527
END:VEVENT
