UID:e387b711f0c0b4b0cb891d8078b341db222026_2:25:41_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Work Visa Options for International Students Attorney Webinar 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294943
DESCRIPTION:US employers and international students are often confused about the work visa options available to allow graduates of US universities to stay and work in the US.  In this webinar, immigration attorney Mark Rhoads will provide a summary of the most common work visa options, including F-1 OPT and H1B.  He will discuss the costs and timing of work visa processing, as well as the H1B quota and the H1B "lottery."  There will be plenty of time for questions and answers. \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/92582645873\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294943
END:VEVENT
