UID:4b100097c0788419d61c3cb45714d2b812172025_12:28:00_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:More than a Moment: Rooted & Restored
LOCATION:JC Georges, 4469 Aquia Creek Ln, Student Union Building 1, Suite 2400, MSN 2F6, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291941
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Thursday, February 12th for More than A Moment “Rooted and Restored”. Support yourself in black wellness and learn what herbs are beneficial to college students.\n\nAn extension of our Global Roots Calendar and the second iteration of CLIE’s More than a Moment series, invites students to an apothecary workshop, learning and leaving with various remedies, teas, and wellness techniques that are much needed as a college student. \n\nIn collaboration with Dynamic Wellness, a Black-owned community centered health and wellness boutique in  in Washington D.C, join CLIE and the Black Alumni Chapter as we dive into making health and wellness simple, fun, and rooted in the cultural and ancestral practices that can help us get right!\n\nNo need to stay the entirety of the event!\n\nLets sip and talk, we’d love to see you there \n📅 Date: Thursday, February 12th\n🕛 Time: 4:30 PM – 7:30 PM\n📍 Location: JC George’s\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291941
END:VEVENT
