DESCRIPTION:Join us for a job search workshop tailored for Costello College of Business students!\nEmbarking on a job search can present unique challenges and opportunities, especially for those studying in the U.S. on a visa and those interested in exploring job opportunities outside the United States. We’ll provide essential guidance and resources to help you successfully navigate both the U.S. and global job markets with confidence.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292155
