UID:52aeafe5d0d5985ad3d3324689508c54172026_1:14:47_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Personal Branding for International Students Workshop
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292156
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Personal Branding for International Students, tailored for Costello College of Business students. Your personal brand is more than just a resume or LinkedIn profile—it’s how you present your unique strengths, values, and story to the professional world. Building a strong, authentic personal brand can set you apart in a competitive job market and help you make a lasting impression on employers. \n\nThis workshop is designed to help you reflect on how you want to be perceived, align your brand with your goals, and communicate it consistently across professional settings. Whether you’re job searching, networking, or growing your presence online, this session will help you better understand what makes your brand memorable—and how to share it with confidence. \n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n\nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292156
END:VEVENT
