UID:f35f570d03c6a13e44c455d5a131e66a1262026_2:31:42_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Arabic Language in Fes - Summer 2026 Study Abroad 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294345
DESCRIPTION:Come learn about this amazing study abroad opportunity in Morocco. This 8-week summer program offers a fully immersive experience, including Arabic language classes, several trips to other cities in Morocco, and cultural workshops on Moroccan cuisine, Islamic calligraphy, and traditional crafts. The program provides constant and exclusive use of Arabic language in the classroom and offers students the opportunity to practice outside of the classroom with the residents of the city. Through our partner the Ibn Ghazi Arabic Institute in Fes (http://www.igai-fez.com/), students will also have the opportunity to pursue the International Certificate for Arabic Language Proficiency (CIMA). Developed by the Arab World Institute, CIMA is the first global certification of its kind, offering a rigorous and internationally recognized assessment of Arabic language proficiency across all levels.\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/6101383264?pwd=Jsa6aHjaaAfTVKkoereJNqg2x15aCw.1\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294345
END:VEVENT
