UID:925c592a21bf999cd72ed498cfc24de41122026_12:21:51_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:2026 Lunar New Year Celebration
LOCATION:Johnson Center Bistro, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292397
DESCRIPTION:Lunar New Year (LNY) is one of the most important holidays in many countries and regions in Asia. Come join us to learn about the cultures and traditions during LNY in different cultural contexts and see how people celebrate it! \n\nEnjoy traditional LNY snacks and drinks and join us with paper cutting, calligraphy, games, and more! Get your Hong Bao (red envelope) and meet new friends! Let's celebrate the Year of the Horse!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292397
END:VEVENT
