SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Vacuum Forming Basics
LOCATION:Horizon Hall 1408 (The MIX), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294706
DESCRIPTION:Learn the basics of vacuum forming, a fast and effective method for shaping plastic sheets into custom designs. In this hands-on workshop, participants will discover how to prepare molds, set up and safely operate the vacuum forming machine at the MIX, and create their own formed parts. Perfect for beginners interested in prototyping, packaging, or model making. No prior experience required.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294706
