SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Workshop to Prepare for the Fair
LOCATION:Student Union Building 1, Room3B, Fairfax Campus, 4400 University Drive, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291573
DESCRIPTION:\nWant to be your best at Mason's biggest career fair? We can help! In this workshop, you will learn how prepare for the Career Fair and get the most out of attending it. Learn to:\n\n1. Create a strategy for being successful at the fair\n\n2. Introduce yourself to employers\n\n3. Follow up to make a lasting impression\n\nThis is your chance to develop and practice your personal pitch. Our strategies for marketing your skills will not only impress employers at the fair but will also help you feel confident during your interview.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291573
END:VEVENT
