UID:053e14a46b1451ada3c01e977c6e789b262026_9:48:58_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:ICN Spring Stromer Guest Speaker Event
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295381
DESCRIPTION:     ICN welcomes back TiArre Stromer for a chat on how students can best prepare themselves for a career in all-source intelligence analysis and operational leadership. Learn about what it is like to work for the Office of the Director of National Intelligence (ODNI), and how interagency coordination helps keep our country safe.\n\nStromer has more than 25 years of service to our country through her time in the Army to when she served as Deputy National Intelligence Manager for Narcotics and Transnational Crime within the ODNI. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295381
END:VEVENT
