SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:SHAHI & VINYLS
LOCATION:JC BISTRO, 4400 University Dr, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294618
DESCRIPTION:SHAHI & VINYLS invites you to step into Libya for the night and experience its culture through sound, taste, and tradition. This immersive evening blends live vintage vinyl sets with Libyan tea, a Libyan-Algerian fusion matcha menu, and a Polaroid photo booth corner to capture the moment. Guests can also receive traditional Libyan henna and learn more about Libyan culture in a relaxed, welcoming space. Come as you are and let the music, flavors, and atmosphere transport you.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294618
END:VEVENT
