DESCRIPTION:The Association of Latino Professionals for America (ALPFA) invites you to a Resume Workshop designed to help you stand out in today’s competitive job market. Participants will receive practical tips, expert feedback, and guidance on crafting a strong, professional resume that highlights skills, experience, and career goals. Whether you’re refining an existing resume or starting from scratch, this workshop will help you put your best foot forward.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294524
