UID:ff8671da906eb2dd9f9a7f71725b48d9162026_12:12:48_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mason Intentional Kindness Day: Screen-Free Self-Care
LOCATION:Johnson Center, Kiosk B, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292096
DESCRIPTION:Unplug for you! Celebrate Mason Intentional Kindness Day & Spring into Well-Being by stepping away from your screens and giving yourself the gift of presence through screen-free self-care.\n\nChoose intentional time to disconnect from devices and reconnect with what matters most, your well-being. Use this pause to recharge, reflect, and plan simple, screen-free activities that nurture your mind and body. It’s an act of kindness for yourself!\n\nREGISTER HERE: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/1979883498842?aff=oddtdtcreator\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292096
END:VEVENT
