UID:41f31c9b7566bd301d289a2d6ce1d388182026_12:17:56_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Design Your Future Workforce Look: Clothing Pop-Up & Professional Headshots
LOCATION:JC Meeting Room C, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292216
DESCRIPTION:Get career-ready with confidence! As part of Innovation Week and in celebration of the University’s Spring STEM Career Fair, CEC-OSSE is hosting a Professional Clothing Pop-Up and Free Headshots Event to help you put your best foot forward.\n\nBrowse our Professional Clothing Closet and select FREE professional attire to support your career journey-perfect for interviews, networking, and face-to-face conversations with industry professionals. From classy blazers to polished accessories, we’ve got you covered with styles that help you feel prepared and confident.\n\nWe’re also offering complimentary professional headshots, so you can elevate your LinkedIn, Handshake, and professional profiles with a high-quality photo that reflects your best professional self.\n\n⭐ What to Expect:\nFree professional clothing for STEM students\nProfessional headshots\nSupportive, welcoming environment\nFirst come, first served while supplies last\n\nWhether you’re gearing up for the career fair, upcoming interviews, or planning your professional future, this is your chance to present, engage, and shine. We’re here to help you make a strong and confident impression!\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292216
END:VEVENT
