UID:0cad46f36cd6d47f490a11bac379946e1212026_8:41:39_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Funding Your Study Abroad Experience
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293630
DESCRIPTION:The Global Education Office, Fellowships, and Financial Aid Office will host this joint virtual info session on multiple sources to fund international programs. \n\nThere are many options available including the Gilman Scholarship for Pell Grant recipients, federal financial aid, GEO scholarships, global fellowships, and more. Learn how to make your global goals a reality through these great resources!\n\nTo learn more about these offices and opportunities, visit:\n\nGlobal Education Office Scholarships: https://studyabroad.gmu.edu/how/explore/index.html#scholarships\n\nFinancial Aid: https://www.gmu.edu/financial-aid\n\nFellowships Office: https://provost.gmu.edu/students/fellowships\n\nBenjamin A. Gilman International Scholarship: https://www.gilmanscholarship.org/\n\n\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/92250872499?pwd=qw1lnaZsTSl5djEeNP2sXffcjG0fwm.1\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293630
END:VEVENT
