SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Shrinky-Dink Charm Workshop
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294198
DESCRIPTION:Live life on the tiny side and join Craft Club for a Shrinky-dink workshop! Craft club members will lead you through how design, heat and shrink, and attach your charms to keychains, pin backs, or make them into phone charms!\n\nMaterials will be provided but feel free to bring any supplies you'd like to use for this project and anything you'd like to share with other crafters! It's a great way to give new life to materials that might otherwise go unused while connecting with fellow crafters in a welcoming, creative environment.\n\nWhether you've never crafted before, you're an expert, or anything in between, please come join us! Everyone is welcome even if you've never been to a craft club meeting before!\n\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294198
END:VEVENT
