SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:From Our Hearts to Theirs 
LOCATION:Johnson Center, 337, Meeting Room G, Fairfax Campus, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293753
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a meaningful Valentine’s Day service event dedicated to supporting families staying at Ronald McDonald House Fairfax while their children receive medical care. Handwritten Valentine’s cards filled with uplifting messages of strength and hope. Origami heart bookmarks paired with inspiring quotes for moments of quiet reflection. Comfort care packages with small but thoughtful essentials parents truly need. Every item made will be donated directly to families at Ronald McDonald House, turning creativity into compassion and care into action.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293753
END:VEVENT
