SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Real Chisme: Toxic Relationships
LOCATION:JC Room G, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294763
DESCRIPTION:An open and honest discussion that creates space for students to talk about toxic relationships in a supportive, judgment-free environment. This event encourages authentic dialogue around recognizing unhealthy patterns, setting boundaries, and understanding the emotional impact toxic relationships can have on personal growth and well-being. Through guided conversation and shared experiences, attendees will gain tools to reflect, learn, and empower themselves to build healthier relationships—while engaging in real conversations that center community, culture, and healing.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294763
