SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Cousin's Corner: Protecting Our Peace
LOCATION:SUB 1 3B, 4469 Aquia Creek Ln, Student Union Building 1, Suite 2400, MSN 2F6, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291943
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our first Cousin's Corner of the semester. Cousin's Corner is a dialogues across difference series hosted by CLIE that invites students to discuss a topic in an intimate, low-stakes environment. This session focuses on prioritizing the self without guilt, exploring how to set boundaries in friendships, family, school, and community, and how rest is part of reclaiming our power.  \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291943
END:VEVENT
