SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:GMU UNICEF Youth in Action
LOCATION:JC Meeting Room F, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294561
DESCRIPTION:For this General Body Meeting, UNICEF club members will be divided into "Emergency Response Teams" using a natural disaster scenario (e.g., severe flooding in a conflict zone). They will use the UNICEF Core Commitments for Children (CCCs) as a guide to prioritize a limited budget across water, health, and protection to come to a solution.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294561
