UID:b522fadade641a806486f7d94d176df21202026_4:52:07_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:QT-BIPOC Regular Meet-Up #1
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293600
DESCRIPTION:The QT BIPOC Initiative is kicking off their Spring 2026 Regular Meet-ups with a meeting centered around self-advocacy. Attendees will learn about the concept and have the opportunity to practice and think through scenarios. Boba will also be provided, first come, first served!\nFor accommodations that require support from Disability Services, please contact them directly at ods@gmu.edu. If you have accommodation-related questions about the general run of program, please email the Center directly at lgbtq@gmu.edu. \n\nPlease be aware that a 1-week notice is requested as some accommodations may require time for the University to arrange. Learn more about Event Accommodations here https://ds.gmu.edu/event-accessibility/ \nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293600
END:VEVENT
