URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296029
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Robot Night to work on building a 3d printed robot from scratch. No prior experience is needed and all majors are welcome. All you need to do is show up. Office hours are from 5:30-6:00pm.\n\nBeginners will work on building a SMARS robot https://www.smarsfan.com/#google_vignette \n\nThose who have build a SMARS robot before can work on one of our more advanced robot platforms!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296029
