UID:7e35bc6b7285d3885dc6a2b4b8380ede252026_11:46:22_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:FAVS Workshop Series: Red vs. Arri Camera Shootout with JaMar Jones
LOCATION:AB 1007, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295165
DESCRIPTION:Many of the biggest films in the world are shot on either a Red or Arri Cinema Camera. Led by Cinematographer & Director, JaMar Jones, this is a hands-on opportunity to get your hands on both professional tools and learn about their individual strengths and what makes them different. Footage from the shootout will be made available after the workshop. Participants who sign up for this workshop are also invited to come with faculty and staff to DC Camera as part of prep for the workshop.\n\nLearn more about JaMar Jones here: www.j.works\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295165
END:VEVENT
