SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Maintain Mason
LOCATION:Student Involvement Office (Hub 2300), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293379
DESCRIPTION:Join Mason Student Government every Friday from 12:30-1:30 for Maintain Mason!! Maintain Mason is a Student Government tradition. Every Friday, we go and pick up trash on campus. It is a volunteer opportunity and a major way to keep George Mason a clean and sustainable campus! We look forward to Maintaining Mason with you!(Gloves and Grabbers provided!)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293379
