UID:79a71bda37ff8b0d42cf4c76d1bb41f9172026_1:29:04_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Networking Workshop
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292160
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an interactive virtual workshop tailored for Costello College of Business students!\nNetworking is more than just exchanging business cards—it's about building meaningful connections. This workshop will help you hone your networking skills and expand your professional circle through authentic and impactful networking strategies. Learn how to leverage your network for career growth and opportunities.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292160
END:VEVENT
