UID:495c455a2737966815969f06aa0684631122026_9:38:47_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Nintendo Night 
LOCATION:Fairfax Campus: Johnson Center Atrium , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292400
DESCRIPTION:🎮 Nintendo Night @ the JC 🎮\nLooking for a fun way to kick off your Friday night? Pull up to Nintendo Night—a collab between GMU Esports and Mason Student Centers—on Friday, Feb 20 from 6–9 PM in the Johnson Center Atrium!\n\nWhether you’re a competitive gamer or just here for the vibes, there’s something for everyone. Jump into tournament zones, play on legacy Nintendo consoles, and try out classic and modern games with friends (or future rivals 👀). It’s also the perfect chance to learn more about gaming clubs on campus, meet fellow gamers, and get involved in the community.\n\nNo experience required—just show up, grab a controller, and play. 🎉\nFree, fun, and open to all. Don’t miss it!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292400
END:VEVENT
