UID:434422267ab07b8b27d3f4988a075d551212026_12:45:35_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Runway on Shuffle
LOCATION:The HUB Ballroom, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293658
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Runway on Shuffle, where music and fashion collide in perfect harmony. This electrifying show takes the audience on a style journey through five distinctive genres-Country, R&B, Rock, Pop, and International. Each section transforms the runway into a new world: from the rustic charm and denim chic of Country, to the smooth elegance and soulful tones of R&B; from the rebellious edge and leather attitude of Rock, to the vibrant colors and playful energy of Pop; and finally, the rich textures and cultural fusion of the International finale. Every beat brings a new mood, every look tells a story, and every transition keeps the audience guessing-because on this runway, the next style is always on shuffle!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293658
END:VEVENT
