UID:dde3c253864672ebcffe28c6db63cad21132026_12:55:49_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Maryland Heights via Harper's Ferry Hike
LOCATION:Maryland Heights via Harper's Ferry, 39.32440904433444,-77.7314046035423
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292460
DESCRIPTION:📏 Distance, Time, & Difficulty\nDistance: ~4.5 miles round trip (to the overlook)\nEstimated time: ~2.5 – 3 hours\nElevation gain: ~1,000 – 1,100 ft\nModerate (steady uphill climb with some steep and rocky sections)\n\n🚗 Parking\nParking is limited and can fill up quickly\nNational Park entry fees may apply (we will try to get funding for this!)\n\n⚠️ Trail Tips\nLong uphill sections — bring water and snacks for breaks\nRocky terrain near overlooks; wear sturdy hiking shoes\nVery exposed viewpoints — be cautious near cliff edges\nPopular trail, so expect crowds on weekends\n\n\n[Link to AllTrails map!](https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/west-virginia/maryland-heights-via-overlook-cliffs-and-combined-trail?sh=ttatpp&utm_medium=trail_share&utm_source=alltrails_virality)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292460
END:VEVENT
