DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special kiosk event highlighting Signal Free Society and its mission to build intentional, present, and purpose-driven community.\n\nThis event is an opportunity to meet the Signal Free Society leadership team, learn more about their vision, and connect with individuals who value real conversations and meaningful engagement in a fast-paced, distracted world. Discover what it means to live “signal free” and how SFS is creating spaces that encourage connection, growth, and impact. Learn about the joy of coffee and cats along the way!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295698
