SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Bites & Insights With GAPSA 
LOCATION:Johnson Center 1st Floor. Kiosk B, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295506
DESCRIPTION:Snack, Scribble & Share with GAPSA! 🍪✍️ \n\nSwing by the GAPSA table for free snacks, fun giveaways, and a quick, low-key activity. Finish a short grad-life prompt, share your thoughts, and grab a treat--It takes less than a minute! \n\nWhether you’re curious about what GAPSA does, want to get involved, or just need a snack between classes, we’d love to see you. Come say hi, learn how GAPSA advocates for graduate students, and connect with the grad community in a casual, no-pressure way. \n\nFinish a prompt. Grab a snack. Be heard. Date: February 23 Time: 2-4 PM. Location: Johnson Center 1st Floor. \n\n \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295506
END:VEVENT
