SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Study Abroad Scholarship- Gilman Scholarship Workshop
LOCATION:Room 241 Johnson Center, Global Education Office , George Mason University, Global Education Office (GEO), Johnson Center, Room 235, 4400 University Drive, MS 2B8, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295503
