SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:LAPS U.S.–Venezuela Discussion Event
LOCATION:JC Gold Room, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295384
DESCRIPTION:This event will be a student-led discussion exploring the political, economic, and humanitarian relationship between the United States and Venezuela. Attendees will learn about key historical context, current issues, and how these dynamics impact Venezuelan communities both abroad and locally. The goal is to create an open space for dialogue, awareness, and student engagement while encouraging critical thinking about Latin American politics and global responsibility.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295384
