UID:c4f4aa2556dc482ac25d2ee1e00325cc1272026_2:13:26_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Old Town Fairfax Coffee Shop Crawl 
LOCATION:Old Town Fairfax Coffee Shops! Check description for details 
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294428
DESCRIPTION:Join Contemporary Student Services, First Year Connections, and the Old Town Fairfax Business Association in this Coffee Shop Crawl! Come by and check out the local coffee shops and get some free samples. Meet up at the CUE bus stop to take the bus together or park for free in the local area! There will be a passport for students to collect and if you visit each location you can get a free GMU Travel Mug! Visit all the stops and stop by Layered Coffee Shop to pick up your mug!\n\nList of participating coffee shops! \n-Layered\n-Commonwealth Brewing\n-Common Culture\n-Sunberry Bowls \n-De Clieu Coffee\n\nGetting to the shops:\nIf you would like to take the CUE bus we will have student staff riding the bus with students to Old Town Fairfax. Just come to the CUE bus stop by Merten Hall starting at 3pm until 4:15pm to check in and ride over! \n\nIf you are planning on driving you can park in one of the garages in Old Town Fairfax for free for two hours. The Old Town Plaza parking garage is right next to the first stop on the map. Layered also has a full parking lot for students to park in. Staff will be between the coffee shops handing out passports and we will have a table in Layered as well! \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294428
END:VEVENT
