UID:c730fda41f4fe32a7b52d49ca32e69701242026_10:00:24_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:IFTAR FOR HARMONY
LOCATION:Fenwick library Wing A, 4348 Chesapeake River Ln, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294281
DESCRIPTION:We are excited to invite you to Iftar for Harmony, a special community gathering hosted by Harmony Circle that brings people together for dialogue, connection, and a shared meal.\n📅 Date: February 24\n⏰ Time: 4:30 PM – 7:30 PM\n📍 Location: Fenwick Wing A, Interfaith Center\nThe evening will include a brief interfaith panel discussion followed by a community dinner as we come together in the spirit of unity, reflection, and understanding. This event is open to everyone—friends, family, students, and community members from all backgrounds are welcome.\nNo prior knowledge is needed—just come as you are and join us for meaningful conversation, good food, and a welcoming atmosphere.\nWe would love to see you there!\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294281
END:VEVENT
