SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Speed Friending
LOCATION:Buchanan Hall D023, George Mason University Korea, Songdomunhwa-ro 119-4, Yeonsu-gu, Incheon, 21985, Korea, South
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296080
DESCRIPTION:This event is catered to helping all students make new friends in a different environment. The participants will sit in a line/table. One side will rotate. Between each rotation, there will be 1-2 minutes for participants to write on their cards about what they liked/didn't like about that person (for personal notes). Each round would last 5 minutes. At the end of the event, we will leave the floor open for people to freely mingle.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296080
END:VEVENT
