UID:75485a5c05acdb1e848389aa25a188732122026_1:58:37_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:General Body Meeting - ColorStack
LOCATION:Innovation Hall, Room 132, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295724
DESCRIPTION:ColorStack @ GMU — General Body Meeting\n\n📅 Feb 24\n🕕 6:30 PM – 7:30 PM\n📍 Innovation Hall 132\n\nLooking for people to study with, grind interviews with, and actually stay consistent with? Pull up to our GBM 👀\n\nWe’ll introduce what ColorStack is all about, how the community works, and the kind of support you can expect throughout the semester 🤝 Then we’ll talk about interview prep habits, how to stay consistent, and how members help each other through recruiting season 💻🧠\n\nWhether you’re just starting CS or already applying, you’ll leave with a plan and people to work with 📈\n\nBring a friend and come see the vibe ✨\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295724
END:VEVENT
