SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Resume Building Event
LOCATION:SUB1 3B, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295495
DESCRIPTION:At this Resume Building Event, we will walk attendees through how to build and improve resumes for federal and non-federal government applications. Propelling women's representation in diplomatic and political fields, we hope to prepare students to stand out in the application pool and excel in their careers, whether that be in the local or international arena.\nAny and all government and/or global affairs adjacent majors are welcome! Besides government focused resume building, we will provide tips for any and all students to cater their resume to whatever position they are applying to. From this, we hope to prepare students for entering the job market now and after graduation. We are preparing students to accurately market their skills to ensure career readiness.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295495
END:VEVENT
