UID:45893289ed78003ae439b74b6bcc2b392102026_1:27:27_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Stock Talk: NVIDIA Earnings Workshop 
LOCATION:Sandbridge Hall 107, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295558
DESCRIPTION:Join Stock Talk for a collaborative NVIDIA Earnings Workshop on February 26th. Join us for a practical breakdown of what actually moves a stock around earnings like analyzing key financial metrics, guidance, narrative, and market expectations using NVIDIA as our real-time case study. We’ll walk through how to read the earnings release and highlights, interpret the numbers that matter, and connect insights to investing decisions. Whether you’re new to earnings or want a sharper framework for analyzing reports, this workshop will help you follow the story behind the results and discuss what it could mean for the stock afterward. We will also take some time to discuss other topics such as day trading, a beginners guide to investing, and ways to jumpstart your career.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295558
END:VEVENT
