UID:1a9d1b2fbba062cea48b43b3c210d8ea172026_1:44:06_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Resume 102: Writing Effective Content Workshop
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292165
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a resume writing workshop tailored for Costello College of Business students!\nThis interactive workshop focuses on the art of writing compelling resume content that showcases your unique value. Our career advisors will teach you how to highlight your achievements, tailor your language to industry expectations, and incorporate keywords that boost visibility with employers.\n\nKey Takeaways:\n-Craft impactful bullet points that demonstrate results and accomplishments.\n-Learn strategies to tailor your resume to specific roles and industries.\n-Master keyword optimization to pass applicant tracking systems (ATS).\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292165
END:VEVENT
