UID:c97d06974825459d9687ac9cf18e6e3c2112026_4:14:16_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Intro 2 SGI Buddhism! 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295672
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to our first meeting of this semester! We will share a short introduction to SGI Nichiren Buddhism, part of the Mahayana tradition, so you can learn more about its philosophy and practice. \n\nWe’ll discuss our plans and goals for the semester as an organization. Toward the end of the meeting, we’ll open the floor for anyone who would like to share general challenges they may be facing in their university or personal life. We’ll explore how Buddhist philosophy can transform our problems into successes (something we will practice and discuss in more depth next time).\n\nSee you soon :)\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/97382130284?pwd=Y5di5hbRa7gf7l54t6MetCLfME7RMu.1\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295672
END:VEVENT
