UID:a5634e479a1325510940cd089a871cfc232026_1:21:51_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Open Talk with University Leadership
LOCATION:2001 - Main Reading Room, Fenwick Library, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294989
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an open and interactive conversation with university leadership designed especially for graduate and professional students. This interactive session offers a welcoming space to ask questions, share concerns, and discuss the issues that matter most to you—whether academic freedom, freedom of speech, graduate student life, campus resources, or your overall experience. \n\nHear directly from Laurence Bray, Senior Associate Provost for Graduate Education and leader of the Graduate Division, along with a representative from University Life at George Mason University. Lunch will be provided for registered attendees.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294989
