UID:88eee3f8e9c452d36c63cfcf628b4ea9172026_1:45:50_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:LinkedIn Workshop featuring Stoladi
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292166
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an interactive virtual workshop featuring Shawn Williams, Director of Administration at Stoladi.\n\nThis workshop, designed specifically for Costello College of Business students, shows you how to unlock the potential of your professional profile! Join us for an engaging LinkedIn Workshop where you'll discover how to create an impactful and attention-grabbing LinkedIn profile. Learn how to optimize your profile, leverage the platform's features to expand your network, and enhance your visibility in the professional world. Gain insights on effective strategies for branding yourself, connecting with industry professionals, and accessing career opportunities. Elevate your LinkedIn presence and harness its power to propel your career forward.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292166
END:VEVENT
