UID:6b82693422d8d98ef4c70c428c46437f2242026_9:28:28_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:French Language in Paris, Summer 2026 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296294
DESCRIPTION:Is there anything better than spending a summer abroad in Paris? This intensive French language program for beginning, intermediate, and advanced students takes place for one month in Paris, the beautiful capital city of France. All students will live with a French family to truly experience Parisian and French life and culture. The program also includes free time for students to use to plan their own weekend excursions or afternoon activities.\n\nMeeting Link: https://nam11.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgmu.zoom.us%2Fj%2F98855848484%3Fpwd%3DNUweEb4LZUUL4db7xKzLiK4qISdsf1.1&data=05%7C02%7Cmasonled%40gmu.edu%7C5960b3e738d34127c7b808de73254015%7C9e857255df574c47a0c00546460380cb%7C0%7C0%7C639074800977678372%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=P7r5DR9XamRtpn9AFJ10xygTDjhCVR3iAQ5rXlKAYi8%3D&reserved=0\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296294
END:VEVENT
