LOCATION:Hanover Hall, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295050
DESCRIPTION:Bienvenue à tout le monde!\nWe are so excited to announce we will be teaming up with the French Club to bring you our 3rd GBM, for French Hot Chocolate with Sweet and Savory Crepes! \nThe meeting will be Friday, February 27th  from 4pm - 6pm.\nIf you are interested, please RSVP and pay the dues using the link that will open one week before the meeting: https://forms.gle/V9hUVhHPkpZ3TaFp6\nWe accept cash and Venmo.\nWe hope to see you all there, and we're excited to cook with you this semester! If you have any concerns or questions, please reach out to our officers through Mason360, Discord, or Instagram. \nWE HOPE TO SEE YOU ALL THERE!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295050
END:VEVENT
