UID:6f8a0e786975ffe01451092410877ce92162026_1:30:23_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Bridge Building Competition
LOCATION:Mason Innovation Exchange (MIX), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295891
DESCRIPTION:Design it. Build it. Watch it break!\n\nJoin ASME for an exciting two-part bridge building competition! During the first session (February 27th, 5-7pm), teams will design and construct a balsa wood bridge. At the second session (March 6th, 5-7pm), we’ll test each bridge under increasing load to determine which design is the strongest. You have 1 full week to work with your team to build the perfect bridge.\n\nNo experience? No problem. This event is open to all students and is beginner-friendly. We’ll provide everything you need — just bring your creativity and competitive spirit!\n\nMay the best bridge win!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295891
END:VEVENT
