DESCRIPTION:For this workshop, ensure that you have emailed trobin30@gmu.edu for access to MoneyGuidePro BEFORE registering. We will work on creating a sample financial plan using the software and applying it to a case study led by Professor Tom Robinson. This is a GREAT opportunity for students to get hands-on access to the software and learn more about what financial advisors do daily. \n\nMeeting Link: https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_YWE4NWNkMWYtZDdmYS00ZDliLWIxYzMtYmU0YWRjYTU5OGNk%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%229e857255-df57-4c47-a0c0-0546460380cb%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%22cc79b46f-d18b-4c01-9924-4b909c2e42a3%22%7d\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295653
