UID:a9246e934754a741fe68884069249d0d222026_7:07:24_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mass Casualty Incidents
LOCATION:Sub-1 3A, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294961
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an EMS Club meeting focused on Mass Casualty Incidents (MCIs)—situations where the number of patients overwhelms available resources. We’ll break down what defines an MCI, how first responders triage and prioritize care, and the critical role EMS plays in coordination and scene management. Through real-world examples, you’ll gain insight into decision-making under pressure and the importance of teamwork during large-scale emergencies.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294961
END:VEVENT
