SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:MIX Welding Open Work Hours in the School of Art Sculpture Area
LOCATION:Art and Design Building Basement Rm L006 (across the lawn from Research Hall and next to the Nguyen Engineering Building), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295673
DESCRIPTION:After completing the MIX Welder Training, students can use the MIG welders in the School of Art Sculpture Lab SOA Building L006 on select Monday's between 2-4pm with the assistance of Prof. Brian Davis. The MIX Welder training is a requirement. If you haven't completed the training you will be turned away from Open Work Hours. Remember to wear closed toed shoes, if you have long hair to tie it back, and limit loose clothing.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295673
