SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Global Affairs GBM 
LOCATION:JC Meeting Room A , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295848
DESCRIPTION:Our Global Affairs GBM (General Body Meeting) is an engaging gathering where members come together to discuss current international issues, explore global policy topics, and learn about upcoming opportunities in diplomacy, development, security, and international advocacy. The meeting will include interactive discussions, updates on club initiatives, networking opportunities, and ways for members to get involved in events, leadership, and professional development activities. Whether you're passionate about international relations, global justice, public policy, or cross-cultural dialogue, this GBM provides a space to connect, learn, and grow within a community committed to global engagement.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295848
END:VEVENT
