LOCATION:Hub Ballroom Front, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295629
DESCRIPTION:This Ramadan Iftar Dinner is an event intended to bring students together to break fast in a welcoming and respectful environment. The program will include brief opening remarks along with a discussion, and a shared meal served at sunset, with time for conversation and community building. The event is open to all students, including those who are fasting and those who wish to attend in support, and aims to promote cultural understanding, reflection, and connection during the month of Ramadan. \nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295629
END:VEVENT
