DESCRIPTION:Join Nu Rho Psi Honor Society & Premedical Society for an informative Pre-Med Information Session led by GMU's Pre-Health Advisor, Dr. Maria Wilkins. This collaborative event will cover the essentials of preparing for medical school, including coursework, extracurriculars, timelines, and application strategies. Whether you’re just starting to explore the pre-med path or getting ready to apply, this session will provide valuable guidance and answers to your questions. We will have food & refreshments - hope to see you there! 🧠🩺⚕️\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295741
