UID:1d9f63b5cfdb1ebb43107678d13c0283172026_1:49:18_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Leveraging International Experience
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292168
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a job search workshop tailored for Costello College of Business students!\nWhether you’re an international student, from a multicultural background, or have studied abroad, your global experience is a powerful asset — but are you leveraging it effectively in your job search?\n\nLearn to confidently communicate your unique perspective and international background in professional settings and how to turn cultural adaptability, language skills, and global awareness into strengths on your resume, in interviews, and throughout your career journey.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n\nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292168
END:VEVENT
