SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mason Chooses Kindness: Inaugural Kindness Summit
LOCATION:Johnson Center, Bistro, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293972
DESCRIPTION:Kindness Starts Here: Shape Your Brand, Transform Your World\n\nJoin us for Mason’s first-ever Kindness Summit, a dynamic and interactive experience designed to explore the power of kindness in shaping personal identity, relationships, and environments. This summit will help you understand how kindness can strengthen your personal brand, enhance well-being, and create positive ripple effects both inside and outside of Mason.\n\nLunch will be provided. \nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293972
