UID:a52318342c887748fbe7631e9aec8ce9322026_9:55:46_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:FREE Knot Tying Clinic
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296649
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever been in a situation where you needed to tie a knot and realized you didn’t know what to do?  Do you ever look down at your shoelace and ponder it’s infinite intricacies!? Fear “knot,” Outdoor Adventures is offering a FREE educational clinic to satisfy all of your knot tying curiosities.  This hour-long session is the perfect introduction to some of the most basic and commonly used knots in the outdoors. By the end, you will have gained the skills to start implementing them into your camping and hiking excursions. No prior experience is necessary, and everything will be provided by the Outdoor Adventures team during the course of instruction. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296649
END:VEVENT
