DESCRIPTION:•	Date: March 4, 2026 (Wednesday)\n•	Time: 12:00 PM – 12:40 PM\n•	Location: G307 (Mason Dreamliner)\n•	Agenda:\n	12:00 PM – 12:10 PM | Welcome & Brief Introduction by CDC\n	12:10 – 12:40 PM | Payment & Timesheet management by HR\n \nAttendance at this orientation is compulsory for all Work-Study students at Mason Korea. \nPlease note that unexcused absences may result in the termination of your Work-Study contract and could affect your eligibility for future on-campus internship opportunities.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296098
