SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:JA Finance Park Volunteer Day
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292359
DESCRIPTION:Volunteer with Beta Alpha Psi at JA Finance Park! Teach financial literacy to K-12 students and make a real impact in our community.\n\nWhat to expect:\n- Guide students through real-world budgeting simulations\n- Build mentorship and communication skills\n- Earn service hours\n\nDate: Wednesday, March 4, 2026\nTime: 8:30 AM - 1:10 PM\nLocation: JA Finance Park, Fairfax (register to view address)\n\nLimited spots. Transportation on your own. Carpooling encouraged.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292359
END:VEVENT
