UID:2da7c294e8bfb0cb660cfaccb4588bd62262026_10:36:30_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Ask the Professionals: Networking
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296536
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Ask the Professionals: Networking featuring Basile Lemba, founder of the BL Networking Institute and author of How to Successfully Network in Business and in Life. Basile’s global journey—from architecture in Africa to building an accredited networking program in the U.S.—led him to uncover the universal, teachable science behind effective networking. With over 30,000 hours of real-world experience, he helps professionals and organizations transform the way they connect, communicate, and create opportunities.\n\nIn this session, you’ll learn the proven techniques behind the Science of Networking, build confidence in approaching anyone anywhere, and gain actionable tools to boost visibility, strengthen relationships, and generate meaningful results. Don’t miss the chance to learn from one of today’s experts in business networking—and elevate the quality of both your connections and your career.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296536
END:VEVENT
