SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:ProfessionalQuest - Government Contracting
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296071
DESCRIPTION:Looking to launch a meaningful career in government or government contracting? Don’t miss this event designed to connect Costello College of Business students with representatives from government agencies and contracting firms including: GSA, WashingtonExec, Peraton, and more.\n\nThis is your chance to:\n-Meet industry professionals\n-Discover internship and job opportunities\n-Gain insider knowledge on navigating government pathways and contracting careers\n-Build connections that could shape your future\n\nThis event is about making real connections, asking smart questions, and standing out as the talent companies are looking for.\n\nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296071
END:VEVENT
