UID:76728e786874815c2f6fa1c9387dcc272162026_8:02:44_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Vision Boards & Vibes
LOCATION:JC ROOM B , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295978
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Women’s History Month with intention, creativity, and community.\n\nJoin us for a special Vision Board Event honoring the powerful legacy of women who have shaped history ,especially in mathematics, leadership, and innovation. From groundbreaking women in STEM to trailblazers in every industry, Women’s History Month reminds us that vision, courage, and strategy create lasting change.\n\nThis interactive experience blends creativity with goal-setting. As we reflect on the achievements of women who broke barriers in math and beyond, you’ll create a personalized vision board focused on your own aspirations whether in academics, career growth, financial empowerment, wellness, or leadership. Just like solving a math equation, success starts with a clear plan and intentional steps.\n\nAll materials will be provided. Come ready to dream boldly, think strategically, and build the future you deserve.\n\nLet’s honor Women’s History Month by designing our next chapter together. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295978
END:VEVENT
