SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Eres Poderosa
LOCATION:JC Room F, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295983
DESCRIPTION:Eres Poderosa is an event created to empower women and remind them of their inner strength, resilience, and worth. Through meaningful conversations and uplifting activities, we encourage women to recognize the power they already carry within themselves. One of our main symbols is the mirror, which we use as a reminder to truly look at ourselves, not with doubt or criticism, but with confidence and self-love. By seeing their own reflection, participants are reminded that the strength they seek is already within them.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295983
END:VEVENT
