SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Cousin's Corner: Soft Launch
LOCATION:SUB1 3B, 4469 Aquia Creek Ln, Student Union Building 1, Suite 2400, MSN 2F6, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291944
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our second Cousin's Corner of the semester! Cousin's Corner is a dialogues across difference series hosted by CLIE that invites students to discuss a topic in an intimate, low-stakes environment. This session invites participants to explore the process of growth and self-transformation through the lens of the “soft launch”, a gentle unveiling of new versions of ourselves. Through creative reflection and open dialogue, students will consider how change, healing, and self-discovery unfold over time. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291944
END:VEVENT
