SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Clearance Ready: International Experiences and Contacts
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291739
DESCRIPTION:When looking for a job in the government or with a government contractor, you will be investigated on a number of topics. This session will look more closely at your international relationships, travel, and overall experience abroad, and how investigators evaluate your background in this area. Learn what is accepted, what could be a problem, and how you can manage relationships moving forward! This program is part of the University Career Services' Clearance Ready Program. For additional information please visit careers.gmu.edu/clearance\n\nLink to event: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/92285813300\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291739
