DESCRIPTION:Join us for an engaging Arabic Calligraphy Workshop where participants will explore the beauty and artistry of traditional Arabic script. This hands-on session will introduce the history, cultural significance, and basic techniques of calligraphy, guiding attendees step-by-step as they practice forming letters and words with specialized tools. No prior experience is needed—just come ready to learn, create, and appreciate this timeless art form.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295728
