SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mid-Semester Success Workshop
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296112
DESCRIPTION:*Priority registration for students in Patriot Fellows, DC-CAP, EIP, and STEP\n\nJoin Student Success Coaching and Learning Services for a  Mid-Semester Success Workshop! Explore supports to help you navigate challenges and finish the semester strong.\n\nLunch Provided!\n\nAt this workshop, you'll have the opportunity to:\n\n➤ Increase your awareness of your academic standing and understand the implications of Satisfactory Academic Progress (SAP).\n➤ Identify actionable next steps and connect with resources.\n➤ Recognize potential barriers and explore ways to overcome them.\n➤ Foster accountability and motivation for improvement. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296112
END:VEVENT
