UID:1ad957c3da8d760b338719b3caf270d71122026_4:57:39_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Yoga: A Curriculum for Life 
LOCATION:The Haven at Fuse, room 2500 , 3401 Fairfax Drive, Arlington 22201, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292438
DESCRIPTION:Yoga: A Curriculum for Life integrates\nmovement, mindfulness, and reflection to explore how yoga philosophy and contemporary consciousness studies can enhance personal well-being.\n\nEach class weaves together three\ninterrelated components: a gentle yoga practice, a lecture-discussion, and a guided meditation. All yoga levels are welcome to attend.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292438
