LOCATION:Finley Lot, Fairfax Campus, Finley Lot, Patriot Cir, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295633
DESCRIPTION:Headed home or planning a spring break getaway? Ride with George Mason! Book a one-way or round-trip ticket to/from the Fairfax Campus at a special discounted rate exclusively for George Mason students. Mason ID required when boarding.\n\n➡️ Departing from Campus\nFriday, March 6, 11 am\nFinley Lot, Fairfax Campus\n\n⬅️ Return to Campus\nSunday, March 15\nVarious Locations\n\nWhy ride with us?\n💰 Affordable & convenient\n📍 Easy pick-up & drop-off right on Fairfax Campus\n🛜 Wi-Fi onboard to stream, study, or scroll\n🛍️ Free snack + giveaway bag for all riders\n🚻 Onboard restroom for added comfort\n🔰 Exclusive to Patriots for a safe, stress-free trip\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295633
