UID:9a89194c9d78a74bcb33c4015009ce852252026_9:15:02_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Culinary x Japanese Language and Culture Club S26 GBM 4
LOCATION:Hanover Hall, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296323
DESCRIPTION:日本語・日本文化クラブで、おいしい日本料理を一緒に作りませんか？ぜひお気軽にご参加ください！皆さまにお会いできるのを楽しみにしています〜\nFor GBM 4, we are teaming up with the Japanese Language and Culture Club for a special cultural exchange! The event will feature Okonomiyaki, Dango, and Melon Floats. Stop by to see what the Japanese Language and Culture Club is all about and experience a few of Japan's most popular sweet and savory treats.\nThe meeting will be Friday, March 6th  from 4pm - 6pm.\nIf you are interested, please RSVP and pay the dues using the link that will open one week before the meeting:  https://forms.gle/dSe9smab18QKwH5v6\nWe accept cash and Venmo.\nWe hope to see you all there, and we're excited to cook with you this semester! If you have any concerns or questions, please reach out to our officers through Mason360, Discord, or Instagram. \nWE HOPE TO SEE YOU ALL THERE!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296323
END:VEVENT
