SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Baseball vs. Georgetown - BASEBALL PIN, BINGO, STUDENTS BRING A FRIEND FREE!
LOCATION:Spuhler Field, 4400 University Drive, MS 3A5, George Mason Field House, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2290095
DESCRIPTION:Baseball vs. Georgetown\n\nGet your student tickets right here on Mason360! DO NOT PRINT your ticket, we are a paperless venue, and WILL NOT accept printed tickets. Make sure you have the Mason360 app downloaded with your tickets accessible via mobile device!\n\nHave your QR code ready, after passing through the metal detectors, present your QR code to the tablet, and you're good to go!\n\nTo find your ticket easier: In the events tab of the Mason360 app, click on the filter button in the top right, filter by group, select "Mason Athletics", apply the filter, and select the game you wish to register for!\n\nCome out and support your George Mason Baseball team! Make sure to join the Athletics group here on Mason360 for all things Mason for upcoming sporting events!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2290095
END:VEVENT
