SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Graduate Student Career Conference and Networking Reception
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291925
DESCRIPTION:Register ahead for the 2026 Graduate Student Career Conference & Networking Reception. This conference is for all current graduate students, master's and doctoral, to gain insights on job search strategies and networking tips. Attendees can expect to hear from alumni, employers, and experts while participating in interactive workshops designed to help you market your academic skills to reach your career goals. The day concludes with a professional networking reception with George Mason alumni. Register now on Handshake to reserve your spot at this special event! This signature conference and reception are presented by University Career Services, Graduate Student Life, the Graduate Division, UL Mason Square, and Alumni Relations.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291925
END:VEVENT
