UID:adfb9fdfedd264e17c01bad951e83a681102026_3:35:03_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Volunteer with EY at JA Finance Park
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292360
DESCRIPTION:Join Beta Alpha Psi and EY professionals for a morning of impact.\nTeach financial literacy to middle school students alongside EY team members, then connect over a networking lunch.\n\nWhat to expect:\n- Guide students through real-world budgeting simulations\n- Volunteer side-by-side with EY professionals\n- Build mentorship and communication skills\n- Network over lunch with the EY team\n- Earn service hours\n\nDate: Tuesday, March 10, 2026\nTime: 8:35 AM – 1:10 PM\nLocation: Address provided upon registration\nSpots are limited. Transportation on your own. Carpooling encouraged.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292360
END:VEVENT
