SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mental Health First Aid Training
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293683
DESCRIPTION:This 8-hour training is split into two 4-hour sessions, and the training is open to students, staff, and faculty. The program is sponsored through the National Council for Mental Well-Being and helps to prepare participants to assist someone in mental distress. Participants should not register unless they are able to attend both sessions. Sessions will take place via zoom on March 10 and 11 from 9 am until 1 pm each day. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293683
END:VEVENT
