SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Volunteer with BDO at JA Finance Park
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292369
DESCRIPTION:Join Beta Alpha Psi. Volunteer alongside BDO professionals at JA Finance Park! Teach financial literacy to K-12 students while networking with one of the largest accounting and advisory firms in the world.\n\nThis is a special volunteer day in partnership with BDO with 15 spots available.\n\nWhat to expect:\n- Volunteer side by side with BDO team members\n- Guide students through real-world budgeting simulations\n- Build connections with firm professionals\n- Earn service hours\n\nDate: Wednesday, March 11, 2026\nTime: 8:30 AM to 1:10 PM\nLocation: JA Finance Park, Fairfax (register to view address)\n\nTransportation on your own. Carpooling encouraged.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292369
END:VEVENT
