UID:6300cdfa81704b030b0b82723b7299732162026_3:19:24_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:The GAIN Mapathon
LOCATION:HUB VIP 3, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295903
DESCRIPTION:Put vulnerable communities on the map. Millions of people live in places that don't exist on any map, making it impossible for aid workers to reach them during disasters. Join GAIN for a digital humanitarian service night where we will use the Missing Maps platform to trace satellite imagery and create life-saving maps for organizations like the Red Cross and Doctors Without Borders. No experience needed, just bring a laptop!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295903
END:VEVENT
