SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Spring Recess Fellowship: Supporting Korean International Students Away from Home
LOCATION:Johnson Center, Bistro, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296544
DESCRIPTION:“Home Away From Home” Cultural Night is a Spring Recess gathering created specifically to support Korean international students who are unable to travel home during the academic break. As campus activity slows and many students leave to spend time with family, this event will provide a welcoming space for Korean students to share a meal, enjoy familiar cultural elements, and connect with peers who share similar experiences of living abroad.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296544
END:VEVENT
