SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Tu Bhi Mixer
LOCATION:RAC - Recreation and Athletic Complex,  4350 Banister Creek Ct,  Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294801
DESCRIPTION:Tu Bhi Nachle's Mixer aims to provide a chance for teams across the country to get to know one another through a variety of games, interactive challenges, a dance-off and more. These challenges build a sense of excitement, reduce stress, create memories, promote camaraderie and team-building, encourage friendly competition, and determine the competition show order. In summary, TBN's Mixer with interactive games and bonding activities not only makes the process of determining the show order more enjoyable but also contributes to a positive competition atmosphere - ultimately enhancing the overall experience for competitors and participants alike.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294801
END:VEVENT
