LOCATION:JC Room A, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295294
DESCRIPTION:Join Signal Free Society for a relaxing movie and pizza night designed to help students unwind and connect with others. We’ll be serving pizza while screening a film in a comfortable, device-free environment. This event offers a chance to take a break from schoolwork, disconnect from screens, and enjoy a shared experience with peers. Come recharge, socialize, and enjoy an stress-free moment! \n\nFeel free to join our discord for any questions. Movies will be announced shortly before the event start date. \n\nhttps://discord.gg/utX8pnWY\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295294
