LOCATION:Katherine Johnson Hall Atrium, George Mason Science and Technology Campus, 10900 University Blvd., Manassas, VA 20110, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296666
DESCRIPTION:This early adjunct to International Week invites us to celebrate difference and diversity a few weeks before the Fairfax campus celebrates iWeek. Students from the SciTech world, the Governor's School and the Office of International Programs and Services serve up the tastes sights and sounds of their cultures in this classic Mason tradition. Taste beverages and snacks, hear music and language, see fashion and form, and speak with students representing their heritages.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296666
END:VEVENT
