SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Dowd & Company PC Immigration Workshop 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294944
DESCRIPTION:This webinar is hosted by the Office of International Programs and Services and Debra J.C. Dowd, an experienced immigration attorney from Dowd & Company PC.    \n\nDebra will offer a comprehensive presentation on post-graduation immigration issues including OPT, H-1B, other employment-based visas, and the green card process.  Debra and the Office of International Programs and Services F-1 Team will be ready to answer your questions related to the presentation during the webinar's Q&A portion.  \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294944
END:VEVENT
