SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Real World AI Projects Interest Meeting
LOCATION:Horizon Hall 4010, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296660
DESCRIPTION:We will gather to go over AI Club's new initiative - Real World AI Projects. The best way to learn about AI is to build it, join our presentation on Tuesday to learn about different projects that we are working on. Whether you are someone with an AI/programming background or who wants to apply knowledge from your field, you are welcome to join AI Project brainstorming event day to learn about the vision and mission of our clubs new initiative. \n\n**This is Session I. Session II is happening from 6-7 PM. Both sessions will contain the same content. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296660
