UID:06b9a54cbec70769772ec0ccdfd958191262026_10:14:47_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:SI2GO Truck: Leadership for Positive Change
LOCATION:In front of Northern Neck and Starbucks , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294306
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the SI2GO Truck: Leadership for Positive Change!\nLooking for a dose of fun, freebies, and leadership inspiration? The Leadership Express: SI2GO Truck for Positive Change is rolling onto campus, and you’re invited to hop aboard for an unforgettable experience! In partnership with Student Involvement and the Center for Leadership and Intercultural Engagement, we’re bringing you a fun vibrant space to engage, connect, and lead. Swing by for awesome giveaways and get a sneak peek at some leadership initiatives that will spark your creativity and passion for positive change. Whether you’re looking to engage with others, learn about upcoming programs and events, or simply enjoy the campus buzz, the SI2GO Truck: Leadership for Positive Change is your place to stop by.  Don’t miss out on this unique opportunity to stay connected and become a leader who makes a difference. We can’t wait to see you there!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294306
END:VEVENT
