UID:c132140a2f89c73e860363e47d440620252026_2:13:56_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Women in the Workplace Panel
LOCATION:Johnson Center, Room E, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295200
DESCRIPTION:Join us in celebrating Women's History Month and hear from an array of women professionals at our 2026 Women in the Workplace Panel. Featuring Shea Holman, Hawer Sherwani, Stephanie Arhin, and Charlotte Jackson, our panelists represent women in law, healthcare, government administration, and aviation!\n\nThe event will begin with a moderated discussion about our panelists' professional experiences, followed by an audience Q&A, and end with an open networking session with our panelists. Whether you are graduating and entering the workplace this spring or are simply curious about issues women face in the professional world and strategies for overcoming them, our panelists will offer insight, advice, and genuine conversation to help students and fellow community members prepare for their careers.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295200
END:VEVENT
