SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Cafe Martí
LOCATION:JC Room D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296711
DESCRIPTION:This event brings students together for meaningful conversation over a warm cup of coffee. Café Martí is a space designed to encourage open dialogue about current political issues in a relaxed and welcoming environment. Attendees will have the opportunity to share perspectives, ask questions, and engage in thoughtful discussions with peers while enjoying coffee and light refreshments.\n\nBy creating a comfortable atmosphere, Café Martí aims to promote civic awareness, critical thinking, and respectful conversation across differing viewpoints. This event invites participants to slow down, connect with others, and explore important topics that impact their communities and beyond.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296711
END:VEVENT
