SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:International Week 2026 Flag Stringing (Volunteers Needed!) 
LOCATION:HUB Ballroom, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297016
DESCRIPTION:Volunteer for the International Week 2026 Flag Stringing! This is an important step in kicking off this exciting week and placing the international flags in the Johnson Center. \n\nWe'll have 128 flags that will be hung in the JC during iWeek. There will be several teams to string the flags in alphabetical order, paying very close attention to ensure that each flag is strung in its proper position. The more volunteers, the merrier! So please invite any Mason staff and/or students to participate. Food will be provided to volunteers! \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297016
