DESCRIPTION:We are excited to invite you to Mason Square Social Hour with GAPSA ft. Patriot Pantry, a welcoming and engaging space to bring our Mason Square community together. Join us to connect with your new VP, Eelma Ahamed, learn more about the Mason Square Patriot Pantry and the resources available to you, and meet fellow students in a relaxed, friendly environment.\nStop by before class to enjoy snacks, play games, and build new connections. Whether you are new to campus or just want to connect, this is the perfect mid-week break!\n\nDate: March 18\nTime: 3-5 PM\nLocation: Student Lounge, Van Metre Hall, Room 211.\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296300
END:VEVENT
