DESCRIPTION:Pathways to the Law: A Panel Discussion is an inspiring and informative event designed for students interested in pursuing a career in the legal field. Our panelists will share their personal journeys into law, reflecting on the academic, cultural, and professional experiences that shaped their paths. They will speak candidly about the challenges they faced, the barriers they overcame, and the communities that supported them along the way. Attendees will gain valuable insight into how identity, resilience, and mentorship play a role in building a legal career, along with practical advice and lessons learned to help guide their own journeys.\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296877
