URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296318
DESCRIPTION:Join Global Action In Nursing (GAIN) for our first-ever Global Health Cafe, a relaxed social mixer designed to bring our community together over great drinks and meaningful conversations. Take a well-deserved break from clinical rotations and coursework to enjoy freshly brewed specialty coffees and teas while connecting with fellow students passionate about global health equity. This is a casual, drop-in event, whether you want to discuss the challenges of nursing or simply unwind with a warm cup and good company, the cafe is the perfect space to recharge and build our growing community.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296318
