SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:FAVS Workshop Series: 16MM Filmmaking with Prof. Wes Hunt, in partnership with Colorlab
LOCATION:AB 1007, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295189
DESCRIPTION:Professor Wes Hunt will walk students through how films are shot on celluloid in a hands-on demonstration with a selection of 16mm cameras. The workshop will shoot a roll of 16mm film side by side with a modern digital camera and work with Color Lab of Rockville when footage is developed. Side-by-side footage will be available after the footage is developed. Participants who sign up for this workshop are also invited to come on a tour of Color Lab when we go to deliver the footage.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295189
END:VEVENT
