DESCRIPTION:Please join the University Services Committee in Student Government on Friday, March 20th from 1:30 to 3:00 PM in HUB Meeting Rooms 3, 4 & 5 for Greater Services Committee! This is an event we put on every semester in Student Government. This event will provide administrators from each of our service departments the opportunity to meet and connect with students, and share your recently completed, current, and future projects and initiatives. After, students will have the opportunity to give feedback, ask questions, and share their initiative ideas. Catering will be provided by Mason Dining\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297088
