SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Signal-Free Game Night
LOCATION:JC ROOM C, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296073
DESCRIPTION:Signal-Free Game Night is simple. Put the phones away, turn off the WiFi, and sit down with real people to play real board games. No scrolling, no notifications, no second screens. Just focus, conversation, and a little chaos over something like Ludo or Uno. The goal is to reset your brain, cut the noise, and remember what it feels like to actually be present.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296073
END:VEVENT
