UID:8d5912e904fae84d1243aa6f411bc1f22272026_5:47:40_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Volition Open Mic Night
LOCATION:JC Bistro, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296599
DESCRIPTION:Volition will be hosting Open Mic Night to celebrate the newest Volume! \n\nPerformances at this event will range from stand-up comedy, musical acts, and readings of prose and poetry. Students are especially encouraged to share work in any language(s) of their choosing, and to speak about what multilingualism and multiculturalism mean to them.  Anyone can come and perform if they want, or just enjoy from the audience. There will also be an interactive art display where attendees can put up their visual art and photography during the event!\n\nThere will be free pizza and no admission charge. Come listen to or participate in the fun! All students are welcome.\n\nFor more information about Volition Magazine and how to submit your work, visit http://volition.gmu.edu/ . \nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296599
END:VEVENT
