UID:7f64e5807184a10e6f5295b5d1b5180c352026_1:47:05_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Silk Road Nations Nowruz
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296836
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the beginning of spring and the renewal of life Nowruz, one of the world’s oldest and most meaningful cultural celebrations. Rooted in over 3,000 years of history, Nowruz, or "new day", marks the Persian New Year and the beginning of the spring equinox. This vibrant tradition originated in ancient Persia and continues to be celebrated by millions of people across Central Asia, the Middle East, the Caucasus, and beyond.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296836
END:VEVENT
