SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Rare Viewing of Archive of classic western balkan film 'Nentori I Dyte'
LOCATION:Innovation Hall 105, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296916
DESCRIPTION:On Friday March 20 at 7:30 pm we will have a showing of the classic Albanian film 'Nentori I Dyte', followed by a discussion led by the director of its restoration and founding director of the Albanian Cinema Project, special guest, film archivist Regina Longo (@longo690). \n\nTo be held at Innovation room 105 - all are welcome, from those with a special interest in Albanian culture to lovers of obscure cinema.\n\nRSVP: https://forms.gle/NP6DSHKYsVDGmv3G7\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296916
