SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Hickerson Hollow Trail, Snead Farm Dickey Ridge Loop
LOCATION:Hickerson Hollow Trail, Snead Farm Dickey Ridge Loop, 38.834230388425965,-78.18587309984987
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292463
DESCRIPTION:**Hickerson Hollow Trail**\n\n📏 Distance, Time, & Difficulty\nDistance: ~2.4 miles round trip\nEstimated time: ~1.5 – 2 hours\nElevation gain: ~656 ft\nModerate (forest hiking with some uphill and uneven terrain)\n\n[Link to AllTrails for Hickerson Hollow!](https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/virginia/hickerson-hollow-trail--2)\n\n**Snead Farm Dickey Ridge Loop Trail**\n\n📏 Distance, Time, & Difficulty\nDistance: ~3.8 miles loop\nEstimated time: ~2 – 2.5 hours\nElevation gain: ~750 ft\nModerate (rolling hills and forest trail)\n\n[Link to AllTrails for Snead Farm Dickey Ridge Loop!](https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/virginia/snead-farm-dickey-ridge-loop-trail)\n\nMORE INFO IN #EVENTS WHEN CLOSER TO HIKE!!!!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292463
END:VEVENT
