SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Caving at Glade Cave
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291948
DESCRIPTION:Come venture underground with Outdoor Adventures as we explore Glade Cave. Stalactites, stalagmites, and other cave features abound!  No previous caving experience is necessary, just an adventurous spirit and a willingness to get muddy. \n\nDifficulty: Beginner – This trip has been designed with beginner cavers in mind.   \n\nAmenities: Restrooms available at a convenience store before proceeding to the cave.  THERE ARE NO FACILITIES AVAILABLE AT THE CAVE \n\nTravel Time: 2 hours each way \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291948
END:VEVENT
