DESCRIPTION:Furs & Friends Group Hike! 🐾\n\nCome join GMU Furs & Friends for a fun group hike on Saturday, March 21st at Lake Accotink Trail ! Only 35 minutes from George Mason’s Fairfax Campus!\n\nYou’re welcome to come on your own, or hop into our Discord to chat about rides and coordinate with others.\n\nTo join the Discord server, please be ready to verify that you’re a mason student or incoming with either:\n• Your Mason ID (digital or physical)\n• Or your acceptance letter\n\nWe’re excited to see everyone there!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297025
