SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Graduate and Professional Student Appreciation Week
LOCATION:Locations vary: in-person and zoom, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291437
DESCRIPTION:Join the Graduate and Professional Student Association and Graduate Student Life in celebrating Graduate and Professional Student Appreciation Week 2026! During this week, we honor the contributions of Mason's 11,000+ graduate and professional students. The Graduate Assistant and Lecturer Appreciation Breakfast is invite-only.\n\nWe would also like to help empower units in showing their support and recognition of graduate and professional students during this year's Appreciation Week by encouraging faculty, supervisors, departments, and units in posting about their graduate students on their social media. Tag Graduate Student Life, @masongradlife, and/or use the hashtag #MasonGradAppreciation to let us know. We will re-share on our accounts and tag your students.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291437
END:VEVENT
