SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:SSA Eid Celebration
LOCATION:Potomac Science Center – River Level
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296304
DESCRIPTION:Join the Saudi Student Association for our Eid Celebration at George Mason University. This event will bring students together to celebrate Eid in a welcoming and engaging environment that highlights Saudi culture and traditions. Attendees will have the opportunity to enjoy food, socialize with fellow students, and learn about the cultural significance of Eid as a celebration of community, generosity, and gratitude after the month of Ramadan. The event aims to strengthen connections among students and promote cultural exchange within the Mason community. All Mason students are welcome to attend and celebrate this special occasion with us.activities in a welcoming environment.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296304
END:VEVENT
