SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:NSPG Real Estate | AIA
LOCATION:The Hub, Meeting Room 3-4-5, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295861
DESCRIPTION:This is an educational guest speaker event hosted by the Alternative Investments Association (AIA) in collaboration with NSPG, where students will attend in person and the guest speaker will present online. The session will teach students how real estate functions as a private-market investment, focusing on wealth creation, capital flow, and tax-efficient strategies such as 1031 exchanges, while also introducing alternative investment vehicles including private real estate structures, DSTs, and oil & gas. Students will interact with the material through guided explanations, real-world case examples, and Q&A. NSPG will provide presentation agenda notes and industry materials in advance, and the event will also highlight career pathways, internship opportunities, and future collaboration with AIA.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295861
END:VEVENT
