UID:5cbf5ab4c52d50d9a716a9e5938332441122026_2:18:49_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Becker CPA Review | Live In-Person
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292398
DESCRIPTION:BECKER CPA REVIEW | LIVE IN-PERSON SESSION\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\nJoin Beta Alpha Psi for an exclusive in-person session with a Becker CPA Review expert.\n\nThis isn't a webinar, it's a live, interactive experience where you'll get face-to-face guidance from one of Becker's top instructors.\n\n🎯 WHAT YOU'LL GAIN\n- Live CPA exam strategies from a Becker expert\n- Direct Q&A with an industry-leading instructor\n- Insider tips on exam preparation and study planning\n- Networking with peers on the same CPA journey\n\n👥 WHO SHOULD ATTEND\n- Students considering the CPA exam\n- Accounting majors planning their certification path\n- Anyone curious about what it takes to pass the CPA\n\n🏆 WHY ATTEND IN-PERSON\nThis is a rare opportunity to engage directly with Becker's team—ask questions, get personalized advice, and connect with fellow future CPAs.\n\nSpace is limited. Register now to secure your spot.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nHosted by Beta Alpha Psi Theta Alpha Chapter\nGeorge Mason University\nlinktr.ee/bap.gmu\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292398
END:VEVENT
