SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:MK Art Therapy Workshop I – “River of Life”
LOCATION:Mason Korea G316, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297103
DESCRIPTION:Date & Time: Tuesday, March 24 | 6:15–7:45 PM\nLocation: Room G316\nDinner Provided: For students who RSVP in advance (walk-ins welcome!)\n\nAbout the Workshop:\nThis creative session invites students to reflect on their life journey by drawing their experiences as a river. Through guided reflection and discussion, students explore challenges, strengths, and future goals in a supportive environment.\n\nNo artistic experience is needed—just bring an open mind and willingness to express yourself!\n\nRSVP Information:\nDinner will be provided for participants who RSVP in advance. Walk-ins are welcome, but dinner availability cannot be guaranteed without an RSVP.\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297103
END:VEVENT
