UID:6ae9c3dcc43121f578cde1b7b4838fa8172026_2:44:15_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Federal Resume Workshop featuring Aston Carter
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292178
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a resume writing workshop featuring Emily Carroll, Account Manager at Aston Carter.\n\nTailored for Costello College of Business students, discover the nuances and strategies crucial for navigating the federal job application process. Learn how to tailor your resume to federal job announcements, highlight your qualifications effectively, and maximize your chances of landing a federal position. Gain insights on formatting, keyword optimization, and showcasing your skills in a manner that resonates with federal hiring managers. Don't miss this opportunity to pave your way towards federal employment success. Secure your spot today and transform your resume into a powerful tool for federal job applications! \n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292178
END:VEVENT
