LOCATION:Johnson Center Bistro, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293099
DESCRIPTION:Come enjoy FREE international drinks and snacks at our next International Cafe! This iCafe will be focusing on countries from Europe! International Cafe (iCafe) is a student-led event centered around teas, snacks, crafts, games, and music from various countries, regions, or cultures. Learn about international cultures without leaving campus! The featured countries will be France, Germany, Italy, Spain, Turkey, and the United Kingdom!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293099
