SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Knit Kindness
LOCATION:The Haven at Fuse, Fuse Room 2500, 3401 Fairfax Dr, Fuse Room 2500, Arlington 22201, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296455
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Knit Kindness, a weekly event where your knitting skills can make a difference! Gather with fellow knitters to create cozy blankets that will be donated to Bridges to Independence , providing warmth and comfort to those in need. \nKnitting supplies will only be provided for the blankets that will be donated to Bridges to Independence. Attendees are welcome to work on other knitting projects with their own supplies.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296455
