SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mend your mind with GMU DECA 
LOCATION:Johnson Center Meeting Room C, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297163
DESCRIPTION:Mend Your Mind with GMU DECA is a student wellness event focused on stress relief and mental well-being. The purpose of this event is to provide students with a safe, supportive environment where they can take a break from academic pressures and engage in relaxing, hands-on activities designed to promote mindfulness and decompression.\n\nParticipants will have the opportunity to engage in creative and calming activities that encourage self-expression, relaxation, and social connection. This event aims to support student mental health by fostering a sense of community while helping attendees manage stress in a positive and engaging way.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297163
END:VEVENT
