UID:3b4f53e03a846f512135501e47c60ace1232025_1:35:17_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Clearance Ready: Science Careers with Clearances
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291741
DESCRIPTION:The cleared world also spans into the sciences. Hear from a panel of professionals who use their science  skills on a daily basis while also holding a clearance. Learn about how they obtained their roles, the differences between working with a clearance and without one, and how you can prepare for a position that requires a clearance. This event is part of the Clearance Ready Program and Science Careers Week.\n\nLink to Event: https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/29119159124777?p=tExsV3DGl25rZHYqef\nMeeting ID: 291 191 591 247 77\nPasscode: Vf674nx7\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291741
END:VEVENT
