UID:75f6ea1ad1150909e3a842b366dd686a292026_8:38:58_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Perler Bead Workshop
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295465
DESCRIPTION:Join the Craft Club for a perler bead workshop! Craft club members will lead you through how to use perler beads to make fridge magnets, keychains, and phone charms!\n\nWhether have never crafted before, you're an expert, or anything in between please come join us! If you've never been to a craft club meeting before this is a great opportunity to meet other club members, officers, and get a feel for the club! \n\nOur mission is simple: meet new people, have fun, and craft sustainably! We encourage everyone to bring basic supplies like markers, scissors, and glue when needed, plus any scrap materials you have at home. It's a great way to give new life to materials that might otherwise go unused while connecting with fellow crafters in a welcoming, creative environment.\n\n\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295465
END:VEVENT
