DESCRIPTION:Join us for an engaging Financial Literacy event designed to help you build confidence with your money. Learn the fundamentals of budgeting, saving, investing, credit management, and debt reduction through practical, real-world strategies. Whether you're just starting your financial journey or looking to sharpen your skills, this session will provide the tools and knowledge you need to make informed financial decisions and plan for a secure future.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295899
