SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AWS Security Hub Workshop 
LOCATION:JC Room G, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296706
DESCRIPTION:This hands-on workshop introduces an innovative solution that leverages Amazon Bedrock and AWS Systems Manager to revolutionize security finding remediation. You'll learn how to deploy and use an AI-powered Security Assistant that transforms the way organizations interact with and resolve AWS Security Hub findings through natural language processing and automated remediation capabilities.\n\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296706
