DESCRIPTION:Get moving and find your flow on March 25th from 2:00 PM to 3:00 PM at the JC G34 Dance Studio. The session features a restorative 30-minute yoga class led by Reeya (RYT 200), followed by a presentation from a RAC representative highlighting the fitness resources available right here on campus. It’s the perfect midday break to stretch your body and clear your mind. Plus, stay after the workout to enjoy some free, refreshing smoothies!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295799
END:VEVENT
