SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Pohela Boishakh 
LOCATION:JC Bistro , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296740
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a lively Boishakhi Utshab as we celebrate Pohela Boishakh, the Bengali New Year and the start of a new year in the Bengali calendar. It’s a special time for Bengalis around the world to come together, celebrate culture, and welcome new beginnings. Come enjoy an evening filled with fun games, delicious Bengali street food, music and lots of laughter with friends and community. Wear your favorite red-and-white traditional outfit, bring your best energy as we welcome the new year together 🌺🎉\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296740
