LOCATION:The Hub Student Media Office Conference Room, Our staff offices and practice studio are located in The HUB, bottom floor, Suite 1201 ÔÇô Office of Student Media., Fairfax, Virg United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297238
DESCRIPTION:Learn how to record, mix, edit and produce compelling PSAs and promos, whether it's to promote your WGMU Radio show, a campus event, for a social media post, or if it is just a skill you want to know! We will teach you where to find audio clips, how to write a good script, what platforms to use to edit, amongst much more. \nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297238
