UID:a39edd0831cba08b300f53654614ebb62252026_9:56:56_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:GBM & Beyond the Booth: 2026 NSBE Convention Reflection 
LOCATION:Innovation Hall 204, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296526
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Beyond the Booth: 2026 NSBE Convention Reflection, a powerful recap and strategy session following the National Society of Black Engineers National Convention 2026.\n\nThis isn’t just a recap — it’s a debrief, reflection, and growth conversation.\n\nWhether you attended Convention or want to experience it through the stories and lessons of those who did, this event will break down:\n\n• Career Fair wins, lessons, and recruiter insights\n• Workshops that shifted perspectives\n• Networking strategies that actually worked\n• Mistakes to avoid next year\n• How to turn conference momentum into internships, offers, and leadership growth\n\nAttendees who went to Convention will share real experiences — the good, the unexpected, and the game-changing moments. New members will leave understanding how to prepare early, move with intention, and maximize their next national conference experience.\n\nThis is about turning exposure into execution.\nCome reflect, reconnect, and reset your strategy for what’s next.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296526
END:VEVENT
