UID:7cdd8009d7131a99aee2ce2142dd9cfa172026_2:47:10_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Job Search Strategies featuring Dominion Energy
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292180
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a job search workshop featuring Mary Tschirhart, Student Employment Program Coordinator at Dominion Energy. \nIn this dynamic session, we'll delve into proven strategies and essential tools to empower you in your quest for the perfect job or internship. Explore the secrets of targeting the right opportunities and leveraging networking to your advantage. Gain insights into navigating job boards, uncovering hidden job markets, and acing interviews. Elevate your approach to securing internships or full-time positions and set yourself apart in the business world.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292180
END:VEVENT
