SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Book of Revelation Study: What we need to know about the End Times
LOCATION:Spiritual Life Center / Fenwick A202,  4400 University Drive, Johnson Center, Room 239H, MSN 2C7, Fairfax, VA 22030-4444 , United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294535
DESCRIPTION:Jesus said “When you see these things, you know that he is near, at the very gates.  Truly, I say to you, this generation will not pass away until all these things take place.” (Matthew 24:33-34).  What are the signs of the end times, and what is God’s plan for us?  The Book of Revelation has some key answers.  Come and find out!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294535
