SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Culinary x  S26 GBM 5
LOCATION:Hanover Hall, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296325
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our 5th GBM as we team up with Alpha Phi Omega for an event focused on health and community! This collaboration features a refreshing and nutritious menu, including a Custom Lemonade Bar, Ancient Rice and Grain Bowls with fresh toppings, and Build-Your-Own Yogurt Parfaits. Stop by to learn more about APO’s service mission and enjoy a lineup of wholesome, vibrant favorites.\nThe meeting will be Friday, March 27th from 4pm - 6pm.\nIf you are interested, please RSVP and pay the dues using the link that will open one week before the meeting: https://forms.gle/WHhk4soHAopGGLMp9\nWe accept cash and Venmo.\nWe hope to see you all there, and we're excited to cook with you this semester! If you have any concerns or questions, please reach out to our officers through Mason360, Discord, or Instagram. \nWE HOPE TO SEE YOU ALL THERE!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296325
END:VEVENT
