SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Pasaporte Latino
LOCATION:JC Georges, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296974
DESCRIPTION:We will host an event celebrating Hispanic culture through interactive stations where students can explore different traditions and activities. Participants will be able to visit stations featuring Hispanic food, hair braiding, and bracelet making. There will also be dance lessons, Spanish slang mini-lessons, and a cultural map activity where students can learn about different Hispanic and Latin American countries. The goal of the event is to create a fun and engaging space where students can learn about and appreciate the diversity of Hispanic culture.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296974
END:VEVENT
