UID:e0b1e457656e8e36e737815d3a79411e162026_3:49:50_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Athlete Academy
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292123
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Athlete Academy, a high-energy fitness program designed to help you build the complete foundation of an athlete. Whether you’re a seasoned fitness enthusiast or looking to try something new, this program blends training techniques with a team atmosphere to push you to your best.\n\nOver the course of the program, you’ll train and improve the five key components of athletic performance:\n✅ Strength — Develop total-body power and resilience through dynamic resistance training.\n✅ Speed — Learn to move quickly and efficiently with sprint drills and acceleration work.\n✅ Power — Build explosive force for better performance in sports and life.\n✅ Agility — Enhance your ability to change direction, react fast, and move with precision.\n✅ Flexibility — Improve mobility and recovery to keep your body performing at its peak.\n\nEach session is carefully designed to combine these elements into fun, challenging workouts that mimic the way athletes train. You’ll leave each class feeling faster, stronger, and more confident in your abilities.\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292123
END:VEVENT
