URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296839
DESCRIPTION:The Patriot Road Runners Motorcycle Club (PRRMC) will host a meet and greet for students interested in motorcycles, riding culture, and rider safety. This event will allow students to introduce themselves, connect with other riders at GMU, and discuss ideas for future club rides, safety discussions. All GMU students interested in motorcycles are welcome to attend.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296839
