UID:67fa91514717148514909dd53d7fd8ba142026_7:09:44_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Murder at the Masquerade
LOCATION:JC Cinema, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292037
DESCRIPTION:In collaboration with the talented GhostLight Players, step into an immersive Mardi Gras masquerade set in the heart of New Orleans — where elegance meets deception and every guest has something to hide.\n\nThe evening begins in celebration… until a shocking murder brings the festivities to a halt.\n\nNow, the masks remain on, but the truth begins to unravel.\n\nIn this interactive, role-play mystery experience, you won’t just watch the story unfold — you’ll become part of it. Question suspects, analyze motives, uncover hidden clues, and decide for yourself who is telling the truth. With a carefully crafted storyline and live performances woven throughout the night, the line between actor and guest blurs as suspicion fills the room.\n\nBehind every mask is a secret.\nBehind every smile is a motive.\n\nCan you solve the crime before the masquerade ends?\n\n💜💛💚 Masks on. Mystery awaits.\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292037
END:VEVENT
