UID:1956ae550740ba89f97c20dece3ec5f2222026_7:26:39_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Emergency Bleeding Control
LOCATION:Sub-1 3A, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294964
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an EMS Club meeting on Emergency Bleeding Control, focusing on rapid recognition and management of life-threatening hemorrhage. We’ll cover types of bleeding, when and how to use tourniquets, pressure dressings, and wound packing, and why early intervention saves lives. Through practical scenarios, you’ll learn how EMS prioritizes bleeding control in emergencies.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294964
END:VEVENT
