UID:75814dcfbc31197d524e190c74e5dd2d12172025_2:16:59_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Hike to Turkey Run
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291949
DESCRIPTION:Spend the day stretching your legs as we explore one of our region’s scenic spring hiking destinations! This trip offers a refreshing change of pace from campus and an opportunity to take in early-season blooms, forest wildlife, and sweeping views from the trail. Whether you’re new to hiking or just looking to spend a day outdoors, this hike is a great way to enjoy the start of spring. \n\nDifficulty: Beginner – Expect a mix of gentle inclines and rolling terrain for a total of 4–6 miles. Trails may be muddy depending on recent rainfall. \n\nAmenities: Vault toilets are located on the trail close to the beginning of the hike \n\nTravel Time: 30 minutes each way \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291949
END:VEVENT
