UID:21be13a8e0abd5c90d55d7393ec19b8f1132026_1:11:32_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Great Falls Overlook via Billy Goat Trail Section A
LOCATION:Billy Goat Trail Section A, 38.98251834231867,-77.22449898765943
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292465
DESCRIPTION:📏 Distance, Time, & Difficulty\nDistance: ~4.7 – 5.0 miles loop (Billy Goat + Canal Towpath + overlook spur)\nEstimated time: ~2.5 – 3.5 hours (varies with pace & scrambles)\nElevation gain: ~150 – 200 ft (mostly flat but rocky)\nHard (rock scrambling on Billy Goat sections with rugged, uneven terrain + flat towpath sections)\n\n⚠️ Trail Tips\nRock scrambling and boulders on the Billy Goat section. proper hiking shoes ESSENTIAL!!!\nBring snacks and water!!\nDon't overpack, very scrambly parts of the route.\n\n[Link to Alltrails Map!](https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/maryland/billy-goat-loop-and-great-falls-overlook)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292465
END:VEVENT
