SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Handshake Highlight: Connecting with Recruiters
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292086
DESCRIPTION:Ever wish you had access to recruiters at thousands of companies? You do, in Handshake! Recruiters and early talent managers actively engage with George Mason students and job seekers via Handshake’s messaging system every day. In this session, we’ll show you how to find recruiter contact info, what to ask them, and how to follow up in a professional way.  \n\nZoom to join: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/94673727585\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/94673727585\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292086
