URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296085
DESCRIPTION:Cultural Crafts is an interactive event that celebrates traditions from around the world through hands-on art and craft activities. Attendees will explore different cultural techniques, learn the history behind them, and create their own pieces inspired by global traditions. The event encourages cultural appreciation, creativity, and community by bringing people together to share stories and artistic practices from diverse backgrounds.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296085
