UID:e97de9f3d0ef1b5f133bfa940e02075712172025_1:39:13_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:More than a Moment: Women's History Month
LOCATION:Fenwick A Wing A110, 4469 Aquia Creek Ln, Student Union Building 1, Suite 2400, MSN 2F6, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291942
DESCRIPTION:Looking for a bit of book fair nostalgia without the price tag? Celebrate Women’s History Month and stories of womanhood through a book lover's party—college edition!\n\nSwing by Fenwick A110 (Spiritual & Interfaith Center) for a book swap, bookmark making, poetry writing, an open mic, and refreshments! \n\nJoin the Center for Leadership and Intercultural Engagement and Watershed Lit for the Women's History Month edition of More than a Moment on March 30th from 1p.m. to 3 p.m. Writers and readers of all interests and identities are welcome! \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291942
END:VEVENT
