UID:b39a90f9619d072644847ce19a8114fb2252026_1:52:29_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:EY 360 Careers Quest
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296322
DESCRIPTION:Beta Alpha Psi Theta Alpha presents an exclusive networking event with EY, one of the Big Four professional services firms and a global leader in assurance, tax, strategy, and consulting.\n\nEY is committed to building a better working world — helping clients, people, and communities achieve their potential. With over 400,000 professionals across 150+ countries, EY offers unmatched scale, innovation, and career development opportunities.\nJoin us to connect with EY recruiters and professionals who will share insights on:\n\nCareer paths in assurance, tax, strategy & transactions, and consulting\nEY's culture, values, and what makes the firm unique\nInternship and full-time opportunities\nInterview tips and recruiting timelines\n\nThis is your chance to engage directly with one of the world's most prestigious professional services firms and learn how EY can launch your career.\n📅 Monday, March 30, 2026\n🕐 6:00 PM – 8:00 PM\n📍 JC Gold Room\n👔 Business Professional Attire\n🍕 Food Provided\nOpen to all Beta Alpha Psi members and prospective candidates. RSVP required.\nQuestions? Contact bap@gmu.edu\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296322
END:VEVENT
