UID:e90e23f090caf2527596d52d8b7b5ba8352026_6:52:43_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Beyond the Bread and Wine: A Conversation on Holy Communion
LOCATION:Lecture Hall 3, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296857
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wondered about the depth of mystery behind the Eucharist we receive every Sunday? Why do we fast for so long? What does it truly mean when we say "One Body and One Blood"?\n\nJoin the us for a deep and open conversation about the Holy Communion. This isn't a lecture—it's a space for us to ask questions, share our understanding, and grow together in our faith.\n\nWhether you are a new believer or have been receiving Communion since childhood, come let us explore this greatest mystery of our Church together.\n\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296857
END:VEVENT
