URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292448
DESCRIPTION:Ready to get a jump on next semester? Stop by our Academic Planning Workshop for personalized, on-the-spot support with choosing your upcoming courses, understanding requirements, and mapping out your path to graduation.\n\nWhether you need quick guidance on next semester’s schedule or want to work through a full academic plan, we’re here to help. No appointment needed—just drop in, bring your questions, and leave with a clearer, more confident plan for your academic future.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292448
