SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mending Cafe
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296849
DESCRIPTION:Spend an evening up-cycling and mending clothes, bags or anything you own that could get a new life with some glue, paint or stickers. Meet with craft club members and enjoy baked goods and coffee while practicing sustainability! \n\nWe will have fabric glue, paint, sewing supplies, iron on patches, buttons and a host of other craft supplies but feel free to bring any supplies you'd like to use for this project and anything you'd like to share with other crafters! It's a great way to give new life to materials that might otherwise go unused while connecting with fellow crafters in a welcoming, creative environment.\n\nWhether you've never crafted before, you're an expert, or anything in between, please come join us! Everyone is welcome even if you've never been to a craft club meeting before!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296849
END:VEVENT
