UID:056e618fcd659977c356227a69911482322026_12:46:14_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:NSBE x HPR - Escape Room Showdown: Game Night Edition
LOCATION:JC Georges , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296663
DESCRIPTION:Join the National Society of Black Engineers (NSBE) and High Power Rocketry (HPR) for an exciting collaborative event: Escape Room Showdown – Game Night Edition. This interactive event will bring students together for a fast-paced, team-based challenge that combines fun competition with STEM-inspired problem solving. Participants will work in teams to complete a series of timed rounds designed to simulate an escape room experience.\n\nThroughout the event, teams will tackle a variety of challenges including decoding secret phrases, solving logic problems, completing puzzles, and answering trivia questions. Each round encourages teamwork, communication, and strategic thinking as teams compete to earn points and advance toward the final challenge. The goal is not only to solve each task but also to collaborate effectively under time pressure.\n\nThis event is designed to create an engaging environment where students from different organizations and academic backgrounds can connect while practicing valuable skills such as critical thinking, collaboration, and problem solving. By the end of the night, teams will have worked together to navigate the challenges and compete for the top score in a dynamic escape room-style competition.\n\nEscape Room Showdown aims to provide a fun and memorable experience that blends social engagement, friendly competition, and STEM-focused thinking in a welcoming and collaborative atmosphere.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296663
END:VEVENT
