UID:427707ad6d704f537a06fec97ca0ae163162026_10:23:49_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Beyond Machismo
LOCATION:Johnson Center, 333, Meeting Room D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297113
DESCRIPTION:Beyond Machismo is an interactive discussion event that explores how traditional gender expectations affect Latino communities while celebrating the strength, resilience, and cultural values within our culture. Attendees will engage in meaningful conversations about challenging harmful stereotypes, supporting gender equity, and uplifting one another while honoring Latino heritage. The goal of this event is to encourage critical conversations about gender roles while empowering participants to recognize and challenge stereotypes within their communities.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297113
END:VEVENT
