LOCATION:Twin Lakes Golf Course
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297078
DESCRIPTION:GMU Golf Club Spring Outing – Twin Lakes (Oaks Course) ⛳\n\nJoin the GMU Golf Club for our Spring Course Outing at Twin Lakes Golf Course on the Oaks Course. Tee times begin at 11:05 AM on Wednesday, April 1st, with groups going out in 10-minute intervals. (This is not a range outing)\n\nArrive by 10:30 AM if you’d like to warm up with free range balls before the round.\n\nGreens fees and carts are covered, so show up ready to play (with your own clubs). We encourage all skill levels to sign up, but please have knowledge of course etiquette and pace-of-play standards if you intend on showing up!\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297078
END:VEVENT
