SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Wandering Wednesday: Intro to Trail Running 
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291950
DESCRIPTION:Curious about trail running but not sure where to start? Join us for a relaxed introduction to the sport as we jog through local dirt paths and forested trails. Trip leaders will cover efficient running techniques, pacing, and how to navigate uneven terrain. Expect lots of encouragement and a fun, supportive environment. \n\nDifficulty: Beginner – Light jogging at a comfortable pace with opportunities to walk as needed. Total distance 2–4 miles. \n\nTravel Time: 10 minutes each way \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291950
END:VEVENT
