DESCRIPTION:The Professional Panel is an engaging event that connects students with experienced professionals from a variety of industries. Attendees have the opportunity to hear firsthand about career journeys, challenges, and successes, while gaining valuable insights into different career paths. The panel features a moderated discussion followed by a Q&A session, allowing participants to ask questions and receive practical advice on networking, internships, and professional growth. This event aims to inspire, inform, and empower students as they prepare for their future careers.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297181
