UID:8688da28199a0fbbd820be885e4c6dab3182026_3:03:59_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Colombia en Vivo
LOCATION:JC Room D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297247
DESCRIPTION:Colombia en Vivo is an event in Phi Iota Alpha Fraternity, Inc.’s Latin American Initiative (LAI) 2026, designed to celebrate and honor the culture, identity, and resilience of Colombia.\n\nFollowing Colombia in Focus: From Awareness to Action, this event shifts from education to cultural connection by showcasing the richness of Colombian traditions through music, artistic expression, and storytelling. Colombia en Vivo invites attendees to engage with the country beyond statistics and headlines, highlighting the people, heritage, and lived experiences that define it.\n\nThis event serves as a meaningful continuation of the Latin American Initiative, leading into the Miss Latina America Pageant on April 21, where the next country of focus will be selected.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297247
END:VEVENT
