SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Free InBody Friday 
LOCATION:Aquatic and Fitness Center - AFC 118, 4520 Patriot Circle, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292412
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Free InBody Friday! Complete a body composition analysis using the InBody scanner! Gain unique insights into unique health metrics via its bioelectrical impedance analysis as another picture into your fitness progress. No appointment is necessary—just stop by and take the first step toward reaching your goals!\n\nRegistration will be available onsite. The final scan will be completed promptly at 12:00 PM, and the event may close early at the discretion of staff present based on capacity or other factors.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292412
END:VEVENT
