UID:601fab13d314b0deb2b03e2cb91eb8912252026_2:30:59_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:FPA GMU RIA DAY 
LOCATION:JC DEWBERRY SOUTH, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296482
DESCRIPTION:Join us for GMU RIA Day, an exciting all-day event co-hosted by the Financial Planning Association at GMU and Charles Schwab! Whether you're exploring a career in finance, financial planning, or wealth management, this is your chance to learn about GMU's FPWM program, gain insight into the Registered Investment Advisory industry, and network with professionals from 20 wealth management firms. The day kicks off with breakfast and opening remarks at 8:00 AM, followed by a students-only career panel with NextGen and specialized advisors, a broader industry panel discussion, and a buffet lunch — all before an exciting speed networking session where you'll connect one-on-one with 20 advisors. Don't miss this opportunity to build real connections and kickstart your career in wealth management!\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296482
END:VEVENT
