SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:NPHC Step Show
LOCATION:Center For the Arts, 4400 University Drive, MSN 2D6, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295652
DESCRIPTION:The NPHC Step Show is a high-energy performance rooted in African American tradition. Members of the National Pan-Hellenic Council Fraternities and Sororities showcase precision stepping, rhythmic movement, chants, and storytelling. This show celebrates culture, unity, and history while highlighting discipline, teamwork, and pride through powerful, synchronized performances.\n\nGeneral Admission: $19\n\nStudents/Faculty/Staff: $14  \nPrices include fees. \n\nStudents/Faculty/Staff tickets are only available at the ticket office.\nBuy tickets here: https://rb.gy/jktksk\n\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295652
END:VEVENT
