SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Dalton Ebanks Invitational- Track & Field: Day 2 | SHIRT GIVEAWAY FOR THE FIRST 150 STUDENTS!
LOCATION:George Mason Stadium, 4400 University Drive, MS 3A5, George Mason Field House, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2289471
DESCRIPTION:🎉 Patriot Party at the Track 🎉\n\nJoin us for an unforgettable night at the track as we celebrate our seniors and bring the energy for Patriot Party at the Track!\n\n🎟️ FREE admission for all fans\n\n🎓 Senior Night begins at 5:30 PM — come out and help us celebrate our seniors as they take their final lap!\n\n👕 Free T-Shirts for Students\n\nFirst 150 students receive a free t-shirt\nVoucher distribution begins at 4:00 PM\n\n🎉 Fan Activities Include:\n\nBingo\nPoster making\nRaffle prizes (enter for a chance to win!)\n\n🍦 Concessions Available Starting at 12 PM:\n\nBen & Jerry's\nTwo Smooth Dudes\n\nBring your friends, rep your green and gold, and be part of an exciting night as we celebrate our Patriots in style! 💚💛\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2289471
END:VEVENT
