UID:89d910a8b12c4d4ee6c184d4dcb93c81352026_4:33:54_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:DIY Beaded Plant Workshop
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296852
DESCRIPTION:At this workshop you will learn how to create a beaded plant and take home a plant of your own! \n\nEverything you need will be provided but feel free to bring any supplies you'd like to use for this project and anything you'd like to share with other crafters! It's a great way to give new life to materials that might otherwise go unused while connecting with fellow crafters in a welcoming, creative environment.\n\nWhether you've never crafted before, you're an expert, or anything in between, please come join us! Everyone is welcome even if you've never been to a craft club meeting before!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296852
END:VEVENT
