LOCATION:Hub Ballroom, Fairfax Campus, 10423 Rivanna River Way, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297695
DESCRIPTION:This event brings together industry leaders in cybersecurity, AI, and emerging technologies to discuss topics such as AI in security, post-quantum cryptography, and evolving cyber threats. Students will gain direct insights from VPs, CEOs, and senior engineers across leading companies. The event will feature four speaker sessions, followed by an interactive Q&A and networking session, providing valuable opportunities for students to connect with professionals and explore career pathways. \n\nThis event is being hosted in collaboration with University Career Services, George Mason AI Club, SWE, Colorstack at GMYU, and WiCys.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297695
