SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:LUL x LTA Networking Night
LOCATION:JC Room C, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297349
DESCRIPTION:Legacy in Motion: LUL X LTA Networking Night is designed to bring together members of Lambda Upsilon Lambda and Lambda Theta Alpha in a space focused on professional growth, meaningful connections, and community building. The event encourages students and young professionals to network, share experiences, and learn from one another while strengthening unity within the Latino Greek community. Through collaboration and mentorship, attendees gain insight into career paths, leadership development, and opportunities for success. Ultimately, the purpose of the event is to empower individuals to continue building their legacy while staying grounded in culture, service, and brotherhood/sisterhood.\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297349
