SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Build a Kit, Take a Hit
LOCATION:The Hub VIP 2, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297132
DESCRIPTION:The Diverse Hearts of Nursing club invites you to our Build a Kit, Take a Hit event. Build and decorate your own personal first aid kit and compete in a special effects competition. Who will create the most realistic wound? No TV, no slides, just skills. Whether you're a master of the bandage or just want to learn how to make a realistic bruise, you won’t want to miss this.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297132
