UID:93796a71864125ce950842cdfd6416353172026_5:06:34_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:oSTEM Interest Meeting
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297165
DESCRIPTION:oSTEM is the world's largest chapter-based LGBTQ+ professional organization, with over 150 collegiate and professional chapters. We think George Mason should have a chapter too! Joining offers access to scholarships, professional conferences, and a way to build community in your field. Come to the interest meeting to chat with other LGBTQ+ STEM students, add your names to the contact list, and sign up for officer positions!\nFor accommodations that require support from Disability Services, please contact them directly at ods@gmu.edu. If you have accommodation-related questions about the general run of program, please email the Center directly at lgbtq@gmu.edu. \n\nPlease be aware that a 1-week notice is requested as some accommodations may require time for the University to arrange. Learn more about Event Accommodations here https://ds.gmu.edu/event-accessibility/ \nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297165
END:VEVENT
