UID:e7a1482eb4024f9c9980df8ffa7825763232026_3:45:23_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Music on the Green at SciTech
LOCATION:Behind Katherine Johnson on the Schofield Lawn by the Green and White Tent, SciTech Campus, 10900 University Boulevard, Manassas, VA 20110, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297402
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Earth Month! \n\nJoin us on Tuesday, April 7, on the Schofield Lawn behind Katherine Johnson Hall by the Green and White Tent for an afternoon of fun!\n\nLive Music: Enjoy jazz beats from Green & Gold Soul\n\nFree Ice Cream: Ice cream food truck with free ice cream for students while supplies last (we have a vegan option too!)\n\nGiveaways: Spin the wheel for SciTech branded giveaways while supplies last! We have SciTech seed planters in honor of Earth Month and SciTech picnic blankets\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297402
END:VEVENT
