UID:1bac06c2bfb17a11f3a881c76b528c8d8192025_11:56:15_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Perils of Perfectionism 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2286197
DESCRIPTION:While perfectionism seems like a worthy trait to have because it involves hard work and meticulousness, it has its downsides. Pursuing perfection is stressful and time consuming and can actually result in poor academic performance. This session will explore the perils of perfectionism and assist participants in setting more realistic goals. \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/94944535876\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2286197
END:VEVENT
