SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Lebanese Networking Event
LOCATION:JC Dewberry, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297328
DESCRIPTION:Lebanese Networking Night 🇱🇧✨\nJoin us for an inspiring evening of connection, culture, and opportunity at our Lebanese Networking Event! This is your chance to meet Lebanese professionals, alumni, and fellow students across a variety of fields—from healthcare and business to tech and entrepreneurship.\nWhether you’re looking for mentorship, career advice, internships, or simply want to expand your circle within the Lebanese community, this event is the perfect space to build meaningful connections.\nEnjoy light refreshments, engaging conversations, and a welcoming environment that celebrates Lebanese identity and success.\nCome ready to network, learn, and represent 🇱🇧\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297328
END:VEVENT
