UID:75118856c07e8e31bfa309c61f10e0f23252026_7:27:21_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AWS Workshop 
LOCATION:Horizon 3010, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297520
DESCRIPTION:Ready to level up your tech skills and tap into the power of the cloud? Join NSBE for an interactive AWS (Amazon Web Services) Workshop designed to introduce you to one of the most in-demand tools in engineering and tech today.\n\nIn this session, you’ll get a hands-on overview of AWS fundamentals, explore real-world applications in areas like cloud computing, data storage, and infrastructure, and learn how AWS is used across industries—from startups to major corporations. Whether you're new to cloud computing or looking to strengthen your technical skillset, this workshop will give you practical insights and a strong starting point.\n\n💡 What to Expect:\n\nIntroduction to AWS and cloud computing concepts\nLive demo of AWS tools and services\nReal-world applications in engineering & tech careers\nTips on earning AWS certifications and boosting your resume\nQ&A + networking opportunities\n\n🎯 Perfect For:\nStudents interested in tech, engineering, IT, cybersecurity, or anyone looking to gain a competitive edge for internships and full-time roles.\n\nCome build your cloud confidence and take a step toward becoming a future tech leader!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297520
END:VEVENT
