UID:3570fcd9a443bd4a13cdb2a61071e2d13182026_8:01:27_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:The Art of Networking Webinar 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297264
DESCRIPTION:Want to boost your confidence and stand out at networking events? Join us for The Art of Networking webinar on April 8th from 3:00–4:00 PM. This interactive session will begin with a brief presentation on essential networking strategies, followed by a panel of alumni sharing how they successfully navigate large events like the Student & Alumni Networking Mixer. \n\nWhat You’ll Learn: \n\nStrategies for navigating large networking events \n\nHow to leverage alumni connections \n\nKey questions to ask in conversations \n\nFollow-up best practices \n\nUnconventional networking tips \n\nWays to practice networking in everyday life \n\nThis webinar is a great way to prepare for the Student & Alumni Networking Mixer on April 16th and gain the skills you need to connect with confidence.  \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/93435986979?pwd=q1DxOfNMoqlfdYZCWjJm98NVagMkqa.1\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297264
END:VEVENT
