LOCATION:Krasnow 229, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297395
DESCRIPTION:The Neuroscience Club is hosting a Pride Week event to celebrate and support LGBTQ+ students in STEM. The event will highlight the challenges they often face while fostering a welcoming space where students can share their stories, connect with others, and be reminded that they are not alone and that success in these fields is absolutely within reach. Catering from Panera Bread and Tea-Do will be provided, and popcorn will also be available during the movie.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297395
