DESCRIPTION:Join us for a public dialogue on “Democracy in the Americas,” sponsored by the LAS minor and the student organizations LAPS (Latin American Political Society) and HLLA (Hispanic Latine Leadership Alliance.) A public dialogue is not a debate or a roundtable, but rather a facilitated conversation where everyone has the opportunity to share from their own experience and to respectfully listen to others' experiences.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297902
