UID:e257c6c4d8e3ce544e2b9008d0606ada1162026_3:47:07_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:An Evening with Deloitte: Careers & Opportunities
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293234
DESCRIPTION:Beta Alpha Psi Theta Alpha (Est. 1981) presents an exclusive networking event with Deloitte, the largest professional services firm in the world and a member of the Big Four.\n\nDeloitte offers unparalleled career development, global mobility, and the opportunity to work on transformative projects across audit, tax, consulting, and advisory services. Their professionals serve clients ranging from innovative startups to Fortune 500 companies.\n\nJoin us to connect with Deloitte recruiters and professionals who will share insights on:\n- Career paths across Audit & Assurance, Tax, Consulting, and Risk & Financial Advisory\n- Deloitte's culture of learning, leadership, and making an impact that matters\n- Internship and full-time opportunities\n- Interview tips and recruiting timelines\n\nThis is your chance to explore opportunities at a firm recognized as a leader in professional services worldwide.\n- 📅 Wednesday, April 8, 2026\n- 🕐 5:00 PM - 6:30 PM\n- 📍 Private (Upon Registration)\n- 👔 Business Professional Attire\n- 🍕 Food Provided\n\nOpen to all Beta Alpha Psi members and prospective candidates. RSVP required.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293234
END:VEVENT
