UID:49fd24b79df58479dfe330c2a106c00d2112026_1:03:19_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:2026 Lambda Awards
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295659
DESCRIPTION:Join the LGBTQ+ Resources Center for our 2026 Lambda Awards, where we will honor LGBTQ+ leaders in our community. We hope you can come to recognize your George Mason peers who are doing amazing things at a "casual semi-formal" event! We'll be honoring your 2026 Emerging Leaders, Trailblazers, and  Possibility Models and enjoying a light dinner and dessert during the formal recognition program. Please come as you are comfortable but be empowered to "dress up" in whatever affirming way that looks for you!\n\nFor accommodations that require support from Disability Services, please contact them directly at ods@gmu.edu. If you have accommodation-related questions about the general run of program, please email the Center directly at lgbtq@gmu.edu. \n\nPlease be aware that a 1-week notice is requested as some accommodations may require time for the University to arrange. Learn more about Event Accommodations here https://ds.gmu.edu/event-accessibility/ \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295659
END:VEVENT
