UID:9c1c730503b414b5ae40dfdce8a9c7a83302026_3:28:10_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Senior Portraits - Day 3
LOCATION:Gold Room (Johnson Center ground floor), Student Media, George Mason University, The Hub Suite 1201, MS 2C5, 4400 University Drive, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297729
DESCRIPTION:Senior Portraits are back! Join us IN PERSON on the Fairfax campus to commemorate your many achievements with a professional graduation portrait.\n\nAll Mason undergraduates and graduate students welcome!\n\nThese are the final sessions offered before May 2026 Commencement.\n\nReserve your appointment now as space is limited:\n• Tuesday, April 7, 2026 \n   10:00am-6:00pm  | Gold Room (JC ground floor)\n• Wednesday, April 8, 2026\n   10:00am-6:00pm  | Gold Room (JC ground floor)\n• Thursday, April 9, 2026\n   10:00am-6:00pm  | Gold Room (JC ground floor)\n\nExtra Day Added:\n• Friday, April 10, 2026\n   10:00am-6:00pm  | Gold Room (JC ground floor)\n\nReserve your portrait appointment online:\n\n1. Visit c2ms.info/portraits\n2. Scroll to browse available times by day\n3. Select an available time from the list and book your appointment\n\nStudent are encouraged to make an appointment for their Senior Portrait sitting well in advance as space is limited and the most desirable time slots fill up quickly. Walk-ins accepted on a first-come, first-serve basis.\n\nNo sitting fee required, print package prices vary.\n\nDress to impress! Each student will be photographed in both professional attire and cap & gown.\n\nNOTE: Undergraduate cap and gown are provided, but graduate students should bring their own regalia if they wish to be photographed in Commencement garb.\n\nGot a question? Email stumedia@gmu.edu\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297729
END:VEVENT
