SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Global Environmental Awareness
LOCATION:King Hall Rm 2016, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297543
DESCRIPTION:The upcoming Global Environmental Awareness event at George Mason University on April 9th, 2026, from 1:00 PM to 3:00 PM promises to be an enriching and impactful experience for students. As a globally connected campus with a diverse international student body, GMU provides the perfect setting for meaningful conversations about environmental responsibility and sustainability. This event will benefit students in numerous ways, from expanding their global perspectives to inspiring collective action toward protecting our planet. Engaging with environmental issues in such a collaborative space will not only raise awareness but also create a memorable and motivating experience for all who attend.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297543
END:VEVENT
