LOCATION:HUB SIDE POCKET LOUNGE, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297300
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an engaging and informative event designed for students interested in healthcare careers! Scrubs and Certifications is a great opportunity to learn how you can start or continue your university journey while working in the healthcare field.\n\nEnjoy free food while creating your own bouquet, and enter a raffle for a chance to win a free pair of scrubs!\n\nCome learn more about AMWA and get your questions answered about healthcare opportunities, clinical hours for graduate programs, stacking certifications, and the steps to obtaining them. We’ll also discuss how these experiences can benefit your future career and academic goals.\n\nDon’t miss this chance to learn, connect, create, and win!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297300
END:VEVENT
