SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Clearance Ready: Preparing Your Clearance Documents
LOCATION:Merten Hall 1202, Fairfax Campus, 4441 George Mason Blvd University Hall, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291744
DESCRIPTION:If you are applying for a position that requires a security clearance, you will have to fill out security forms such as digital version of the Standard Form 86 (SF-86). This interactive session will provide you the opportunity to engage with security officers who will share tips on how to effectively complete the SF-86. You are encouraged to bring your laptop or tablet to this session. This event is a part of University Career Service’s Clearance Ready Program. For additional information, please visit careers.gmu.edu/clearance.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291744
END:VEVENT
