UID:f8bd11114141cd8605857beffea643ac3202026_11:51:01_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Military-Connected Student Graduate Admissions Information Session (Virtual)
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297309
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a virtual information session designed specifically for U.S. military-connected prospective students, including active duty service members, veterans, spouses, and dependents.\n\nDuring this session, you will learn more about the graduate programs offered at the Costello College of Business at George Mason University. Led by the Director of Graduate Enrollment at the Costello College of Business, the webinar will provide an overview of our graduate business programs, the admissions process, and application timelines.\n\nWe will also be joined by the Associate Director of George Mason University's Office of Military Services, who will discuss the resources and support available to military-connected students.\n\nAttendees will also have the opportunity to ask questions and learn more about the next steps for applying to a graduate business program at George Mason.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297309
END:VEVENT
