UID:225b2b7e28c54c3e43c702cfad7f00ac3202026_11:45:06_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Convention Prep Egg Hunt
LOCATION:JC Room D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297330
DESCRIPTION:The Convention Prep Egg Hunt is a gamified educational workshop designed to prepare members for the upcoming ALPFA Convention through interactive networking and professional development checkpoints. Like an Easter egg hunt, participants will find eggs containing specific questions and answers, requiring them to mingle with one another to discover the benefits of the national convention, such as networking with top companies and attending lectures from Latinx professional leaders. We will provide snacks and drinks to create a social atmosphere where students can learn how to apply their skills in front of recruiters and hear from professionals with similar backgrounds. This interactive format ensures that every attendee is fully prepared to succeed and represent our chapter at the national level.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297330
END:VEVENT
