UID:370f8ec01cfc9572bad087b36d3a679a172026_3:03:29_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Job Search Strategies Workshop featuring Deloitte
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292189
DESCRIPTION:Join us for this interactive virtual workshop featuring GMU alum Megan Farina, Specialist Leader, Cyber and Strategic Risk with Deloitte. \n\nIn this dynamic session, designed specifically for Costello College of Business students, we'll delve into proven strategies and essential tools to empower you in your quest for the perfect job or internship. Explore the secrets of targeting the right opportunities and leveraging networking to your advantage. Gain insights into navigating job boards, uncovering hidden job markets, and acing interviews. Elevate your approach to securing internships or full-time positions and set yourself apart in the business world.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292189
END:VEVENT
