UID:1db9cb57d9c62b1bbfacbe63ae28fd1d432026_12:06:09_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Culinary  S26 GBM 6
LOCATION:Hanover Hall, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297913
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our 6th GBM on April 10th from 4–6 PM in Hanover Hall \n\nOur president’s been missing home a little lately… so naturally, we turned this meeting into a Texas-themed hangout! Come enjoy some Southern comfort favorites like sweet tea, Texas Sunrise (OJ + grenadine), kolaches, and dump cake.\n\nWhether you’re from Texas or just here for the vibes, it’s the perfect chance to relax, connect, and enjoy some good food. Y’all don’t want to miss it! If you are interested please RSVP with the link in our bio and pay the $5 dues.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297913
END:VEVENT
