UID:33dd65109567dd37d02d23a8d39e7eff2172026_11:39:05_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:An Evening with CLA: Careers & Opportunities
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296064
DESCRIPTION:Beta Alpha Psi Theta Alpha (Est. 1981) presents an exclusive networking event with CLA (CliftonLarsonAllen), one of the top 10 largest accounting and professional services firms in the United States.\nCLA is known for its people-first culture, industry specialization, and commitment to helping clients and communities thrive. With over 8,500 professionals nationwide, CLA offers meaningful career paths across a wide range of industries and service lines.\nJoin us to connect with CLA recruiters and professionals who will share insights on:\n\nCareer paths across Audit, Tax, Outsourcing, and Advisory services\nCLA's culture of collaboration, growth, and creating opportunities for its people\nInternship and full-time opportunities\nInterview tips and recruiting timelines\n\nThis is your chance to explore opportunities at a firm consistently ranked among the nation's best places to work in accounting.\n\n📅 Friday, April 10, 2026\n🕐 5:00 PM – 6:30 PM\n📍 Private (Upon Registration)\n👔 Business Professional Attire\n🍕 Food Provided\n\nOpen to all Beta Alpha Psi members and prospective candidates. RSVP required.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296064
END:VEVENT
