UID:fcb6bfab986fd0cd8002574767934ca011182025_11:50:52_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Graduate Student Life Write-In Day at Fairfax
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291435
DESCRIPTION:Looking for a way to make progress on your dissertation, thesis, or paper? Graduate Student Life's Write-In Day will give you group accountability and a space to write with other George Mason graduate students who are also serious about getting writing done. Graduate Student Life will provide the space, structure, meals, coffee, and snacks. You need to bring your computer, any other materials you need, achievable goals, and most importantly, your personal commitment to working diligently and productively. \n\nFor more information about Write-In Day, visit https://graduate.gmu.edu/grad-life/events/write-in. \n\nSpaces are limited! Registration opens Tuesday, March 17 at 10:30 AM and closes Sunday, April 6 at 11:55 PM. Confirmed registrants will be provided additional information, including the location.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291435
END:VEVENT
