SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Spring Herp Walk 
LOCATION: Hemlock Overlook Regional Park, 13220 Yates Ford Rd, Clifton, VA 20124, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297272
DESCRIPTION:Did you know that the VA is home to one of the world's salamander hotspots? Join TWS for a guided herp walk at Hemlock Overlook Regional Park as we look for these salamanders and more as they reemerge for spring! \n\nTransportation is not provided, and parking is available at the park. Meet at the parking lot just past Paradise Springs Winery. Bring clothes you don't mind getting muddy! \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297272
END:VEVENT
