URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297845
DESCRIPTION:We’re excited to announce The Bloom, George Mason Esports’ premier multi-day LAN tournament featuring top collegiate competition, live matches, and a full weekend of events.\n\n\n🌸 Day 3 – April 12\n•Valorant Upper Finals, Lower Round 3 + Lower Finals — 9:00 AM – 2:00 PM\n•League Finals (BO3) — 12:30 PM – 3:00 PM\n• :Clash Royale Playoffs — 2:30 PM – 5:00 PM\n• Overwatch Finals (BO7) — 4:00 PM – 6:00 PM\n• Valorant Grand Finals (BO3) — 7:00 PM – 9:30 PM\n\n🎉 EXTRA ACTIVITIES\n• Smash setups\n• Yard Pong\n• Cornhole\n• VR + Casual Games\n• Reaction Games\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297845
