UID:4828ffcc0864543cc468c6ff547754b73172026_12:13:50_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Major Fair
LOCATION:G101 Matz Hall, G405, George Mason University Korea, Songdomunhwa-ro 119-4, Yeonsu-gu, Incheon, 21985, Korea, South
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297143
DESCRIPTION:**Event Description (4–5 lines):**\n\nThe Major Fair is an interactive academic event designed to connect Mason Korea students with major representatives across departments. Through direct conversations, students can explore curricula, concentration options, and academic pathways, including minors and potential major changes. The event aims to simplify access to essential academic information that is often difficult to find, while fostering cross-departmental understanding. By encouraging open dialogue and comparison among majors, the fair supports students in making informed and strategic decisions about their academic future.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297143
END:VEVENT
