SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Que Son Hombres
LOCATION:JC Room F, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297676
DESCRIPTION:The Aguilas Mentoring Program will host a discussion about what society teaches about being a man and how these ideas affect people. Students will talk about toxic masculinity, men's mental health, and how masculinity relates to race and culture in a safe, private space. The event will help students connect with each other and think about how these beliefs shape their own lives.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297676
