SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Anti Hate Interfaith Panel
LOCATION:Spiritual and Interfaith Center (Fenwick A Wing), 4469 Aquia Creek Ln, Student Union Building 1, Suite 2400, MSN 2F6, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298083
DESCRIPTION:Harm doesn't belong to one community - and neither does healing.\nJoin us for an interfaith panel of students and community members on trauma, bias, and solidarity across difference.\n\nLet's learn, reflect, and build a community rooted in care and belonging - together.\n\nWe are offering two organizations with the highest number of attendees and RSVPs $800 of co-sponsorship funds to go towards any of your spring or fall event of your choosing.  Linked ​​​here​​ ​ are our co-sponsorship funding parameters and restrictions. \n\nIf you are not apart of a registered student organization no worries, we are also raffling off $50 to two individual students.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298083
END:VEVENT
