UID:1f86a8d1526b49e1b8aebf8208fef52a2272026_11:42:10_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Brain Awareness Fair! (04/13)
LOCATION:Krasnow Institue (rm 229 and Great Room), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296613
DESCRIPTION:Join Nu Rho Psi for our (newly rescheduled) & exciting Brain Awareness collaboration event - bringing together neuroscience and psychology RSOs for an evening of fun, interactive activities, great conversations, and brainy discoveries! Come explore hands-on experiences, meet new people, and learn more about what makes your brain so incredible - all while networking with students, researchers, and faculty.\n\nWe’re also shining a spotlight on the GMU neuroscience community and the amazing work happening within the department, so it’s the perfect chance to get inspired, ask questions, and discover opportunities to get involved. Plus, there will be snacks and refreshments.\n\n📍 Krasnow Institute for Advanced Study\n🗓 April 13\n⏰ 5:30 PM\n\nBring a friend, come curious, and get ready for a fun night celebrating the brain 🧠✨\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296613
END:VEVENT
