SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Internship Success 101
LOCATION:The Hub Room 1 and 2, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297623
DESCRIPTION:This event is held for students who have an upcoming internship or are interested in learning about what makes a student into a professional. Topics of discussion may include: navigating corporate culture and expectations, understanding and using corporate language effectively, strategies for securing a return offer, making a strong and lasting professional impression, and email etiquette.\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297623
END:VEVENT
