SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:ColorStack Study Session
LOCATION:Planetary Hall, Room 127, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297737
DESCRIPTION:Join ColorStack GMU for a focused Study Session designed to help you stay on track, get support, and lock in for the semester 📚💻\n\nWhether you’re preparing for exams, working through assignments, or just need a productive environment, this is your space to study alongside a supportive community of peers. We’ll have dedicated time for independent work, plus opportunities to ask questions, collaborate, and get help from other students.\n\n💡 What to Expect:\n• A quiet, productive study environment\n• Peer support and collaboration\n• Help with coursework, concepts, and problem-solving\n• Degree audit guidance & academic planning (if applicable)\n\n🎯 Perfect For:\nAnyone looking to stay accountable, improve their understanding, and build consistency in their academic routine.\n\nCome through, bring your friends, and let’s lock in together 💪\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297737
END:VEVENT
