UID:9fbfd82ff6f5c30caac9851c4aa80097412026_3:11:39_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Money Smart Day 
LOCATION:Fairfax: SUB I Quad (Rain Location: Patriot's Lounge), Mason Square Plaza, SciTech Plaza, Student Union Building I, Suite 3200 , United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297839
DESCRIPTION:Join us for 2 days of fun and education surrounding Financial Well-Being across all three GMU campuses!\n\nTuesday, April 14th: Kick off Money Smart Day with outdoor tabling and activities at all three GMU campuses- Fairfax, Sci-Tech, and Mason Square. The kick off event will be held outdoors from 11:00AM-2:00PM on each campus, with a backup indoor location in case of rain.\n\nWednesday, April 15th: This day is dedicated to educational sessions on financial well-being topics. These sessions include 2 in-person presentations with a virtual component and 1 all-virtual presentation.\nHow to Budget and Manage Credit: 12:00PM–1:00 PM | JC 337, Room G [Virtual link will be provided]\nSalary Negotiation and Career Strategies: 3:00PM–4:00PM | Mason Square [Virtual link will be provided]\nFirst Time Home-Buying and Financing: 6:00PM – 7:00PM | Virtual Only [Link will be provided]\n\nWin Prizes!\nThis year, SSAC is partnering with SoFi to offer one qualifying GMU student a $5,000 scholarship! Register and attend one entire Money Smart Day session on April 15th to be entered to win. Note you must be a currently enrolled student to receive the scholarship.\nAdditionally, one lucky student will win our drawing for a new iPad! To be entered, you must register and attend one entire Money Smart Day session on April 15th. Note you must be a currently enrolled student to win the drawing.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297839
END:VEVENT
