SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Perils of Perfectionism
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293427
DESCRIPTION:While perfectionism seems like a worthy trait to have because it involves hard work and meticulousness, it has its downsides. Pursuing perfection is stressful and time consuming and can actually result in poor academic performance. This session will explore the perils of perfectionism and assist participants in setting more realistic goals. \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/94944535876\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293427
