URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2284820
DESCRIPTION:The Leadership Certificate Series is a virtual program open to Mason students, faculty, staff, and alumni. Participants will explore their personal leadership values, develop skills in emotional intelligence and team collaboration, and learn how to lead with purpose and impact. Through interactive sessions and a supportive cohort model, this series offers opportunities to connect with others, reflect on strengths, and grow as a confident, socially conscious leader.\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/95240143661\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2284820
