SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:DECA Meet, Eat & Connect
LOCATION:Johnson Center, Gold Room , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297742
DESCRIPTION:This event is designed to create a welcoming and engaging environment for DECA members to connect, build relationships, and strengthen our chapter community. Attendees will have the opportunity to socialize, enjoy food, and network with fellow members while learning about DECA’s goals, events, and plans for the upcoming school year. The event will also serve as a platform to introduce leadership opportunities, competition pathways, and ways for members to get involved. Overall, the goal is to increase member engagement, foster a sense of belonging, and set a positive tone for the year ahead\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297742
