DESCRIPTION:This event is catered to helping all students make new friends in a different environment. The participants will sit in a line/table. One side will rotate. Between each rotation, there will be 1-2 minutes for participants to write on their cards about what they liked/didn't like about that person (for personal notes). Each round would last 5 minutes. At the end of the event, we will leave the floor open for people to freely mingle. Snacks will be provided at each table throughout the event. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297829
