UID:6c121a0f15d4f22a8445e7991ad894633272026_12:19:05_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Peel and Play
LOCATION:HUB VIP 1, 10423 Rivanna River Way, Fairfax 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297589
DESCRIPTION:Feeling the pre-finals pressure? Don't let the end-of-semester stress drive you bananas! Slip away from the study guides and join the GAIN club for Peel and Play: A Peaceful Potassium Party.\n\nWe’re prescribing a massive dose of relaxation (and a literal mountain of 40 lbs of free bulk bananas) to help you boost your brainpower and bounce back from burnout. Grab a healthy snack, pick up a controller, and drift your worries away with some low-stakes, friendly Mario Kart. Not a racer? Unwind with our chill mini-games or just hang out and enjoy the appealing atmosphere.\n\nIt's the perfect pit stop to hit the brakes on finals panic and catch your breath!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297589
END:VEVENT
