SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:EfID International Meeting
LOCATION:Nguyen Engineering Building Room 3507, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294380
DESCRIPTION:Join Engineers for International Development (EfID) at George Mason University for a meeting on our international water infrastructure project in Costa Rica. We’ll cover project updates, design work, logistics, and ways to get involved as we work with a rural community to improve access to clean drinking water.\nAll majors and experience levels are welcome. Come learn more and be part of a project that makes a real-world impact!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294380
