URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297430
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever felt stuck — unmotivated or unsure how to move forward? You’re not alone.\n\nJoin us for Mental Health Talk III: Getting Unstuck – Finding Motivation When You Feel Stuck, a practical and conversation-based session designed to help you understand why you feel stuck and learn simple strategies to get started again.\n\n🍱 Lunch provided for RSVP participants. Walk-ins are welcome, but lunch availability is not guaranteed.\n\nTake the first step toward getting unstuck and reconnecting with your motivation!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297430
