SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Healing Space - April
LOCATION:Spiritual and Interfaith Center, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296980
DESCRIPTION:Join the Office of Access, Compliance & Community, Faculty Affairs, Human Resources & Center for Leadership & Intercultural Engagement and the College for Visual & Performing Arts for a time to pause, connect and relax. Faculty, Staff and Students are welcome to stop by the Spiritual Interfaith Center on March 24 and April 15 from 12p - 3p to enjoy activities centered around well-being.\n \nStop by and enjoy:\nMeditation\nMindful Coloring\nSensory-friendly activities\nThought provoking discussions\n \nThis is a great opportunity to build community, have fun and relax\nWe hope to see you there!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296980
END:VEVENT
