URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296670
DESCRIPTION:Thinking about grad school but not sure where to start? Join our Graduate School Workshop hosted in collaboration with Graduate Student Life. It is designed especially for first-gen students getting ready to level up. We’ll break down the process, share insider tips, and help you turn “maybe someday” into a real plan. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296670
