URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297795
DESCRIPTION:Join the Vietnamese Student Association (VSA) for a vibrant Fan Dance Workshop celebrating culture, creativity, and community! Whether you have dance experience or are just looking to try something new, this workshop is a fun, low-pressure space to learn choreography, build confidence, and connect with fellow students. You’ll also gain insight into the cultural significance of fan dance and its role in Vietnamese performances and celebrations.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297795
