SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Global Village & Global Headlines
LOCATION:JC Gold Room , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297144
DESCRIPTION:What is the significance of a waterway, thousands of miles away?  Discuss and exchange views, general and specific.\nWe are globally interconnected and we can feel the ripple effect.  When transportation costs go up at the gas pump, the price of everything else follows.\nIt's as if the globe, this Earth is a village.. or as the saying goes: "it's a small world after all!"\nJoin us for a bite to eat, chat and solve world problems.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297144
END:VEVENT
