UID:451d4960044ed7652e988e9b6f9ffc2e3312026_1:08:07_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:General Body meeting: Hearts for Humanity 
LOCATION:JC room 327, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297776
DESCRIPTION:At this general body meeting, members will come together to deepen their understanding of Hearts for Humanity’s mission and the impact we strive to make within both the Mason community and the greater Northern Virginia area. We will highlight upcoming service opportunities, including details about our next mission day, and provide clear ways for members to get involved and take on active roles in serving others.\n\nIn addition to sharing information, members will participate in a meaningful, hands-on service activity that directly contributes to our outreach efforts. This allows students to not only learn about service, but to actively practice it in a collaborative and engaging environment. The meeting will also create space for connection, encouraging members to build relationships, share ideas, and grow in their commitment to making a difference.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297776
END:VEVENT
