UID:cbfdd37d0a59a13e1dc454cedee9f4c1432026_9:53:43_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Technical Analysis with Svein Backer
LOCATION:Innovation Hall, 206, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297955
DESCRIPTION:The Investment Club is excited to welcome Svein Backer from Lockheed Martin Investment Management Company for an exclusive speaker session on technical analysis in institutional investing. \n\nSvein will provide insight into how professional investors use technical indicators, price action, and market trends to inform investment decisions. Drawing from his experience managing large-scale portfolios, he will break down how technical analysis is applied in real-world asset management environments and how it complements fundamental analysis. \n\nThis session is a great opportunity for students interested in equity research, trading, and portfolio management to gain practical knowledge and ask questions directly to an industry professional. \nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297955
END:VEVENT
