UID:44c823ea0732f782128f16a6e4b96b54172026_3:07:46_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AI in the Job Search featuring Deloitte
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292192
DESCRIPTION:Join us for this interactive virtual workshop featuring GMU alum Megan Farina, Specialist Leader, Cyber and Strategic Risk with Deloitte.  \n\nIn this workshop, designed specifically for Costello College of Business students, we'll explore how artificial intelligence can revolutionize the way you approach finding your next job. This workshop is designed to equip you with cutting-edge strategies and tools to enhance your job search efficiency and effectiveness.\n\nDuring each session, you'll learn how to utilize AI-powered platforms for:\n-resume and cover letter building\n-job matching and search optimization\n-interview preparation\n-understanding and leveraging applicant tracking systems (ATS).\n\nOur expert career advisors will demonstrate practical applications that can give you a competitive edge in today's job market.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292192
END:VEVENT
