LOCATION:The Source, Katherine Johnson 122, SciTech Campus, 10890 George Mason Circle, Manassas, VA 20110, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293061
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars! Drop-in hours with Office of Fellowships are happening at the Source (Katherine Johnson 122). Don't miss this chance to learn about exciting academic and professional opportunities.\n\nFinal exams, papers, and projects are right around the corner and we’ve got just the thing to help you recharge. Stop by and pick up supplies for your own DIY Final Exam Kit. We'll have snacks and small giveaways to help you stay grounded and prepared as we head into the end of the semester.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293061
