SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Arabic Calligraphy Club Workshop
LOCATION:Johnson Center, 327, Meeting Room C, Fairfax Campus, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293180
DESCRIPTION:Participants will learn the basics of Arabic calligraphy, which includes basic letter forms, strokes, and composition with an instructor. This is open to all skill levels, no prior experience needed. Materials will be provided, and attendees will leave with their own finished calligraphy piece. \nCome learn the beauty and history of Arabic script in a welcoming and creating environment!\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293180
