UID:27365dfbf875e967af6aa136b92fe78a412026_12:38:02_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:SSA Action
LOCATION:The HUB, Ballroom, Back, Fairfax Campus, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297831
DESCRIPTION:Sudan Action Week is an event hosted by the Sudanese Student Association dedicated to raising awareness about Sudan through ongoing discussions and educational engagement. Throughout the event, attendees will participate in continuous conversations highlighting Sudan’s rich culture, history, and unique traditions, while also addressing the ongoing conflict and the challenges faced by the Sudanese population. Educational videos will be played throughout to provide additional context and insight. This event aims to both celebrate Sudan’s heritage and inform the campus community about current issues, fostering awareness, empathy, and meaningful dialogue. Our guests will be fed during the entire event, as it will be a long one.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297831
END:VEVENT
