SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Fusion360 - Introduction to 3D Modeling
LOCATION:Horizon Hall 1408 (The MIX), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295013
DESCRIPTION:Teach you the basics of 3D modeling using Fusion360 software. Basic understanding about CAD is recommended but not required. \nBring your laptop  with Fusion360 installed and a reliable mouse.\n\nYou can download free version of Fusion360 for student from the link below after verify using GMU email\nhttps://www.autodesk.com/education/edu-software/fusion \n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295013
