UID:727eee9159f50755aa6dcbffbb26b7da482026_10:41:09_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Ask the Professionals: Banking & Finance
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298078
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Ask the Professionals: Banking & Finance featuring a panel of professionals from Northwest Federal Credit Union!\n\nThis interactive session will give you a behind-the-scenes look at careers in banking and finance through the real experiences of industry professionals. Panelists will share their career journeys, what led them to Northwest Federal Credit Union, and what a typical day in their roles looks like. You’ll also gain insight into why a career in finance is worth considering, opportunities for professional growth, and how you can get started.\n\nCome prepared to hear honest advice they wish they knew in college—and bring your questions for a live Q&A at the end!\n\nWhether you’re exploring career options or ready to take your next step, this is a great opportunity to learn, connect, and get inspired.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298078
END:VEVENT
