UID:57e2f4154771f55c277da292940f6d83352026_11:03:31_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:🎉 Grand Opening: The Activities Building 🎉
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296864
DESCRIPTION:George Mason students, faculty, and staff — come check out the brand new Activities Building and celebrate with us!\n\nJoin us for the official ribbon-cutting ceremony with President Washington as we open this exciting new space for student life at George Mason.\n\nStick around for an afternoon packed with fun as we showcase the many ways this building will bring the community together:\n\n🎶 Green Machine performances\n🎮 Nintendo Switch gaming\n🎨 Crafts & novelty artists\n⛳ Mini golf & giant chess\n🎲 Tabletop gaming & recreational activities\n🎧 Live DJ\n🎭 Registered Student Organization performances\n🍕 FREE pizza & sweet treats\n🎁 Games and prizes\n\nCome explore the space, hang out with friends, and experience one of the newest places for connection, creativity, and student engagement at George Mason.\n\nBring your friends and celebrate with us — we can’t wait to see you there! 💚💛\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296864
END:VEVENT
