UID:97a3fbd87fd801bcd3516f8cc97bcf47172026_3:10:47_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Turn Strengths into Success: How to Stand Out in Your Job Search & Beyond
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292193
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an interactive workshop tailored for Costello College of Business students!\nDiscovering your unique strengths is key to building and maintaining a successful career. This workshop will help you better understand how to apply the CliftonStrengths in professional settings.\n\nThis engaging session will provide practical strategies for connecting your top strengths to your career goals, highlighting them in resumes and interviews, and using them to thrive in team environments. Whether you’re exploring career paths or preparing to enter the job market, this workshop is a valuable opportunity to gain clarity on what makes you stand out.\n\nPre-requisite: use this link to identify your specific CliftonStrengths before attending the workshop.\n\nThis virtual workshop takes place on Zoom. Pre-registration required.\n \nQuestions? Contact Costello College of Business Office of Career Services at mycareer@gmu.edu or 703-993-2140. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292193
END:VEVENT
