SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Black Excellence Gala
LOCATION:JC Dewberry, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296668
DESCRIPTION:The Black Excellence Gala is an elegant evening dedicated to honoring and celebrating the achievements, leadership, and lasting impact of Black Mason. This special event brings together community members, leaders, and supporters to recognize excellence across various fields, including service, scholarship, entrepreneurship, and advocacy. The Gala serves as both a celebration and a reflection, highlighting the dedication, resilience, and commitment that define Black excellence while uplifting individuals who continue to inspire, lead, and create meaningful change within our communities. Join us for a night of recognition, culture, and empowerment as we celebrate legacy, leadership, and the ongoing pursuit of excellence.\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296668
END:VEVENT
