UID:c821217b44b36f4e4751376527802ff03252026_7:19:54_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Bridging the Gap: Students & Engineering Panel
LOCATION:Horizon 4014, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297519
DESCRIPTION:Attendees will take part in a live panel discussion featuring engineering professionals from different backgrounds who will share their career journeys, daily responsibilities, challenges, and advice for students preparing to enter the field. The event will also include an interactive Q&A and networking session, giving students the chance to ask questions, build connections, and gain direct insight into internships, career preparation, and professional growth. Food and refreshments will be provided so attendees can enjoy a welcoming and engaging environment while connecting with panelists and peers. By the end of the event, students will leave with a better understanding of engineering career paths, industry expectations, and the skills needed to succeed, along with valuable advice and connections that can support their future goals.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297519
END:VEVENT
