UID:a02d19fccc5ab791532da8be124c2dca132026_10:26:57_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Writing Center Friday Graduate Write-In—Spring 2026
LOCATION:Johnson Center 227E (Fairfax Campus) or on Zoom, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292029
DESCRIPTION:Calling all Mason graduate students! Starting January 28th, every Wednesday evening and Friday morning throughout the semester, graduate students gather to write together for support and accountability! \n\nThis is the event registration for a Friday write-in. Writers can join us online or in person each Friday from 9:30am-1:00pm. We are located on the second floor of the Johnson Center, room 227E, for those who are looking for a quiet and productive space to meet on campus. \n\nWriters bring a set of goals and a commitment to arrive on time and remain for the entire session. We begin with a short conversation about goals and end with a short wrap-up on accomplishments. The remaining time is dedicated to writing. A Writing Center consultant coordinates the session and takes short consultations with writers who request them.\n\nIf you're looking for group accountability and regular time to write with other Mason graduate students who are also serious about making progress on their writing goals, sign up for any number of sessions. You may schedule just one or two sessions to get started on a course project, or attend all 26 to give yourself regular, structured time to work on a thesis, dissertation, or other writing project.\n\nIf you register for a write-in, you are committing to:\n-Join on time and to stay for the duration\n-Turn off access to Facebook, online games, and other computer/online-based distractions during writing time\n-Minimize distractions by phone by limiting texting and phone calls to scheduled break times\n-Contribute to a supportive writing community among fellow participants\n\nPlease register ahead of time and indicate whether you'll be attending in person or on Zoom. If you register and then realize you can't make it, please cancel your Mason360 reservation and let the coordinator (jwiggi@gmu.edu) know in advance. The Zoom link is: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/97660056638\n\nTo sign up for a write-in, register here on Mason360 for the dates you'd like. Please email the writing coordinator Jessie (jwiggi@gmu.edu) with questions. The write-ins are open to Mason graduate students only.\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/97660056638\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292029
END:VEVENT
