UID:7fc85c40d3f899e155405f39460ebd01432026_11:51:21_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Spring Daywalk
LOCATION:The HUB, Student Involvement Office, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297935
DESCRIPTION:Join us on April 17th in the HUB from 1:30 to 3:30 for our Spring Daywalk! This event has been a 30-year Student Government tradition. Every semester, members of Student Government and select administrators come together to locate safety issues across campus. This Daywalk will be focused on accessibility issues. We will also have a couple of groups focused on Sustainability Issues. \n\nWe will start my meeting in the HUB Student Involvement Office at 1:30 so that everyone can meet their groups. Food will be provided by Moe's Southwest Grill!. The walk will begin at 2:15 and end at around 3:30. If you have any questions, please email me at ccolli9@gmu.edu.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297935
END:VEVENT
