UID:153a7e29498c0ac6c8a15dbda80a3bed1232026_11:27:52_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Global Career Accelerator Information Session
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293990
DESCRIPTION:The Global Career Accelerator equips students with in-demand skills in applied technology and intercultural communication (ICC). Through live collaboration with peers from over 50 countries, participants learn to work in diverse, remote teams and build inclusive products. The program focuses on three core areas: global experience, applied learning, and ICC.\nStudents will develop these skills through a combination of interactive LiveLabs, reflective assignments, and real-world projects aligned with the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (UNSDGs).\nStudents can choose from four technical skills tracks to specialize\nin key competencies and have access to unique global projects:\n● Global Data Analytics\n● Global Digital Marketing\n● Global Coding for Data\n● Global Web Development for Everyone\n● Global Career Rotation\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/96553042265?pwd=ZeFzYt3HAE8BobbiobKrLrlB5hzwEk.1\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293990
END:VEVENT
