DESCRIPTION:IMPORTANT: Please RSVP in Mason360 and complete the Graduate Participation Form using the QR code in the event flyer or the following link. You will also receive a Mason360 confirmation email with the link: https://forms.office.com/r/GWz6vqq31C\n\nContemporary Student Services and the Office of Military Services invite you to a special graduation celebration honoring Contemporary and Military Students. Graduates will be featured in a graduate slide show (upon completion of the Participant Form) and receive their CSS and/or OMS cords during a recognition ceremony. \n\nRepresentatives from University Career Services and the Office of Advancement and Alumni Relations will also be on-site to share information and resources for Mason Alumni!\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297329
