SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:NCNW N-Terest Meeting 
LOCATION:ENTERPRISE HALL ROOM 174, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297772
DESCRIPTION:Please come join NCNW Membership to learn more about how to join the organization, applications, dues, and more! During this event, attendees will have the opportunity to engage with current members, ask questions about the membership process, and learn about the mission and impact of NCNW on campus and beyond. We will also provide an overview of upcoming programs, leadership opportunities, and ways to get involved in advocacy and service initiatives. Food will be provided, including Chick-fil-A, to create a welcoming and engaging environment for all attendees. This event is important to the Mason community because it fosters connection, empowerment, and support for women of color while promoting leadership, service, and community engagement.\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297772
END:VEVENT
