SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Clarendon FitFest 2026
LOCATION:Mason Square Plaza, 3351 Fairfax Drive, Van Metre Hall 222, Arlington 22201, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296685
DESCRIPTION:Clarendon FitFest 2026 is a free, community-centered wellness event bringing together George Mason University, Pacers, the Clarendon Alliance, and the greater Arlington community to promote active living and holistic health.\n\nThe event features a Pacers 5K run and 2-mile walk beginning at 8:00 a.m., along with live fitness demonstrations, interactive wellness activities, and tabling from local fitness and wellness businesses.\n\nJoin us at Mason Square Plaza on Saturday, April 18, 2026, from 8:00 a.m. to 12:30 p.m. to connect, move, and celebrate health together.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296685
END:VEVENT
