SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Bird Banding @ SCBI
LOCATION:Smithsonian Conservation Biology Institute, Front Royal, VA, 1500 Remount Road , Front Royal, VA 22630, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297273
DESCRIPTION:Join TWS alum Bernadette Rigley for a bird banding demonstration on the campus of the Smithsonian Conservation Biology Institute (SCBI) in Front Royal, VA. This is peak time for spring migration, so this will be a great chance to see some of these migrants up close while learning about the conservation work being done on the SCBI campus!\n\nREISTRATION US REQUIRED as names need to be submitted to SCBI for access to the property a week in advance. Transportation is not provided but parking will be available on site. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297273
END:VEVENT
