URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297997
DESCRIPTION:After completing the MIX Welder Training, students can use the MIG welders in the School of Art Sculpture Lab SOA Building L006 on select Monday's between 2-4pm with the assistance of Prof. Brian Davis. The MIX Welder training is a requirement. If you haven't completed the training you will be turned away from Open Work Hours. Remember to wear closed toed shoes, if you have long hair to tie it back, and limit loose clothing.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297997
