SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:🚲 Bike to Mason - Fairfax Campus
LOCATION:Merten Hall Front Lawn, 4441 George Mason Blvd, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296982
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Bike to Mason at the Fairfax Campus! Ride your bike to campus on April 21 and stop by our event table to celebrate sustainable commuting. We’ll have free food, fun giveaways, and helpful bike resources to support your ride.\n\nWhether you’re a daily cyclist or trying it for the first time, this is a great opportunity to connect with the biking community and learn more about biking at Mason.\n\nCome by, grab some goodies, and enjoy the ride! 🚴‍♂️✨\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296982
END:VEVENT
