LOCATION:Northern Neck , United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297548
DESCRIPTION:Slice of Mason Day is a pop up event designed to get students excited for Mason Day. We will be parked on campus with the SI2GO truck handing out free pizza slices while talking to students about what is coming up including performances, activities, and everything you do not want to miss. It is a quick and easy way to grab food, learn more about Mason Day, and start building excitement across campus. Whether you are already planning to go or just hearing about it, this event is all about spreading the word and getting everyone ready for Mason Day.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297548
