UID:9544413c539ff3a068eeffc6579144bf422026_9:01:11_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AWS Image Generation Workshop
LOCATION:JC Gold Room, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297888
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exciting AWS Image Generation Workshop where creativity meets cutting-edge technology! In this hands-on session, you’ll explore how to use Amazon Web Services tools to generate stunning AI-powered images from simple text prompts.\n\nWhether you're interested in design, marketing, or just curious about AI, this workshop will guide you through the fundamentals of image generation, how these models work, and how to apply them in real-world projects. You'll get the chance to experiment, create your own visuals, and learn practical skills that are increasingly in demand across industries.\n\nNo prior experience is required—just bring your curiosity and creativity!\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297888
END:VEVENT
