LOCATION:THE SOURCE, ROOM NO. 122 KATHERINE G. JOHNSON HALL, SCITECH CAMPUS, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297555
DESCRIPTION:Looking to meet fellow graduate students at the SciTech campus? Join GAPSA for a fun evening of speed friending, games, and great conversations! You’ll rotate through quick 2-minute chats with different people using fun conversation cards—perfect for breaking the ice and making new connections.\n\nEnjoy snacks, refreshments, and a spin-the-wheel prize game while mingling with other grad students. Whether you come with friends or on your own, GAPSA welcomes you to connect, relax, and meet new people in the SciTech graduate community.\n\nDate: April 21\nTime: 5:30 PM – 7:00 PM\nLocation: The Source, Room no. 122 Katherine G. Johnson Hall, SciTech Campus\n\nCome connect, chat, and make some new grad-school friends with GAPSA SciTech!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297555
END:VEVENT
