SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:ALPFA x AMA: Reframing Your Experience with Intention 
LOCATION:Hub Rooms 1 and 2, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297907
DESCRIPTION:Join Association of Latino Professionals For America (ALPFA) and the American Marketing Association (AMA) for an interactive workshop focused on helping students confidently explain their experiences in professional settings.\n\nThis session will break down how to turn your involvement—whether it’s clubs, projects, jobs, or internships—into a clear and impactful story. Using a simple 5-step framework and marketing concepts, you’ll learn how to present yourself in a way that stands out to recruiters and in networking conversations.\n\nCome ready to engage, practice, and walk away with a stronger understanding of how to market your experience.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297907
END:VEVENT
