SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:NSBE Digital Grind: Notion for Productivity + Internships
LOCATION:Innovation Hall 132, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297564
DESCRIPTION:Struggling to stay organized, keep up with assignments, or prepare for internship season? This event is designed to help you take control of your academic and career success using one powerful tool—Notion.\n\nJoin NSBE for an interactive workshop where you’ll learn how to build a personalized system to manage your classes, track assignments, and stay ahead on exam prep. We’ll also guide you through creating a custom internship and resume tracker, perfect for staying organized and prepared for Summer 2027 opportunities.\n\nThrough live demos and hands-on activities, you’ll walk away with practical study strategies, including time management techniques and productivity hacks that actually work. Plus, enjoy fun games, challenges, and prizes as we bring energy to learning how to work smarter—not harder.\n\nCome ready with your laptop and leave with a system built for success.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297564
END:VEVENT
