SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Art for Advocacy
LOCATION:JC Meeting Room D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297760
DESCRIPTION:Join the UNICEF Club this Earth Month for a special screening of the award nominated documentary It Takes A Child (via GMU DocuSeek). This film follows a young activist who travels to South Asia in an attempt to help transform their communities and fight for the environment. \n \nAs we watch, we’ll be getting creative by decorating mini flower pots with markers and decorative stickers to represent the "seeds of change" we want to plant in our own community. All supplies are provided! Come for the art, stay for the inspiration, and leave with a reminder that you are never too young to make a difference.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297760
END:VEVENT
