SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Earth Day Closet Exchange
LOCATION:SUB 1 QUAD, Mason Recreation - RAC, 4350 Banister Creek Ct, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2289219
DESCRIPTION:Are you ready for a closet refresh or looking to declutter your wardrobe? All students, faculty, and staff are invited to participate in the Well-being Closet Exchange event! Join us on Earth Day for a sustainable experience where you can swap out your gently used clothing items for new-to-you pieces. It's a fantastic opportunity to give back to the planet while updating your wardrobe with second-hand fashion finds. Don't miss out on this eco-friendly event!\n\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2289219
END:VEVENT
