URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295802
DESCRIPTION:Prioritize your peace of mind on April 22nd from 12:00 PM to 2:00 PM in SUB1, Room 3B. This event features a dedicated 30-45 minute presentation from a CAP representative, offering essential strategies for managing stress and improving your mental well-being. It’s a great opportunity to connect with mental health professionals and discover the support systems available to you at Mason. To make the afternoon even better, we’ll be providing free Chick-fil-A for all participants!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295802
