SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Donut Fundraiser for Sudan
LOCATION:JC Kiosk D, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296812
DESCRIPTION:Join the Global Affairs Club for a sweet way to support an important cause. On April 22nd from 12–2 PM at JC Kiosk D, we will be hosting a donut fundraiser where all proceeds will go toward humanitarian support efforts in Sudan.\nStop by between classes, grab a donut, and help make a difference. This event is a small way for our campus community to come together and raise awareness and support for people affected by the ongoing humanitarian crisis.\nBring your friends, enjoy a treat, and contribute to a meaningful global cause.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296812
