SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Goals and Bundts!
LOCATION:JC kisok, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297986
DESCRIPTION:Join Hearts for Humanity for a fun and interactive tabling event where you can take a moment to reflect, set achievable goals, and start building toward your future. Whether your goals are academic, personal, or wellness-focused, we invite you to write them down and take the first step toward making them a reality. As you participate, enjoy a sweet treat with free bundt cakes while connecting with others and spreading positivity on campus. Stop by, set your goals, and leave feeling motivated and inspired.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297986
