UID:9ea8593766a7f723f5cf62d131b52f563262026_12:24:51_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Hygiene Kits Donation Drive
LOCATION:EXPLORATORY 3301, 4400 University Dr, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297542
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the month of April to help donate materials for local shelters in the Fairfax and Loudoun County families!\n\nOn April 22nd, we will be packing these kits and delivering them to shelters! Please donate via Amazon Wishlist and Venmo! Our hygiene kits will be donated to ShelterHouse, a local shelter serving Fairfax and Loudoun counties. Our goal is to purchase all items by this date and pack our Hygiene Kits as a group. \n\n-\n\nPlease look forward to our sub events where we sell Alanis & Jarritos to our communidad!\n\nApril 6th: JC East Plaza (Outside), 12:00 - 2:00 PM ; JC Kiosk E, 3:00 - 5:00 PM\nApril 8th: JC Kiosk F, 3:00 - 5:00 PM\nApril 13th: JC East Plaza (Outside), 3:00 - 5:00 PM\nApril 15th: JC Kiosk A, 3:00 - 5:00 PM\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297542
END:VEVENT
