DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun volleyball social with Alpha Kappa Psi, Accounting Society at Mason, Mason Consulting Group, and Women in Business! Whether you're a volleyball pro or just looking for a good time, this is the perfect way to unwind, meet new people, and enjoy great food before finals season hits.\n\nRegistration REQUIRED so we can gauge attendance for food. Show up, wear your athletic clothes, bring your friends, and come ready to have a great time with some of the best business students at Mason!\n\nLocation: Hampton Roads Court by Rappahannock Parking Deck\nTime: Wednesday, 4/22 at 5:00 PM \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297949
