UID:086a7ee12648e532f7733b473f0e70d3132026_10:11:13_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Writing Center Wednesday Graduate Write-In—Spring 2026 
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292017
DESCRIPTION:Calling all Mason graduate students! Starting January 28th, every Wednesday evening and Friday morning throughout the semester, graduate students gather to write together for support and accountability! \n\nThis is the event to register for a Wednesday weekly write-in. Writers can join us online each Wednesday from 6:30-8:00pm. On Wednesdays we meet ONLINE ONLY!\n\nWriters bring a set of goals and a commitment to arrive on time and remain for the entire session. We begin with a short conversation about goals and end with a short wrap-up on accomplishments. The remaining time is dedicated to writing. A Writing Center consultant coordinates the session and meets with writers who request consultations for 20-minute sessions.\n\nIf you're looking for group accountability and regular time to write with other Mason graduate students who are also serious about making progress on their writing goals, sign up for any number of sessions. You may schedule just one or two sessions to get started on a course project, or attend all 26 to give yourself regular, structured time to work on a thesis, dissertation, or other writing project.\n\nIf you register for a write-in, you are committing to:\n-Join on time and to stay for the duration\n-Turn off access to Facebook, online games, and other computer/online-based distractions during writing time\n-Minimize distractions by phone by limiting texting and phone calls to scheduled break times\n-Contribute to a supportive writing community among fellow participants\n\nOnce you register for a write-in, the Zoom link will be available. If you register and then realize you can't make it, please cancel your Mason360 reservation and let the coordinator (jwiggi@gmu.edu) know in advance.\n\nTo sign up for a write-in, just register here for the dates you'd like. Please email the writing coordinator Jessie (jwiggi@gmu.edu) with questions. The write-ins are open to Mason graduate students only.\n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/97660056638\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292017
END:VEVENT
