DESCRIPTION:Learn more about human trafficking and how it intersects with your major! We will have speakers from across the public and private sector from investigators, a former national human trafficking hotline advocate, forensic nurse examiners, pro-bono attorneys and more. \n\nCheck out our Instagram to see our evolving list of amazing speakers! \n\nFood will be provided! Come at 6:30pm to network with other students and panelists before the panel. \n\nSee you there! \nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297337
