SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:ADVANCE Spring 2026 Graduation Event
LOCATION:Johnson Center - Bistro (bottom floor), Fairfax, VA United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296990
DESCRIPTION:This event is currently ONLY open to Mason-ADVANCE graduating seniors, no plus ones are currently available. This event will be the only ADVANCE graduation ceremony for Spring and Summer 2026 graduates.\n\nPlease join us for an afternoon of joy, food and celebration! The ADVANCE graduation lunch is a time to reflect on your accomplishments throughout your time at Mason, have lunch catered by Cafe Rio, accept your graduation stole and gift on behalf of the Mason-ADVANCE team and hear some special remarks from the folks who have helped get you to the finish line! Please RSVP by 4/17/26 to ensure accurate food amount is ordered. we hope to see you there!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296990
END:VEVENT
