SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:🚲 Bike to Mason - Mason Square Campus
LOCATION:The Plaza at Mason Square, 3383 Fairfax Dr, , Arlington, VA 22201, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296984
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Bike to Mason at the Mason Square Campus! Ride your bike to campus on April 23 and stop by our event table to celebrate sustainable commuting. We’ll have free food, fun giveaways, and helpful bike resources to support your ride.\n\nWhether you’re a daily cyclist or trying it for the first time, this is a great opportunity to connect with the biking community and learn more about biking at Mason.\n\nCome by, grab some goodies, and enjoy the ride! 🚴‍♂️✨\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296984
