UID:27ef54d4379b9ba403b2d3fb5bfc71293182026_6:32:23_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Voices at the Center
LOCATION:Spiritual and Interfaith Center (Fenwick A), 4469 Aquia Creek Ln, Student Union Building 1, Suite 2400, MSN 2F6, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297263
DESCRIPTION:In this talk, Dr. White will describe his journey into the Greek Orthodox community, with brief stops in Athens, Thessalonica and Istanbul as well as the thriving communities here in the Washington, D.C. area. Welcomed as an outsider, he found a community that was more than willing to guide me as I tried to plumb the depths of a culture and a spiritual tradition thousands of years old\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297263
END:VEVENT
