UID:870def83ab66ce1254af4cae94f173b1362026_4:49:46_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Real Estate 101
LOCATION:Lecture Hall 2, Classroom, Fairfax Campus, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296882
DESCRIPTION:Real Estate 101 is an interactive networking and educational event designed to help students better understand real estate and housing in the Northern Virginia (NoVA) area. Volunteer real estate agents will join us to discuss the leasing and buying process, common gaps and challenges—especially for struggling communities—and what renters and buyers should know to make informed decisions. The event will also explore career paths in real estate while providing practical resources, open discussion, and opportunities to network directly with professionals.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296882
END:VEVENT
