SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:La Herencia: A Night of Masquerade 
LOCATION:Hub Ballroom, Fairfax, Virg 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296767
DESCRIPTION:The Hispanic Latine Leadership Alliance (HLLA) proudly presents its annual gala, “La Herencia: A Night of Masquerade,” an evening dedicated to celebration, culture, and community.\n\nGuests can enjoy a night filled with free food, music, dance performances, and a variety of exciting activities. This event highlights the richness and vibrancy of Hispanic and Latine cultures, offering attendees the opportunity to experience and learn about diverse traditions from across Latin America.\n\nOpen to students, faculty, and the local community, this gala creates a welcoming space to come together in celebration of diversity, unity, and multiculturalism.\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296767
END:VEVENT
