DESCRIPTION:Writing Day is meant to provide CLS graduate students and faculty with a dedicated time and space to work on writing, course work, reading, data analysis, or anything else that needs to be checked off your to-do-list! These events are meant to provide students with a space to dedicate to their tasks while encouraging fellowship amongst students. CLSSA books out a conference room for students to have a dedicated to work on these assignments alongside their peers. Food and coffee will be provided to students to fuel their work.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2284370
