SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Mason Day 2026!
LOCATION:Lot L and Lot A, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2286137
DESCRIPTION:Mason Day is our largest, and longest running, campus tradition! One fun-filled day packed with carnival rides, free games and activities, food trucks, midway games, a concert headliner, and so much more you won't want to miss. \n\nWe cant wait to see you and celebrate the end of another fantastic academic year together!! \n\nFind out more online at MasonDay.gmu.edu\n\nMusical Performances\n-  Student performances will occur from 3pm - 7pm\n- Headliner begins at 8pm (open act will start around 7:30pm)\n\nCheck out our album from Mason Day 2025 here https://universitylife.smugmug.com/Student-Involvement/Mason-Day/Mason-Day-Spring-2025 \nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2286137
