UID:e1f408e2e45cd466dc0c75dd5ade2b2912172025_2:24:36_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Backpacking to Dolly Sods
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291957
DESCRIPTION:Dolly Sods Wilderness is one of the most stunning backpacking destinations on the East Coast. Known for its high elevation bogs, sweeping vistas, and rugged terrain, this trip offers a true taste of backcountry adventure. Expect breathtaking sunrises, quiet forests, and unforgettable nights spent under a vast, star-filled sky. \n\nDifficulty: Intermediate – Participants should be prepared for rocky trails, wet areas, and elevation changes while carrying a full backpack. Mileage varies (6–8 miles per day). \n\nAmenities: No restroom facilities; wilderness camping \n\nTravel Time: 3 hours each way   \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291957
END:VEVENT
