UID:e930b237164fb2c74785cc19fe1abbfb12172025_2:25:30_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:C&O Canal Biking: Great Falls National Park to National Mall
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291958
DESCRIPTION:Ride along one of the most historic and scenic corridors in the region! We’ll start our ride near Great Falls and make our way down the C&O Canal Towpath toward Georgetown and the National Mall. Enjoy peaceful stretches along the Potomac River, lockhouse landmarks, and a rewarding finish in the heart of D.C. \n\nDifficulty: Beginner–Intermediate – The towpath is flat and wide, but riders should expect a full day of biking covering 15–20 miles. \n\nAmenities: Restrooms available at the beginning and along the towpath \n\nTravel Time: 45 minutes each way \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291958
END:VEVENT
