UID:fed42c1a613c75a45ae8f836a71a12163302026_5:17:29_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:WOCStem Brunch
LOCATION:JC Bistro, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297741
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an inspiring and uplifting brunch dedicated to celebrating and empowering women of color in STEM. This event creates a welcoming space for students, professionals, and aspiring leaders to connect, share experiences, and build meaningful networks.\n\nAttendees will enjoy a relaxed brunch atmosphere while engaging in guided conversations, listen to a guest speaker, and have discussions centered on navigating STEM spaces, overcoming barriers, and embracing identity in professional environments. \nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297741
END:VEVENT
