UID:6b0f8c2c781692178c059425ff421b1d1142026_1:30:51_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:The EDGE - Spring Open Climb (Alpine Tower) 
LOCATION:The EDGE Alpine Tower, Mason SciTech Campus, 10960 George Mason Cir, Manassas, VA 20109, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293056
DESCRIPTION:Reach new heights at the EDGE! \nJoin us for an unforgettable experience at George Mason’s Sci Tech Campus as you scale the 50-foot Alpine Tower! This open climb event is perfect for adventurers of all levels. Whether you're trying it for the first time or returning for another round, there’s a route waiting for you. \n\nNo prior experience is needed. Just bring your sense of adventure! \n\nNeed transportation? You can reach SciTech using the free Mason shuttle. Check the Spring 2026 schedule for departure times. \n\nAccessibility: Climbers of all abilities are welcome. Please reach out to us at least 2 weeks prior to discuss accommodations, such as closer parking or adaptive options. edge@gmu.edu\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293056
END:VEVENT
