UID:448610aca13176341910e58bf067aa87392026_5:57:06_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Sips & Jarra
LOCATION:JC Meeting Room A, 4400 University Dr, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296924
DESCRIPTION:Join Libyan Club for Sips & Jarra, a sit-down painting afternoon inspired by the Libyan jarra, a traditional clay jar and cup commonly found in Libyan homes. In this relaxed and intimate setting, attendees will enjoy refreshments and snacks while learning how to paint their own jar-inspired design.\n\nDuring the event, participants will also learn about the cultural history and significance of the jarra in Libyan households and society. \n\nNo painting experience is needed. Come get creative, and connect with others while exploring Libyan culture through traditional art!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296924
END:VEVENT
