SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Clearance Ready: Demystifying the Polygraph
LOCATION:Student Union 1 Building, University Career Services Office, Room 3400, 4400 University Drive, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291745
DESCRIPTION:The polygraph process can be intimidating, but it doesn't have to be. Hear from professionals with experience in the polygraph process about what you can expect, what they might be looking for, and why this is necessary for some cleared positions.\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291745
