UID:00f52bad19d6c79c9706eb382e280b853282026_4:01:20_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Totally (G)Rad: A retro craftzavaganza!
LOCATION:Side Pocket and Patio, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297658
DESCRIPTION:Join the craft club in celebrating our 2026 graduates with food, photos and crafts! Dress up in your retro-est funky fits, connect with craft club members, enjoy the food, get a portrait taken by Photography Club, and enjoy our favorite crafts from this semester at our craft stations!\n\nCraft Stations: photo frame decorating, postcard making, graduation cap decor (bring your own cap!), and coloring books\n\nThis is a celebration for everyone! We will provide dinner, drinks, dessert, as well as all the crafting supplies you'll need but feel free to bring any supplies you'd like to use or a project you want to work on. \n\nBring friends and family, dress up, and enjoy the last big event of Craft Club before summer begins!\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297658
END:VEVENT
