SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AIA Final General Body Meeting
LOCATION:The Hub, Meeting Room 3, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298055
DESCRIPTION:This will be AIA’s Final General Body Meeting of the semester, where we will reflect on the club’s progress and key highlights from recent events while also looking ahead to the future. During the meeting, we will hold officer elections for the upcoming semester and discuss plans, goals, and opportunities for continued growth within AIA. Members will gain insight into how they can stay involved, take on leadership roles, and contribute to the organization moving forward. This event serves as both a conclusion to the semester and a transition into the next phase of AIA, bringing together members to connect, share ideas, and shape the direction of the club.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298055
END:VEVENT
