SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Ask the Professionals: Argon Accounting LLC
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298081
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an interactive virtual workshop featuring Aida Davalos, Director of Accounting at Argon Accounting LLC. In this intimate 30–45 minute "Ask the Professional" chat, Costello College of Business students are invited to have an open, candid conversation covering everything from salary negotiation and job market navigation to entrepreneurship as an international student in the U.S.\n\nCome with your questions, curiosity, and ambition - and leave with practical insights to help launch or nail a rewarding career.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298081
