LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296653
DESCRIPTION:Prometheus may have brought fire to humanity, but Outdoor Adventures is passing on its secret to you…for FREE! Come join us for an hour-long educational session on the art of fire building. By the end, you will be able to take these skills and apply them safely in your own outdoor trips. No prior experience is necessary, and everything will be provided by the Outdoor Adventures team during the course of instruction. Come Meet us At Skyline Fitness Center for the course!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296653
