UID:2f8967272e683303b92168ea2ef3349e3202026_1:54:07_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Behind the Curtain: Total Compensation Webinar
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297315
DESCRIPTION:Looking to start a new job? Don't get blindsided by the offer letter! Join us as we learn from experts in Human Resources (HR) to decode total compensation and negotiate your worth with confidence.\n\n \n\nYou'll Learn:\n\n• What goes beyond your base salary: health insurance, retirement plans, and more!\n\n• How to compare and evaluate different compensation packages.\n\n• Essential questions to ask during the job offer stage.\n\n• Strategies to negotiate for a competitive total compensation offer.\n\nRegister on Handshake Now for this webinar and take control of your financial future\n\nVirtual Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/97871991210\nDress Code: Business Casual\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297315
END:VEVENT
