UID:b58aeed6de631cb850d000cb26e4ca833302026_3:23:42_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:AI in Marketing
LOCATION:HUB Room 3 and 4, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297726
DESCRIPTION:The AI Club and the American Marketing Association will present an AI marketing guide exploring how AI is transforming business-to-consumer and business-to-business marketing. The session will highlight how tools like Claude and Copilot are being used to automate marketing campaigns and how AI agents are increasingly taking on marketing functions. We will also discuss why understanding AI-driven marketing is becoming essential for students entering the field.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297726
END:VEVENT
