URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293750
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Co‑Working & Connection, a recurring in‑person gathering designed to bring the Mason Chooses Kindness community together through collaboration, shared purpose, and intentional kindness. Each session offers dedicated time to connect with eachother through a brief kindness-focused activity. We'll also offer opportunities for MCK updates, MCK working group time, and community co-working. Join us!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2293750
