SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Intro to Virtual Reality (VR) Basics 
LOCATION:Horizon Hall 1410 (check-in 1408), Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297995
DESCRIPTION:Dive into the fundamentals of virtual reality as you learn how Oculus headsets work, navigate their software, and understand the benefits and limitations of both standalone and PC‑powered VR. This hands‑on session lets you step directly into immersive environments, explore VR locomotion, and experience a game or two to build confidence and comfort in virtual spaces.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297995
END:VEVENT
