SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Wandering Wednesday: Sunset Standup Paddleboarding 
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291959
DESCRIPTION:Wind down your week with a peaceful evening on the water. As the sun sets, we’ll paddle across calm water and enjoy golden-hour views while learning the basics of SUP technique. This is a relaxed, beginner-friendly paddle perfect for first-timers or anyone looking to decompress outdoors. \n \nDifficulty: Beginner – Stable boards and calm water make this a great introduction to paddling. \n\nTravel Time: 10 minutes each way \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291959
