DESCRIPTION:Join us for a collaborative gathering designed to empower students through dynamic discussions, networking, and action planning. This is your opportunity to connect with peers, share ideas, and engage in meaningful conversations about initiatives that shape our academic and professional growth. Whether you're a seasoned member or new to the group, your voice matters as we strategize and work together on upcoming projects and events. Join us to build connections, explore leadership opportunities, and make a lasting impact within the student body!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295575
