SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Noche De Cultura
LOCATION:Student Union 1, Quad, Fairfax, VA 22030, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297295
DESCRIPTION:Come to LSA's biggest cultural showcase to celebrate the end of the academic year! Noche de Cultura will show cultural dances such as Baile Folkloricos, soulful renditions of songs in native languages, and captivating spoken word poetry. These cultural performances will be accompanied by Latin cuisine food catering that will capture the food aspect of Latin culture that attendees can experience. Attendees can engage in these performances through mini dance lessons that allows them to get on their feet and move to the Latin rhythms, which is a big aspect of said culture.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297295
END:VEVENT
