UID:3e924ba6e0b4bda03afe027ba0d1b74f1232026_1:54:10_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Vinyl Cutter and Sublimation with Heat Press
LOCATION:Horizon Hall 1408, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294196
DESCRIPTION:This workshop will teach users how to format for sublimation printing onto a number of different material types, including wood, metal, plastics, and fabrics, and will lead participants through a demonstration of the heat press functions, format, and safety procedures. This workshop teaches participants how to design for an operate Vinyl Cutter software and hardware in order to implement a range of different project applications and then to use the heat press to transfer the designs to different materials\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2294196
END:VEVENT
