UID:41ce4ea0028975fd9414d42c9a34e27a472026_8:47:17_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:My Natural Hair Fair 
LOCATION: JC SOUTH PLAZA, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298072
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our Hair Fair, a fun and interactive event celebrating natural hair, beauty, and self-expression! This event will feature hands-on hair activities, educational booths, and engaging trivia to help you learn more about hair care, styling techniques, and healthy hair practices.\nAttendees can explore different stations focused on hair education, discover new products and styles, and connect with others. We’ll also have opportunities to support and network with small businesses in the hair and beauty community.\nWhether you’re looking to learn, shop, or just have a good time, the Hair Fair is the perfect space to embrace your natural beauty and gain valuable knowledge in a welcoming environment.\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298072
END:VEVENT
