SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Hike to Sweet Run State Park
LOCATION:TBD
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291960
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate spring by hiking through the State’s newest state park! This early May trip is a great way to enjoy warm weather, vibrant foliage, and relaxing time outdoors before finals season ramps up. Enjoy scenic trails, quiet forests, and plenty of time to recharge. \n\nDifficulty: Beginner – Expect 4–6 miles on well-marked trails with some mild inclines. \n\nAmenities: Restrooms available at the trailhead \n\nTravel Time: 1 hour and 15 minutes each way \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291960
END:VEVENT
