UID:cd42b282e94e50abbe9c0adfe064f31a162026_9:12:22_AM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Handshake Highlight: Job Search Tips and Tricks
LOCATION:Online Event
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292088
DESCRIPTION:Graduating and need a job now? Handshake is one of the most powerful tools at your disposal. In this 30-minute virtual workshop, we’ll demonstrate the Handshake features most useful in your full-time job search, including how to save your searches, “favorite” employers, filter by location, or get alerts when your dream company posts a new position. You’ll also learn how to identify employers willing to sponsor international students and even ways to get advice directly from employers before you apply.   \n\nZoom to join: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/91449088719 \n\nMeeting Link: https://gmu.zoom.us/j/91449088719\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292088
END:VEVENT
