DESCRIPTION:Interactive activities to support your physical and mental well-being during finals!\nTake a moment for your well-being during finals week! Join the Center for the Advancement of Well-Being, CAPS, Student Health Services, and Mason Recreation for a restorative pop-up event designed to help you pause, recharge, and carry well-being with you wherever you go. Hosted at the SI2GO truck, this event features interactive activities that support both physical and mental well-being.\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2292112
