SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Fellowships in 15 - Summer Series
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295988
DESCRIPTION:Join us in-person at the Writing Center or virtually to learn how fellowships can open doors to research, global experiences, and graduate study. This very short and casual overview is a great chance to meet with an advisor, ask questions, and learn about how you can apply! Bring your lunch, bring a friend, and come learn about Fellowships!\n\nThe Office of Fellowships works with currently enrolled students and alumni as they apply to fellowships, which we define as external (non-Mason) funding that gives you money for school. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295988
END:VEVENT
