SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE: JA 2026 Stock Market Challenge (Age 21+)
LOCATION: Sign in to download the location
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297446
DESCRIPTION:Join Beta Alpha Psi for the 2026 Inaugural JA Stock Market Challenge presented by Baker Tilly, an interactive trading simulation where teams compete to grow a $500,000 mock portfolio in a fast-paced market environment. Participants will analyze trends, make real-time decisions, and test their risk tolerance while working as a team in a high-energy setting.\n\nNo prior finance experience is required. This event is limited to ages 21+.\nDress Code: Business Formal\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297446
