UID:a038dfe897b622f5b425f3c9b7d2f62b2162026_4:02:52_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Heal Together 2026: Rest
LOCATION:Spiritual and Interfaith Center, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295907
DESCRIPTION:SAVE THE DATE: Thursday, May 7th, 2026. \n11:00am-4:00pm at the Spiritual Interfaith Center & Around Campus!\n\nThis year, we honor the power of rest - not as a luxury, but as a vital part of healing, growing, and thriving together. Join us in creating a culture where rest is respected, celebrated, and protected.\n\nHeal Together is an event that brings together individuals from all campuses for a day dedicated to healing, self-care, and wellness. Through curated experience that blend movement, mindfulness, and cultural insights, we provide an inclusive space where individuals can restore balance and build community.\n\nWhat to expect:\nFree aromatherapy workshop: Come make your own essential oil!\nRest spaces across campus\nYoga and Meditation\nCreative outlets for expression\nFree Food!\n-Rest spaces across campus\n-Yoga and Meditation\n-Creative outlets for expression\n-Free Food!\n\nThank you to our Mason sponsors!\n\n-Center for Leadership and Intercultural Engagement (CLIE) \n-Community Engagement and Civic Learning (CECIL) \n-Contemporary Student Services  \n-Human Resources\n-Costello College of Business\n-Carter School \n-Center for the Advancement of Well-being\n-Mason Rec\n-College of Public Health\n-College of Computing and Engineering (CEC)\n-College of Visual and Performing Arts (CVPA)\n-Libraries\n-Student Support and Advocacy Center (SSAC)\n-Housing & Residence Life  \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2295907
END:VEVENT
