SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:2026 Mason Film Festival & FAVS at 20 – Day 2: Alumni Roundtable
LOCATION:Harris Theatre, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296755
DESCRIPTION:The Alumni Rountable will take place at Day 2 of the Mason Film Festival.\n \nThe event is free and open to the public.  Each attendee must have their own separate reservation for each separate event taking place during the two-day Mason Film Festival. On Day 2, seating will be extremely limited. Please be sure to register and reserve your seat.\n\nGeorge Mason University is committed to providing access and reasonable accommodations in its services, programs, and activities. Please make accommodation requests related to a disability by contacting film@gmu.edu at least one week prior to the event.\n\nIn order to increase accessibility for all audiences, all films screened in this year's Festival will have open captions (captioning featured on screen). \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2296755
END:VEVENT
