UID:55a3e50afd45b176ddf7235804fc2e004102026_2:13:24_PM@campusgroups.com
SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:University Commencement
LOCATION:EagleBank Arena, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298212
DESCRIPTION:University Commencement is the official, university-wide graduation ceremony at George Mason University. This event includes:\n\nDegree conferral by the University President.\nRemarks from both the invited Commencement guest speaker and the selected Class of 2026 student speaker.\nMusic provided by the George Mason University student ensemble.\nAll spring bachelor’s and master’s graduates, as well as spring doctoral candidates, are invited to attend.\n\nSpring doctoral candidates will be individually recognized and hooded during the Commencement Ceremony.\nBachelor’s and Master’s graduates will be recognized as a group when their major is called but do not cross the stage individually at this event.  For individual recognition, all Bachelor’s and Master’s graduates will cross the stage at their respective School/College Degree Celebration Ceremonies.\n\nAll students registered to graduate will receive a University Commencement Information Email on March 2 from gmuevent@tassel.com with instructions on registering for your ceremony and claiming tickets.\n\nGuest tickets are required for all guests to enter the arena and attend the ceremonies. If you are attending both Commencement and your College Degree Celebration, you will need the appropriate guest tickets and stage passes for each ceremony.\n\nPlease note that tickets for the University Commencement are available through the George Mason email link for no charge/no service fee. This is the only authorized source for ceremony tickets. Please be aware that reports of individuals selling tickets and charging service fees have been reported in the past. This activity is suspect and caution is advised.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298212
END:VEVENT
