DESCRIPTION:Each School/College will host its own Degree Celebration to honor its graduates.\n\nBachelor’s and Master’s graduates will be individually recognized and photographed as they cross the stage.\nThe event will also feature guest speakers from relevant fields.\n\nAll students registered to graduate will receive a Degree Celebration Information Email on February 27 from gmuevent@tassel.com with instructions on registering for your ceremony and claiming tickets.\n\nGuest tickets are required for all guests to enter the arena and attend the ceremonies. If you are attending both Commencement and your College Degree Celebration, you will need the appropriate guest tickets and stage passes for each ceremony.\n\nPlease note that tickets for the Degree Celebration are available through the George Mason email link for no charge/no service fee. This is the only authorized source for ceremony tickets. Please be aware that reports of individuals selling tickets and charging service fees have been reported in the past. This activity is suspect and caution is advised.\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2298215
