SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Interwoven by LAVIET: AAPI Heritage 
LOCATION:GILLESPIE GALLERY, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297307
DESCRIPTION:The Gillespie Gallery of Art at George Mason University welcomes its attendees to “Interwoven: AAPI Heritage” presented by LAVIET, a Vietnamese American owned upcoming fashion brand. Created at the intersection of culture, fashion, and community, this intimate, curated evening celebrates Asian American voices through storytelling, cultural cuisine tastings, live music performances, and fashion design showcases.\n\n* Dress code: Light muted colors and cultural attire\n* Standing room ticket – no assigned seat\n\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297307
END:VEVENT
