SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Resume Studio
LOCATION:Johnson Center Meeting Room A, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297141
DESCRIPTION:Resume Studio is your one-stop shop for Just-In-Time Fair prep. Drop in to Johnson Center Meeting Room A between 10 and 11:30 am for personalized feedback on your resume, help developing your professional pitch, and guidance what to ask the employer reps at the Just-In-Time Hiring Fair that afternoon. Bring your laptop to update your resume in time to print copies for the fair.    \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297141
