SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:Technical Interviewing Strategies
LOCATION:Johnson Center Meeting Room C, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297138
DESCRIPTION:The technical interview is designed to assess and affirm an applicant’s technical abilities, content knowledge and problem-solving skills and has become a critical part of the hiring process for tech-related roles in recent years. During this session, a top tech recruiter will share what to expect and how to ensure your skills and abilities shine in the process. \n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297138
