DESCRIPTION:Y-Element or Young Element is a powerful, God-given attribute in young adults that drive spiritual victory, enabling them to overcome evil; it signifies youthfullness excitement and passion.\n\n🔥 Y-Elements is a Sunday service that ignites young hearts for God ❤️.We lift up Jesus with praise 🎶, worship 🎤 and dancing 🥳. Every moment ✨ revives our love for God and draws us close to Him 🎉. Come expectant 🔥 for an unforgettable time of faith, fun, and The Word🎉!\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2291920
