LOCATION:JC Meeting Room C, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297662
DESCRIPTION:Step right up and learn all about the Alpha Epsilon Chapter of Gamma Rho Lambda, George Mason's only LGBTQIA+ centered, all inclusive social sorority! Join us for our first information session and our first recruitment event of the semester! At this event, you will meet the siblings, learn about our values, events, leadership opportunities, and what makes our organization special. This the perfect place to ask questions and see if GRL is the right for you! \n*You must attend at least 1 info session and 1 social events to be considered for membership*\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297662
