DESCRIPTION:Come one, come all to Carnival Game Night with Gamma Rho Lambda, George Mason's only LGBTQIA+ centered, all-inclusive national sorority! Join us as awe kick off rush for a fun night of carnival-style games, prizes, and laughter. This is a great change to relax, have fun, hang out with and get to know the siblings of GRL.\n*You must attend at least 1 info session and 1 social event to be considered for membership*\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297664
