SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:CRU Large Group
LOCATION:Johnson Center Cinema, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297644
DESCRIPTION:Come to our weekly Thursday night Large Group meeting! Our night will contain worship, a meet and greet, a talk from a staff member, and a raffle for a prize. If you are a Christian, this is a special oppurtunity for fellowship with brothers and sisters in Christ. If you are not a Christian, this is a special oppurtunity for you to check out who Jesus Christ really is, and what Christianity is all about. Come join this event with fellow college students, and we'll see you on Thursday at Large Group!\nDress Code: Casual (jeans ok)\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297644
END:VEVENT
