SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:GRL Recruitment Event: Movie Night
LOCATION:JC Gold Room , Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297666
DESCRIPTION:Join Gamma Rho Lambda, George Mason's only LGBTQIA+ centered all-inclusive social sorority for Circus Movie Night where we will be watching Madagascar 3: Europe's Most Wanted! Grab some snacks, relax, and enjoy a classic film with the siblings of GRL. We will be handing out bingo cards for you fill while you watch the movie, which you can redeem for prizes at the end of the night. We hope to see you there! \n*To be eligible for membership, you must attend at least 1 social event and 1 info session*\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297666
END:VEVENT
