SUMMARY;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:GRL Recruitment Event: Open Mic Night 
LOCATION:JC Meeting Room C, Fairfax, Virginia, United States
URL:https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297668
DESCRIPTION:Have a talent? Step right up for Open Mic Night with Gamma Rho Lambda, George Mason's only LGBTQIA+ centered, all-inclusive social sorority, and show us what you've got whether it be singing, poetry, comedy, instruments, storytelling, or any hidden talent you would like to share! You are also welcome to just come support and enjoy the show! This is a great opportunity to have fun, be silly, and  get to know Gamma Rho Lambda in a welcoming space. \n*To be eligible for membership, you must attend at least 1 social event and 1 info session*\n---\nEvent Details: https://mason360.gmu.edu/rsvp?id=2297668
